NK133(po)002:1: // bka' ma theg rim dgu'i phrin chog mtha' dag phyogs
NK133(po)002:2: gcig tu bsdus pa'i dkar chag yid bzhin dbang gi
NK133(po)002:3: rgyal po'i bang mdzod ces bya bzhugs so //
NK133(po)002:5: rab 'byams zhing gi bkod pa rgya mtshor rtag tu dgyes rol rgyal dang de sras 'phags pa'i tshogs //
NK133(po)002:7: mtha' dag kun gyi mkhyen brtse nus pa'i dpal yon gcig bsdus gazhana ngor phana bde'i byed po ru /
NK133(po)002:9: ngur smrig 'dzin pa'i gar gyis rnam rol lung rtogs yon tan pha matha'a yasa pa'i grangs dkar gyi /
NK133(po)002:11: 'od zer stong 'bar 'khor lo'i mgon de byang chub bar du rigs kyi bdag por spyi bos mchod //
NK133(po)002:12: 1 gdod nas 'od gsal spros pa kun bral chos
NK133(po)002:13: dbyings dri med shin tu rnam dag sgrib pa gnyis
NK133(po)002:15: srid dang zhi ba mnyam par brdal ba'i ye shes
NK133(po)002:16: chen pos yongs ye snod bcud dag pa'i 'khor lor
NK133(po)002:17: longs spyod rdzogs // mkhyen brtse'i rol gar zhi dang
NK133(po)002:18: khro chags gdul bya'i rjes 'gro srid mthas gtugs par
NK133(po)002:19: mdzad pa mi nyams sprul pa'i sprin //
NK133(po)002:20: sku gsum bdag nyid mkhyen pa bzhi ldan phyogs bcu'i
NK133(po)002:21: zhing gi mgon po rnams la rab tu dwangs pas
NK133(po)002:22: bdag phyag 'tshal / 2 /'phags pa gsum gyi so
NK133(po)002:23: so rang gi ye shes dag pa'i spyod yul nyid
NK133(po)002:24: gyur chags bral 'gogs pa'i dbyings de dang //
NK133(po)002:25: lam bden gyis bsdus byang chub phyogs dang stobs sogs
NK133(po)002:26: 'bras chos rtogs pa'i ngo bor gyur pa mtha' dag
NK133(po)002:27: bcas // kun gyi lam rkyen dmigs par gyur pa'i
NK133(po)002:28: gsung rab yan lag bcu gnyis la sogs lung gi
NK133(po)002:30: kun 'byung srid pa'i tsha gdung gzhil mdzad zhi bsil
NK133(po)002:31: bdud rtsi'i dpal gyi 'byung gnas ma la ya tshal
NK133(po)002:33: yan lag brgyad ldan 'phags pa'i lam gyi rol mtsho'i
NK133(po)002:34: dbus su bslab gsum gshog yangs dkar po'i 'jo sgeg
NK133(po)002:35: gis // brgya phrag lung dang rig pa'i rnam 'gyur
NK133(po)002:36: cir yang ngoms pa'i dar dir mgrin pa'i rdza rnga
NK133(po)002:37: gis // cher sgrogs shing // rgyal bstan pad+ma'i mtsho
NK133(po)002:38: chen mdzes byed bshad dang sgrub pa'i zlos gar stong
NK133(po)002:39: du bsgyur mkhas thub pa'i sras //
NK133(po)002:40: theg gsum dge 'dun ngang mo'i khyu tshogs slob dang
NK133(po)002:41: mi slob bcas kun lan brgyar bstod cing dad phyag
NK133(po)002:42: brtsegs / 4 /'phags yul chos kyi gsang mdzod brtol nas kyang //
NK133(po)002:43: bsil ldan gangs ris bskor ba'i ljongs 'di ru //
NK133(po)002:44: bstan pa rin chen 'dren pa'i shing rta ba //
NK133(po)002:45: rgya bod lo pan mkhas pa'i tshogs rnams rgyal /
NK133(po)002:47: 5 / bskal mang gong nas goms pa'i bsod nams stobs //
NK133(po)002:48: smon lam shugs kyis 'phangs pa'i sems dpa' rnams //
NK133(po)002:49: bod yul rgyal po'i zol gyis chos skyongs pa //
NK133(po)002:50: mes dbon gsum sogs bka' drin snying nas dran /
NK133(po)002:52: 6 / snyigs ma'i spyod tshul chu 'dzin 'khrigs pa'i ltor //
NK133(po)002:53: rnam dag bstan pa'i nyi ma nub nye'i tshe //
NK133(po)002:54: thugs bskyed stobs kyis slar yang gsal mdzad pa'i //
NK133(po)002:55: 'dul 'dzin dbang po rma g.yo gtsang gsum rgyal /
NK133(po)002:57: 7 / gzhan yang mdo sngags theg pa rgya mtsho yi //
NK133(po)002:58: bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan srid rtser bsgreng mkhas pa'i //
NK133(po)002:59: grags snyan phyogs su 'bar ba'i skyes bu mchog /
NK133(po)002:60: gang yin kun la mgo bos phyag 'tshal nas /
NK133(po)002:61: 8 /'di ru snga 'gyur theg pa rim pa dgu'i //
NK133(po)002:62: chos tshul rgya mtsho'i bcud phyung bka' ma yi //
NK133(po)002:63: phrin chog mtha' dag bsdus pa'i bzhugs byang gi //
NK133(po)002:64: dkar chag yid bzhin bang mdzod gsal bar bya //
NK133(po)002:65: de ltar tshigs su bcad pa nyung ngus mdun bsus nas //
NK133(po)002:66: 'dir bka' ma theg rim dgu'i phrin chog mtha' dag
NK133(po)002:67: phyogs gcig tu bsdus pa'i spar gyi bzhugs byang dkar
NK133(po)002:68: chag su bkod yid bzhin dbang gi rgyal po'i bang
NK133(po)002:69: mdzod ces bgyi ba 'di la don rnam pa gsum
NK133(po)002:70: ste / bstan pa rin po che spyi'i babs tshul lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK133(po)002:71: ji ltar spar du sgrub tshul bzhugs byang dkar chag dngos 'god pa dang /
NK133(po)002:72: de ltar bsgrub pa'i dgos ched phan yon bstan pa bsngo smon shis brjod dang bcas pa'o //
NK133(po)002:73: dang po la'ang ston pa mchog gi sprul pa'i skus
NK133(po)002:74: byang chub brnyes nas chos kyi 'khor lo bskor zhing
NK133(po)002:75: bka' yi bsdu ba mdzad tshul /
NK133(po)002:76: de nas rgyu dang 'bras bu'i theg pa so sor 'phags pa'i yul du ji ltar bskyangs tshul /
NK133(po)002:77: phyis gangs can gyi ljongs 'dir mdo sngags kyi bstan
NK133(po)002:78: pa dar tshul skabs babs kyi brgyud pa'i lo rgyus
NK133(po)002:79: dang bcas pa ste gsum las /
NK133(po)002:81: theg pa thun mong gi 'dod pa brjod pa dang /
NK133(po)002:82: thun mong ma yin pa theg mchog rdo rje rtse mo'i lugs bzhag pa'o //
NK133(po)002:84: theg pa che chung gi phyogs gnyis las /
NK133(po)002:85: nyan thos spyi'i lugs ltar na /
NK133(po)002:86: bdag cag gi ston pa 'dis bskal pa grangs med
NK133(po)002:87: gsum gyi sngon rol du sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa
NK133(po)002:88: chen po'i drung du byang chub mchog tu thugs bskyed
NK133(po)002:89: pa nas brtsams te byang chub snying po'i shing drung
NK133(po)002:91: so so'i skye bo dbang rnon tshogs kyi lam pa zhig yin pa las /
NK133(po)002:92: de nas gdan thog gcig tu lam lnga rdzogs par mdzad nas mngon par sangs rgyas par 'dod de /
NK133(po)002:94: ston dang bse ru byang chub pa //
NK133(po)002:95: bsam gtan mtha' rten gcig la kun //
NK133(po)002:97: theg pa chen po pa'ang 'ga' zhig gis ni /
NK133(po)002:98: thog mar sems bskyed nas grangs med dang por tshogs sbyor gyi lam gnyis dang /
NK133(po)002:99: gnyis par ma dag sa bdun /
NK133(po)002:100: gsum par dag pa sa gsum rnams rdzogs par mdzad
NK133(po)002:101: nas 'og min rnam mdzes chen por mngon par sangs
NK133(po)002:102: rgyas nas / slar yang 'dod pa'i khams 'dir 'tshang rgya ba'i tshul bstan par bzhed de /
NK133(po)002:103: rgyan stug po bkod pa las /
NK133(po)002:104: yang dag sangs rgyas 'og min du //
NK133(po)002:105: sangs rgyas ma gyur 'dod khams su //
NK133(po)002:106: sangs rgyas mdzad pa mi mdzad do //
NK133(po)002:108: chos dang longs spyod mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i mdo las /
NK133(po)002:109: rin chen sna tshogs mdzes pa yi //
NK133(po)002:110: 'og min gnas ni nyams dga' ba //
NK133(po)002:111: gtsang ma'i gnas kyi steng bzhugs te //
NK133(po)002:112: yang dag sangs rgyas der sangs rgyas //
NK133(po)002:115: yang theg chen pa kha cig gis bzhed pa ltar na /
NK133(po)002:116: ston pa 'di nyid bskal pa bsam gyis mi khyab
NK133(po)002:117: pa'i gong nas mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas nas
NK133(po)002:118: / slar mi mjed 'jig rten gyi khams gling bzhi
NK133(po)002:119: bye ba phrag brgya 'di nyid kyis mtshon pa'i phyogs
NK133(po)002:120: bcu'i zhing khams rgya mtsho bsam gyis mi khyab par
NK133(po)002:121: / / sems can gyi khams rgya mtsho smin par bgyi ba'i phyir /
NK133(po)002:122: la lar byang chub tu thugs bskyed pa dang /
NK133(po)002:123: la lar lam sbyangs pa dang /
NK133(po)002:124: la lar sa nas sar 'phar ba dang /
NK133(po)002:125: la lar mngon par byang chub pa dang /
NK133(po)002:126: la lar chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba sogs sangs
NK133(po)002:127: rgyas kyi rnam par rol pa tshad med pa'i bkod
NK133(po)002:128: pa rgya mtsho sngon dang phyi ma'i mtha' mi mngon
NK133(po)002:130: yab sras mjal ba'i mdo las /
NK133(po)002:131: dpa' bo chen po thabs mkhas te //
NK133(po)002:132: sems can yongs su smin mdzad phyir //
NK133(po)002:133: bye ba phrag brgyar rgyal ba nyid //
NK133(po)002:134: sangs rgyas nyid du bstan gyur kyang //
NK133(po)002:135: da dung yang ni 'dren pa khyod //
NK133(po)002:136: sangs rgyas mang por ston par mdzad //
NK133(po)002:138: mdo sde pad+ma dkar po las /
NK133(po)002:139: bskal pa bye stong bsam gyis mi khyab pa //
NK133(po)002:140: de yi tshad ni nam yang med pa nas //
NK133(po)002:141: byang chub mchog rab 'di ni ngas thob ste //
NK133(po)002:142: nga ni rtag tu chos kyang rab 'chad do //
NK133(po)002:144: de rnams kyang gdul bya'i blo stobs che chung gi
NK133(po)002:145: dbang las 'dod tshul tha dad du byung bar snang
NK133(po)002:146: yang / don sangs rgyas kyi spyod yul ni bsam
NK133(po)002:147: gyis mi khyab pa'i phyir mtha' gcig tu tshad gzung
NK133(po)002:148: bar sla ba ma yin te /
NK133(po)002:150: byang chub rgya mtsho ra ba brnyes gyur nas kyang //
NK133(po)002:151: sems can rgya mtsho rab tu smin bya'i phyir //
NK133(po)002:152: byang chub sems bskyed rgya mtsho ston mdzad cing //
NK133(po)002:153: mi 'grib spyod pa rgya mtsho dus kun ston //
NK133(po)002:154: bde gshegs rnams kyi rnam 'phrul de 'dra'o //
NK133(po)002:157: dpal gsang ba'i snying po las /
NK133(po)002:158: chos sku dpag med brjod du med //
NK133(po)002:159: longs sku zad med yid bzhin gter //
NK133(po)002:160: sprul pa bye ba bsam mi khyab //
NK133(po)002:162: gang gi tshe ston pa sku gsum gyi mnga' bdag 'di nyid /
NK133(po)002:163: srid zhi gang du'ang dbyer mi phyed pa'i snga rol du /
NK133(po)002:164: ye thog dang po'i gzhi la rig pa'i ye shes
NK133(po)002:165: gzung 'dzin gyi sbub rgya las grol te khyad chos
NK133(po)002:166: drug gi tshul gyis mngon par byang chub nas /
NK133(po)002:167: nang dbyings gzhon nu bum pa sku'i zhing khams chen
NK133(po)002:168: por dbyings ye shes 'du 'bral med pa'i dgongs pa
NK133(po)002:169: 'od gsal ba'i ngang dus gsum 'pho 'gyur med par
NK133(po)002:170: bzhugs pa la / dpal chos sku'i ston pa kun tu bzang po zhes grags te /
NK133(po)002:172: rab tu dag pa kun gyi mchog /
NK133(po)002:173: gdod nas grol ba de bzhin gshegs //
NK133(po)002:174: kun tu bzang po kun gyi bdag /
NK133(po)002:175: byang chub sems nyid nges pa'o //
NK133(po)002:177: de lta bu'i dgongs pa chos nyid kyi ngang na /
NK133(po)002:178: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba thams cad gcig dang tha
NK133(po)002:179: dad bral ba'i rang bzhin du dbyer mi phyed cing
NK133(po)002:180: yul yul can gyi dngos por ma grub pas /
NK133(po)002:181: phan tshun gzigs bya gzigs byed las 'das pa'i rang
NK133(po)002:182: byung gi ye shes kyi rol pa 'ba' zhig tu
NK133(po)002:183: snang ba ste / gsang snying las /
NK133(po)002:184: gcig dang tha dad bral ba yi //
NK133(po)002:185: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin nyid //
NK133(po)002:186: sangs rgyas kyis kyang mi gzigs te //
NK133(po)002:187: rang byung ye shes gnas med snang //
NK133(po)002:189: de ltar gnyis su med pa'i ston pa kun tu
NK133(po)002:190: bzang po de nyid kyis 'khor ye shes rgya mtsho
NK133(po)002:191: la / dus bsam gyis mi khyab par /
NK133(po)002:192: chos 'od gsal 'dus ma byas pa'i dgongs pa rang snang bar mdzad do //
NK133(po)002:195: yi ge med dang rig pa'i gsung //
NK133(po)002:196: ljags kyi rtse mor ma phyung yang //
NK133(po)002:197: thugs rje gsung gi byin rlabs kyis //
NK133(po)002:198: 'gro don sna tshogs so sor gsal //
NK133(po)002:200: de'i ngang las nang gsal thim la ma rmug phra ba'i ye shes mched pa'i cha las /
NK133(po)002:201: lhun grub stug po bkod pa'i zhing khams longs spyod
NK133(po)002:202: chen po'i rgyan dang bkod pa tshad med par rang
NK133(po)002:203: snang ba ni / snga ma las /
NK133(po)002:204: phyogs bcu dus bzhi mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK133(po)002:205: zhing khams rnam dag bsam yas dang //
NK133(po)002:206: rgya dang bral ba'i gzhal yas khang //
NK133(po)002:207: 'khor lo'i rgyan dang rol mo'i tshogs //
NK133(po)002:208: dkyil 'khor ma lus bsam yas kun //
NK133(po)002:209: mthong nas nye bar mnyes pa dang //
NK133(po)002:210: rgya chen gsung la don byung ba'ang //
NK133(po)002:211: mthun pa'i ye shes rang snang ba'o //
NK133(po)002:213: der mnga' dbang rdzogs pa'i ston pa kun tu bzang
NK133(po)002:214: po nyid mtshan dang dpe byad yongs su rdzogs pa
NK133(po)002:215: rigs bdag drug pa'i phyag rgyar bzhengs nas /
NK133(po)002:220: 'jom byed khro bo dang bcas pa snang bar mdzad pa yang /
NK133(po)002:221: rgyal ba'i ye shes kyi rang snang kho na ste /
NK133(po)002:223: zag pa med pa'i bsod nams kyi //
NK133(po)002:224: ye shes sgyu ma rang snang ba //
NK133(po)002:225: rol mo'i dkyil 'khor mtha' yas mchog /
NK133(po)002:226: gsang ba'i thig le nyid kyi dbyings //
NK133(po)002:228: de lta bu'i gnas dang ston 'a khor thams cad
NK133(po)002:229: skye 'jig mtshan ma'i yul las ring du song ba'i
NK133(po)002:230: dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid kyi 'khor lor rdzogs pa
NK133(po)002:231: na / chos zab gsang rdo rje'i theg pa nang
NK133(po)002:232: pa bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi 'khor lo sgra tshig rang
NK133(po)002:233: mtshan las 'das pa'i gsung gis rgyun mi 'chad par
NK133(po)002:235: de las e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK133(po)002:236: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK133(po)002:237: sgra dang ming tshig kun las 'das //
NK133(po)002:238: sna tshogs sgra rnams gsal bar 'byung //
NK133(po)002:240: theg pa mtho dman bsam yas kyang //
NK133(po)002:241: de bzhin nyid las ma gsung ste //
NK133(po)002:242: gdul bya'i thabs su so sor thos //
NK133(po)002:244: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs sku'i zhing khams chen po 'di nyid ni /
NK133(po)002:245: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams 'ba' zhig gi spyod yul las /
NK133(po)002:246: sa bcu pa'i sems dpa' rnams la'ang snang ba ma yin te /
NK133(po)002:248: sangs rgyas khams dang sangs rgyas byang chub dang //
NK133(po)002:249: sangs rgyas yon tan sangs rgyas phrin las te //
NK133(po)002:250: dag pa'i sems can gyis kyang bsam bya min //
NK133(po)002:251: 'di ni 'dren pa rnams kyi spyod yul yin //
NK133(po)002:253: de ltar sangs rgyas rang snang gis bsdus pa'i sa
NK133(po)002:254: na gnyis snang gi rtog pa shin tu phra ba'ang
NK133(po)002:255: dbyings su nub pas byed rtsol gyi spros pa mi
NK133(po)002:256: mnga' yang / sngon gyi thugs rje chen po'i dbang gis /
NK133(po)002:257: gdul bya'i khams la gzugs sku'i rnam rol sna tshogs su snang ba ste /
NK133(po)002:259: de bzhin nyid las ma g.yos kyang //
NK133(po)002:260: yang dag thar ba'i gzugs sku dang //
NK133(po)002:262: mthun byas sku ni sna tshogs ston //
NK133(po)002:264: rang snang longs spyod rdzogs pa'i ngang las mkha' zla chu mtshor shar ba ltar /
NK133(po)002:265: gdul bya sa bcu'i sems dpa' rnams kyi ngor /
NK133(po)002:266: gnas 'og min khang bu brtsegs pa la sogs par /
NK133(po)002:267: ston pa rnam par snang mdzad sogs rigs lnga'i sangs
NK133(po)002:268: rgyas mtshan dang dpe byad rgya mtshos brgyan pa'i skur
NK133(po)002:269: snang bas / chos bya spyod rnal 'byor gyi rgyud
NK133(po)002:270: gsum gtso bor gyur pa'i gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde
NK133(po)002:271: mtha' dag dgongs pa brda'i gsung gis /
NK133(po)002:272: dus rtag pa rgyun gyi 'khor lor ston par mdzad pa ste /
NK133(po)002:274: 'og min snga med gnas mchog tu //
NK133(po)002:275: sku ni rnam par snang mdzad tshul //
NK133(po)002:276: byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor rnams la //
NK133(po)002:277: 'di bzhin gsung mchog mi smra ste //
NK133(po)002:278: sku yis chos rnams mjal bar ston //
NK133(po)002:280: de'i tshe 'jig rten gyi khams ma dag pa rnams su /
NK133(po)002:282: rgyal ba'i thugs rje'i rkyen nye bar 'dzoms pa las /
NK133(po)002:283: gang zag so so'i khams dbang dang 'tshams par zhi
NK133(po)002:284: dang khro bo'i sprul pa'i rol gar chags can dang
NK133(po)002:285: / chags bral gyi tshul bsam gyis mi khyab par snang ba yang /
NK133(po)002:287: de tshe mi mthun sna tshogs la //
NK133(po)002:288: so so 'dra bar snang ba ni //
NK133(po)002:289: de bzhin nyid las ma g.yos kyang //
NK133(po)002:290: las 'phro'i dbang gis so sor snang //
NK133(po)002:291: dper na me long chu zla bzhin //
NK133(po)002:292: zhes pas steng 'og dang s+n+rel gzhi'i 'jig rten 'gro
NK133(po)002:293: ba drug gi gnas ris so sor rig pa'i skyes
NK133(po)002:294: bu thub pa drug grangs med par sprul nas sems
NK133(po)002:295: can gyi don mdzad pa ste /
NK133(po)002:297: lha yi gnas na brgya byin mgon //
NK133(po)002:298: lha ma yin la thag bzang ris //
NK133(po)002:300: yi dwags rnams la kha 'bar ste //
NK133(po)002:301: dmyal bar las kyi gshin rje mgon //
NK133(po)002:304: de tshe 'gro drug thams cad la //
NK133(po)002:305: sdig spong gzugs su snang bar bstan //
NK133(po)002:307: de ltar sprul pa'i rol pa tshad med par bkod pa las /
NK133(po)002:308: gtso bor mchog gi sprul pa'i sku'i 'gro ba 'dul ba'i phrin las ji ltar mdzad pa'i tshul yang /
NK133(po)002:310: s+n+rel gzhi dang yan man gyi 'jig rten drug gi
NK133(po)002:311: phyogs bcu mtha' yas mu med pa'i stong gsum gyi
NK133(po)002:313: thub pa chen po bcom ldan 'das re res gdul
NK133(po)002:314: ba rnam bzhis 'gro ba'i don mdzad de zhes pa
NK133(po)002:315: ltar bzhi las / sku bsod nams chen po'i 'dul ba ni /
NK133(po)002:316: mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyi sgo nas sems can gyi don mdzad pa ste /
NK133(po)002:317: de yang rgyud bla ma las /
NK133(po)002:318: thugs rje chen pos 'jig rten mkhyen //
NK133(po)002:319: 'jig rten kun la gzigs nas ni //
NK133(po)002:320: chos kyi sku las ma g.yos par //
NK133(po)002:321: sprul pa'i rang bzhin sna tshogs kyis //
NK133(po)002:322: skye ba mngon par skye ba dang //
NK133(po)002:323: dga' ldan gnas nas 'pho ba dang //
NK133(po)002:324: lhums su 'jug dang bltams pa dang //
NK133(po)002:325: bzo yi gnas la mkhas pa dang //
NK133(po)002:326: btsun mo'i 'khor dgyes rol ba dang //
NK133(po)002:327: nges 'byung dka' ba spyod pa dang //
NK133(po)002:328: byang chub snying por gshegs pa dang /
NK133(po)002:329: bdud sde 'joms dang rdzogs par ni /
NK133(po)002:330: byang chub chos kyi 'khor lo dang //
NK133(po)002:331: mya ngan 'da' bar ston mdzad rnams //
NK133(po)002:332: yongs su ma dag zhing rnams su //
NK133(po)002:333: srid pa ji srid gnas par ston //
NK133(po)002:337: theg pa lnga las brtsams pa'i chos kyi tshul dpag
NK133(po)002:338: tu med pa snang bar mdzad pa rnams yin te
NK133(po)002:340: 'dul ba'i dbang gis lha dang mi'i theg pa dang /
NK133(po)002:341: nyan thos kyi theg pa dang /
NK133(po)002:342: rang byang chub kyi theg pa dang /
NK133(po)002:343: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa dang /
NK133(po)002:344: bla na med pa'i theg pas /
NK133(po)002:345: ma rig pa'i rnam par rtog pa nyon mongs pa
NK133(po)002:346: stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi'i gnyen por chos stong
NK133(po)002:347: phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi gsungs so //
NK133(po)002:351: thugs mngon sum pas 'dul ba ni /
NK133(po)002:352: mngon shes drug gi sgo nas gdul bya'i rgyud smin par mdzad pa ste /
NK133(po)002:354: dus bzhi kun tu mkhyen pa dang /
NK133(po)002:355: thams cad kyi sems kyi rgyud kun tu mkhyen pa dang /
NK133(po)002:356: rdzu 'phrul gyi spyan gyis thams cad kun tu gzigs pa dang /
NK133(po)002:357: rdzu 'phrul gyi snyan gyis kun tu gsan pa dang /
NK133(po)002:358: rdzu 'phrul gyi tshogs kun tu don spyod pa dang /
NK133(po)002:359: zag pa med pa kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa
NK133(po)002:360: yongs su rdzogs pa'i mngon par shes pa chen po
NK133(po)002:362: rdzu 'phrul bsam gyis mi khyab pas 'dul ba ni /
NK133(po)002:364: kun tu sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK133(po)002:365: kun tu thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK133(po)002:366: kun tu zhal bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK133(po)002:367: kun tu gsung bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK133(po)002:368: bsam gyis mi khyab pa grangs med phyogs bcur snang bar 'gyur ro zhes pa ltar ro //
NK133(po)002:369: mdor na rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs mi zad pa
NK133(po)002:370: rgyan gyi 'khor lo bsam gyis mi khyab pa las
NK133(po)002:371: gang 'dul gzugs sku'i rol ba ni gdul bya'i 'gro
NK133(po)002:372: ba mtha' dag gi khams dang dbang po bsam pa'i
NK133(po)002:373: bye brag ji ltar mos pa bzhin du mtha' yas
NK133(po)002:375: de lta bu'i ston pa sku gsum gyi bdag nyid
NK133(po)002:376: can de'i bstan pa dam pa'i chos kyi tshul 'god
NK133(po)002:377: pa la / spyir chos zhes bya ba ni /
NK133(po)002:379: chos ni shes bya lam dang ni //
NK133(po)002:380: mya ngan 'das dang yid kyi yul //
NK133(po)002:381: bsod nams tshe dang gsung rab dang //
NK133(po)002:388: khyad par du 'phags pa'i don gyis /
NK133(po)002:389: sdug kun phyogs kyi gnyen por gyur pa rnam byang gis bsdus pa'i chos la 'jug ste /
NK133(po)002:390: sdug bsngal dag ni thams cad dang //
NK133(po)002:391: sgrib kun sel byed dam pa'i chos //
NK133(po)002:394: brjod bya don gyi ngo bor gyur pa rtogs pa'i chos dang /
NK133(po)002:395: rjod byed tshig gi rigs su gnas pa lung gi chos gnyis te /
NK133(po)002:397: ston pa'i dam chos rnam gnyis te //
NK133(po)002:398: lung dang rtogs pa'i bdag nyid do //
NK133(po)002:400: de la rtogs pa'i chos ni 'gog pa dang lam gyi bden pa dag gis bsdus pa ste /
NK133(po)002:402: gang zhig gang gis chags bral ba //
NK133(po)002:403: bden gnyis mtshan nyid can de chos //
NK133(po)002:404: chags bral nyid ni 'gog pa dang //
NK133(po)002:405: lam gyi bden pa dag gis bsdus //
NK133(po)002:408: lam bden gyi dmigs par gyur pa gsung rab ming
NK133(po)002:409: tshig gi rnam par gnas pa gang zhig ngo bo'i
NK133(po)002:411: legs par gsung ba'i bka' dang /
NK133(po)002:412: de'i dgongs 'grel gyi bstan bcos gnyis te /
NK133(po)002:413: lha'i bus zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK133(po)002:414: chos rnams thams cad bka' dang bstan bcos gnyis su 'dus //
NK133(po)002:415: legs par gsung dang de yi dgongs 'grel pa //
NK133(po)002:419: gang zhig don ldan chos dang nyer 'brel zhing //
NK133(po)002:420: khams gsum kun nas nyon mongs spong byed gsung //
NK133(po)002:421: zhi ba'i phan yon ston par mdzad pa gang //
NK133(po)002:422: de ni drang srong gsung yin bzlog pa gzhan //
NK133(po)002:424: brjod bya don ldan gyi chos lhag pa'i bslab pa
NK133(po)002:425: gsum dang nye bar 'brel zhing byed las khams gsum
NK133(po)002:426: gyi nyon mongs pa mthong sgom lam gyis spang bya
NK133(po)002:427: thams cad spong bar byed pa dang /
NK133(po)002:428: 'bras bu zhi ba mya ngan las 'das pa'i phan yon ston par byed pa gang zhig /
NK133(po)002:429: bdag rkyen rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi rnam rig las byung ba'o //
NK133(po)002:432: gang zhig rgyal ba'i bstan pa 'ba' zhig gi //
NK133(po)002:433: dbang byas rnam g.yeng med yid can gyis bshad //
NK133(po)002:434: thar ba thob pa'i lam dang rjes mthun pa //
NK133(po)002:435: de yang drang srong gsung bzhin spyi bos blang //
NK133(po)002:437: rtsom pa po rnam g.yeng med pa'i yid can zab mo'i blo dang ldan pa dag gis /
NK133(po)002:438: rgyal ba'i bstan pa kho na'i dbang du byas nas
NK133(po)002:439: thar ba'i lam mtshon pa'i ngag 'chos skyobs kyi yon
NK133(po)002:440: tan gnyis dang ldan par bkod pa la bstan bcos
NK133(po)002:441: zhes brjod de / rnam bshad rig par /
NK133(po)002:442: nyon mongs dgra rnams ma lus 'chos pa dang //
NK133(po)002:443: 'khor ba'i 'jig las skyob pa gang yin pa //
NK133(po)002:444: 'chos skyob yon tan phyir na bstan bcos te //
NK133(po)002:445: gnyis po 'di dag gzhan gyi lugs la med //
NK133(po)002:447: de ltar lung dang rtogs pa'i rnam 'byed spyir bkod nas /
NK133(po)002:448: bye brag chos kyi 'khor lo ji ltar bskor ba'i tshul dngos la /
NK133(po)002:449: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa rnams ni rgyal ba
NK133(po)002:450: thabs la mkhas pa'i bdag nyid can des gdul bya'i
NK133(po)002:451: gang zag gi blo nus kyi rim pa dang mthun
NK133(po)002:452: par / 'o ma'i sman gyi dpe dang /
NK133(po)002:453: nor bu sbyong ba'i dpe sogs kyis bstan pa ltar /
NK133(po)002:454: dang por 'khor ba las nges par 'byung ba'i gtam dang /
NK133(po)002:455: bar du rnam thar sgo gsum gyi gtam dang /
NK133(po)002:456: tha mar phyir mi ldog pa'i 'khor lo'i gtam gyis /
NK133(po)002:457: chos kyi 'khor lo rim pa gsum du bskor bar mdzad pa yang /
NK133(po)002:458: gzungs kyi dbang phyug rgyal po'i zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK133(po)002:459: rigs kyi bu de bzhin gshegs pas yongs su ma dag pa'i sems can gyi khams rig nas /
NK133(po)002:463: mi sdug pa yid 'byung bar 'gyur ba'i gtam gyis
NK133(po)002:464: 'khor ba la mngon par dga' ba'i sems can rnams
NK133(po)002:466: 'phags pa'i chos 'dul ba la 'jug par byed do //
NK133(po)002:467: de tsam gyis de bzhin gshegs pa brtson 'grus rgyun mi gcod cing /
NK133(po)002:468: de'i 'og tu stong pa nyid dang /
NK133(po)002:470: smon pa med pa'i gtam gyis de bzhin gshegs pa'i tshul khong du chud par byed do //
NK133(po)002:471: de tsam gyis kyang de bzhin gshegs pa brtson 'grus rgyun mi gcod kyi /
NK133(po)002:472: de'i 'og tu phyir mi ldog pa'i 'khor lo'i gtam
NK133(po)002:473: dang 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa'i gtam gyis sems
NK133(po)002:474: can de dag de bzhin gshegs pa'i yul la 'dzud
NK133(po)002:475: do // zhes gsungs pa ltar las dang po bden bzhi'i chos 'khor ni /
NK133(po)002:476: ston pa sangs rgyas nas zhag bdun phrag bdun gyi mthar shing sgrol rgyu'i tshal du bzhugs nas /
NK133(po)002:477: zab zhi spros bral 'od gsal 'dus ma byas //
NK133(po)002:478: bdud rtsi lta bu'i chos shig bdag gis rnyed //
NK133(po)002:479: su la bstan kyang go bar mi nus pas //
NK133(po)002:480: mi smra nags 'dab nyid du gnas par bya //
NK133(po)002:481: zhes chos mi gsung bar thugs las chung ngu la gzhol ba'i tshe /
NK133(po)002:482: sngon gyi smon lam chen po'i rgyud bskul nas lha'i dbang po tshangs pa dang /
NK133(po)002:483: brgya byin gnyis kyis gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs stong pa dang /
NK133(po)002:484: yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che phul nas
NK133(po)002:485: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar gsol ba btab pa
NK133(po)002:486: la brten nas / yul w+aa ra na s+ai drang srong lhung ba ri dwags kyi nags su /
NK133(po)002:487: 'khor lnga sde bzang po lha brgyad khri dang bcas pa la /
NK133(po)002:488: bden pa bzhi lan gsum du bzlas pa'i chos kyi
NK133(po)002:489: 'khor lo rnam pa bcu gnyis su bskor ba ste
NK133(po)002:490: 'dul ba lung la sogs pa rnams so //
NK133(po)002:491: bar ba mtshan nyid med pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo ni /
NK133(po)002:492: gnas bya rgod spung ba'i ri bo la sogs par /
NK133(po)002:493: 'khor nyan thos dang byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs la /
NK133(po)002:494: zab mo stong pa nyid kyi tshul las brtsams te /
NK133(po)002:495: gzugs nas rnam mkhyen gyi bar gyi chos thams cad
NK133(po)002:496: rang rang gi ngo bos stong par gtan la phabs
NK133(po)002:497: nas bstan pa sher phyin stong phrag brgya ba sogs
NK133(po)002:498: yum sras bcu bdun gyi sder gtogs pa thams cad
NK133(po)002:499: do // tha ma legs pa rnam par phye ba'i chos 'khor ni /
NK133(po)002:502: ma la ya sogs gnas ma nges pa rnams su /
NK133(po)002:503: 'khor byang chub sems dpa' blo gros chen po dang /
NK133(po)002:504: dpal phreng seng ge'i nga ro sogs sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa'i tshul la mkhas pa sha stag la /
NK133(po)002:505: drang ba dang nges pa'i don dag so sor rnam
NK133(po)002:506: par phye ste legs par gtan la phabs nas bshad
NK133(po)002:507: pa / lang kar gshegs pa dang /
NK133(po)002:510: mya ngan las 'das pa chen po'i mdo la sogs pa rnams dang /
NK133(po)002:511: gzhan yang phal po che dang /
NK133(po)002:512: dkon mchog brtsegs pa sogs shin tu rgyas pa'i sde snod ji snyed pa rnams so //
NK133(po)002:513: de ltar chos kyi 'khor lo rim pa gsum du bskor ba yang /
NK133(po)002:514: spang bya dang gnyen po'i sgo nas chos kyi phung po brgyad khri bzhi stong du nges te /
NK133(po)002:516: spyod pa rnams kyi gnyen por ni //
NK133(po)002:517: chos kyi phung po mthun par gsungs //
NK133(po)002:520: nyon mongs 'dod chags 'dul ba'i gnyen po ru //
NK133(po)002:521: 'dul ba'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK133(po)002:522: zhe sdang 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsung pa ni //
NK133(po)002:523: mdo sde'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK133(po)002:524: gti mug 'dul ba'i gnyen po gsung ba ni //
NK133(po)002:525: mngon pa'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK133(po)002:526: cha mnyams 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsung ba ni //
NK133(po)002:527: sde snod bzhi pa nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK133(po)002:529: bdag rkyen ston pas gsungs tshul gyi sgo nas gsum du bzhag ste /
NK133(po)002:530: zhal nas gsungs pa'i bka' dang /
NK133(po)002:531: byin gyis brlabs pa'i bka' dang /
NK133(po)002:533: brjod bya bslab pa gsum du ston pa'i sgo nas kyang gsum ste /
NK133(po)002:534: lhag pa'i tshul khrims kyi bslab pa gtso bor ston pa 'dul ba /
NK133(po)002:535: lhag pa'i sems kyi bslab pa gtso bor ston pa mdo sde /
NK133(po)002:536: lhag pa'i shes rab kyi bslab pa gtso bor ston pa mngon pa rnams so //
NK133(po)002:537: rjod byed gsung rab kyi sgo nas rnam grangs bcu gnyis su 'gyur te /
NK133(po)002:539: mdo sde dbyangs bsnyad lung du bstan //
NK133(po)002:540: tshigs bcad ched brjod gleng gzhi dang //
NK133(po)002:541: rtog brjod de lta bu byung dang //
NK133(po)002:542: skyes rab shin tu rgyas pa dang //
NK133(po)002:543: rmad byung gtan la dbab pa'i sde //
NK133(po)002:544: gsung rab yan lag bcu gnyis so //
NK133(po)002:546: gdul bya'i gang zag gi dbang las /
NK133(po)002:547: theg pa'i rim pa gnyis su yang bzhag ste /
NK133(po)002:551: theg pa mchog gi bye brag gis gnyis su 'gyur te /
NK133(po)002:552: nyan thos kyi sde snod dang /
NK133(po)002:553: byang chub sems dpa'i sde snod do //
NK133(po)002:555: theg dman la nyan rang gnyis su dbye bas theg pa gsum dang /
NK133(po)002:557: rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa so sor phye bas bzhi dang /
NK133(po)002:558: lam stegs lha mi'i theg pa dang bcas pas lngar
NK133(po)002:559: bzhag pa sogs nas gnas skabs lam gyi dbye bas
NK133(po)002:560: grangs med pa'i bar du gsungs kyang /
NK133(po)002:561: mthar thug gi don la theg pa tha dad kyi rnam pa yang bzhag pa 'ga' yang med de /
NK133(po)002:563: ji srid sems ni 'jug pa'i bar //
NK133(po)002:564: theg pa'i mtha' la thug pa med //
NK133(po)002:565: sems ni rab tu gyur pa na //
NK133(po)002:566: theg pa med cing 'gro ba'ang med //
NK133(po)002:568: grub matha'i sgo nas bzhag na /
NK133(po)002:569: 'khor lo dang po'i rjes su 'brang ba theg dman bye mdo gnyis dang /
NK133(po)002:570: 'khor lo bar tha gnyis kyi rjes su 'brang ba theg chen dbu sems gnyis te bzhi'o //
NK133(po)002:571: de dag la'ang nang gses kyi dbye ba dang 'dod
NK133(po)002:572: tshul kyi bye brag rgya cher yod kyang 'dir yi
NK133(po)002:574: de dag las khyad par du 'phags pa 'bras bu
NK133(po)002:575: gsang chen rdo rje'i theg pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo
NK133(po)002:577: gnas rang snang shin tu rnam par dag pa 'og min chen po'i zhing khams su /
NK133(po)002:578: ston pa rigs drug pa kun tu bzang po'am khyab bdag rdo rje 'chang chen pos /
NK133(po)002:579: nyid las mi gzhan pa'i bde bar gshegs pa'i tshogs tshad med pa la /
NK133(po)002:580: chos nyid brjod bral chen po'i dgongs pa sgra tshig
NK133(po)002:581: rang mtshan las 'das pa'i gsung gis snang bar mdzad
NK133(po)002:583: 'og min rnam mdzes chen po dang /
NK133(po)002:585: 'dzam bu'i gling rnams su longs spyod rdzogs pa dang /
NK133(po)002:586: sprul pa'i rnam pa tha dad pas gdul bya sa la gnas pa /
NK133(po)002:587: rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor dpa' bo dang
NK133(po)002:588: rnal 'byor ma'i tshogs bsam gyis mi khyab pa rnams
NK133(po)002:589: la / gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde mtha' dag brda'
NK133(po)002:590: dang tshig gi sgo nas dus ci rigs par gsungs
NK133(po)002:591: la / te / 'jam dpal sgyu d+r+wa'i bshad rgyud las /
NK133(po)002:592: gleng gzhi rnam pa gsum yin te //
NK133(po)002:593: 'og min gnas dang ri rab rtse //
NK133(po)002:595: byang chub sems dpa' lha rnams dang //
NK133(po)002:596: mi rnams kyi ni don du gsungs //
NK133(po)002:597: ston pa yang ni rnam gsum ste //
NK133(po)002:598: sangs rgyas rdo rje 'chang chen dang //
NK133(po)002:599: sprul sku 'khor los bsgyur ba dang //
NK133(po)002:600: sh+aakya thub pa nyid kyis gsungs //
NK133(po)002:601: dus ni gdul bya 'dul ba'i tshe //
NK133(po)002:607: dpal ldan sham+b+ha la sogs su /
NK133(po)002:608: ston pa nyid dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo'i rnam par
NK133(po)002:609: bzhengs pa'am ma bzhengs pa ci rigs pas sngags kyi
NK133(po)002:610: rgyud sde bsam gyis mi khyab pa gsungs so //
NK133(po)002:611: theg pa'i rim pa gzhan ji snyed pa rnams kyang
NK133(po)002:612: dus de'i tshe gsang chen bla na med pa'i chos
NK133(po)002:613: kyi 'khor lo 'di nyid las 'phros te gsungs pa'ang
NK133(po)002:615: 'dul ba mdo sde chos mngon dang //
NK133(po)002:616: dam tshig sgrub dang grub pa dang //
NK133(po)002:617: sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi rgyud //
NK133(po)002:618: phyogs bcu rnams su rab grags pa //
NK133(po)002:619: gsang ba'i snying po las 'phros te //
NK133(po)002:620: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di //
NK133(po)002:621: sde snod kun dang rgyud kun gyi //
NK133(po)002:624: de ltar rgyu dang 'bras bu'i theg pa ji ltar gsungs pa rnams /
NK133(po)002:625: so sor bka' yi bsdu ba mdzad pa'i tshul la /
NK133(po)002:626: theg dman nyan rang dang thun mong pa'i sde snod rnams te /
NK133(po)002:627: ston pa mya ngan las 'das pa'i 'og tu /
NK133(po)002:628: lha rnams kyis 'phya ba bsal ba'i phyir /
NK133(po)002:629: rgyal po'i khab kyi nya gro d+ha'i phug par /
NK133(po)002:630: dgra bcom pa lnga brgya 'dus nas /
NK133(po)002:633: 'od srung chen pos mngon pa ste /
NK133(po)002:634: sde snod gsum ka legs par bsdus te bka' bsdu dang po'o /
NK133(po)002:636: mi rung ba'i gzhi bcu dang /
NK133(po)002:637: rtsod pa'i gzhi lnga rnams byung ba la brten nas /
NK133(po)002:638: de dag bsal ba'i phyir bka' bsdu gnyis pa dang /
NK133(po)002:639: gsum pa dag kyang rim bzhin mdzad do //
NK133(po)002:640: theg chen pha rol du phyin pa'i sde snod rnams ni /
NK133(po)002:641: rgyal po'i khab kyi lho phyogs bi ma sam b+ha'i ri la rgyal sras 'bum phrag bcu 'dus te /
NK133(po)002:642: phyag na rdo rjes mdo sde /
NK133(po)002:644: 'jam dpal gyis mngon pa rnams bsdus zhes grags so //
NK133(po)002:645: thun mong ma yin pa gsang ba sngags kyi rgyud sde rnams ni /
NK133(po)002:646: lcang lo can du byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs bye
NK133(po)002:647: ba phrag dgu bcu rtsa drug gi dbus su gsang
NK133(po)002:648: ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rje nyid kyis bsdu
NK133(po)002:649: ba mdzad do // in+d+ra b+h+au ti'i bde mchog gi 'grel ba las /
NK133(po)002:650: phyi dus rim par lung bstan sdud pa pos //
NK133(po)002:651: ri bo mchog rab byang shar lha gnas mchog /
NK133(po)002:652: lcang lo can gyi pho brang chen por ni //
NK133(po)002:653: rgyud rnams ma lus sems dpa' chen po'i tshogs //
NK133(po)002:654: bye ba phrag ni dgu bcu rtsa drug sogs //
NK133(po)002:655: 'dus te rje btsun gsang ba'i bdag po la //
NK133(po)002:656: gsol ba btab tshe 'di skad bdag thos zhes //
NK133(po)002:657: rab tu gsungs pa gser gyi glegs bu la //
NK133(po)002:658: bee d+aur+ya yi zhun mas yi ger bkod //
NK133(po)002:661: ma 'ongs ba'i dus su gsang ba'i rgyud skal ba
NK133(po)002:662: dang ldan pa'i sems can la sus 'chad par byed
NK133(po)002:664: phyag na rdo rje mgon pos bshad par byed do //
NK133(po)002:666: de ltar na dus 'khor zla ba bzang po dang brtag gnyis rdo rje snying po /
NK133(po)002:667: rdo rje mkha' 'gro phag mo sogs kyis bsdus pa ma yin nam zhe na /
NK133(po)002:668: de dag rnams kyang ston pa nyid kyi thugs rdo
NK133(po)002:669: rje sdud po dang 'khor gyi tshul du snang ba
NK133(po)002:670: las / rgyud tha dad pa ma yin pa'i phyir skyon med de /
NK133(po)002:671: gsang ba grub pa'i rgyud las /
NK133(po)002:672: 'di yi sdud par byed pa po //
NK133(po)002:673: gzhan dag yod pa ma yin zhes //
NK133(po)002:674: bdag nyid 'ba' zhig smra bar byed //
NK133(po)002:675: rgyud 'chad pa de thugs rdo rje //
NK133(po)002:677: rgyud 'chad pa de thugs rdo rje /
NK133(po)002:678: 'chad pa po de sdud pa'ang de //
NK133(po)002:680: des na rdo rje chos dang /
NK133(po)002:682: rdo rje snying po sogs mtshan gyi rnam grangs tha dad pa dang /
NK133(po)002:683: rdo rje sems dpa' dus kyi 'khor lo /
NK133(po)002:684: sh+aakya thub pa sogs ston pa dang /
NK133(po)002:688: 'khor gyi sku'i snang tshul tha dad pa rnams kyang
NK133(po)002:689: don la dgongs pa dbyer mi phyed par shes par
NK133(po)002:690: bya ste / ye shes thig le'i rgyud las /
NK133(po)002:691: lta ba kun ni srung don du //
NK133(po)002:692: sna tshogs pa yi gzugs su spyod //
NK133(po)002:693: la lar rdo rje 'dzin pa dang //
NK133(po)002:694: la lar sangs rgyas kyi ni gzugs //
NK133(po)002:695: la lar he ru ka yi gzugs //
NK133(po)002:696: la lar de bzhin gshegs pa dang //
NK133(po)002:697: la lar byang chub sems dpa'i gzugs //
NK133(po)002:698: la lar nyan pa lta bur bzhugs //
NK133(po)002:700: la lar klog pa'i tshul du bzhugs //
NK133(po)002:701: la lar rgyud dang bstan bcos ni //
NK133(po)002:702: mdzad pa dang ni la lar 'dzin //
NK133(po)002:703: mang du brjod lta ci zhig dgos //
NK133(po)002:704: de ston phyag na rdo rje rgyal //
NK133(po)002:706: de ltar ston pa sku gsum gyi rnam bzhag chos
NK133(po)002:707: kyi 'khor lo bskor tshul bka' yi bsdu ba mdzad
NK133(po)002:708: pa dang bcas pa mdor bsdus tsam brjod grub nas
NK133(po)002:709: / don gnyis pa rgya gar 'phags pa'i yul du
NK133(po)002:710: rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa bshad sgrub kyi sgo nas
NK133(po)002:711: rim pa bzhin ji ltar bskyangs pa'i tshul la /
NK133(po)002:712: thog mar nyan thos kyi theg pa gtso bor gyur pa'i sde snod rnams ni /
NK133(po)002:713: ston pa mya ngan las 'das pa'i tshe /
NK133(po)002:714: nyan thos 'od srung chen po la bstan pa gtad /
NK133(po)002:715: des kyang sngar bshad pa ltar bka' yi bsdu ba sogs mdzad nas bstan pa dar bar byas te /
NK133(po)002:716: kun dga' bo la gtad nas ri bo bya rkang
NK133(po)002:717: can du sku gdung mi 'jigs par byin gyis rlabs
NK133(po)002:719: kun dga' bos rgyal po'i khab tu gzhon nu gser
NK133(po)002:720: mdog gi skyabs mdzad nas dgra bcom pa la bkod
NK133(po)002:721: pa dang / lho phyogs kyi bram ze ba ra
NK133(po)002:722: d+h+wa dza gnod can dang rus gcig pa cho 'phrul
NK133(po)002:723: gyis tshar bcad pa sogs lha dang mi'i don rgya
NK133(po)002:725: sha na'i gos can bsnyen par rdzogs te bstan pa gtad /
NK133(po)002:726: de nas chu bo gang g+aa'i dbus su drang srong
NK133(po)002:727: nyi ma'i gung ba rab tu phyungs nas bsnyen par
NK133(po)002:728: rdzogs shing / spyir sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa skyongs pa dang /
NK133(po)002:729: khyad par kha che'i yul du bstan pa spel bar gdams nas mya ngan las 'das so //
NK133(po)002:730: sha na'i gos can gyis rgyal po gzhu bzang gi
NK133(po)002:731: 'khor nyis stong rab tu phyungs na sa 'bras bu
NK133(po)002:732: la bkod pa sogs dgra bcom pa khri dang bden
NK133(po)002:733: pa mthong ba'ang 'bum tsam du byung bar grags shing
NK133(po)002:734: / de nas mtshan med pa'i sangs rgyas su lung
NK133(po)002:735: bstan pa spos 'tshong gi bu nyer sbas rab tu
NK133(po)002:736: byung nas bstan pa gtad de yul tsam par mya
NK133(po)002:741: gar mkhan dpa' bo'i gtsug lag khang rnams su rim
NK133(po)002:742: par byon nas chos bstan pas dgra bcom pa thob
NK133(po)002:743: pa yang bgrang gis mi lang ba byung ngo //
NK133(po)002:745: bdud sdig to can rdzu 'phrul gyis btul ba sogs
NK133(po)002:746: rgyal ba'i bstan pa la rmad du byung ba'i mdzad
NK133(po)002:748: grong khyer ma thu rar bram ze d+h+ai ti ka
NK133(po)002:749: rab tu phyung nas zhag bdun na dgra bcom par
NK133(po)002:750: gyur pa de la bstan pa gtad na sa mya
NK133(po)002:752: 'di'i dus su nyan thos bye brag smra ba dag
NK133(po)002:753: gi gzhung phyi mor gyur ba bye brag bshad mdzod
NK133(po)002:754: chen mo'ang dgra bcom pa rnams kyis spyi mthun du
NK133(po)002:756: d+h+ai ti kas tho gar gyi rgyal po nam mkha' la mchod pa dang /
NK133(po)002:757: shar phyogs k+aa ma r+au pa'i bram ze sing+ha zhes
NK133(po)002:758: pa 'khor stong phrag mang po dang bcas pa nyi
NK133(po)002:760: mal+la war bram ze dregs byed ces pa ra skyes
NK133(po)002:761: kyi mchod sbyin byed pa rnams rdzu 'phrul gyis dad
NK133(po)002:762: par byas nas skye bo mang po dgra bcom pa
NK133(po)002:765: de nas shar phyogs ang+ga'i yul gyi tshong dpon nag
NK133(po)002:766: po zhes pa rgya mtsho'i gling du srin mo'i 'jig
NK133(po)002:767: pa las bskyabs nas mthar rab tu phyungs nas dgra
NK133(po)002:768: bcom par gyur pa la bstan pa gtad de grong
NK133(po)002:769: khyer 'phags rgyal du mya ngan las 'das so //
NK133(po)002:770: 'di'i ring la dgra bcom pa grags pa dang /
NK133(po)002:771: thams cad 'dod sogs kyis bka' bsdu bar ba mdzad pa'i skabs yin no //
NK133(po)002:773: kha che'i yul du bstan pa la skyon byung ba bsal ba dang /
NK133(po)002:774: sing+g+ha la'i yul du byon nas /
NK133(po)002:775: rgyal po sing+ha ko sha 'khor bcas 'bras bu la
NK133(po)002:776: bkod nas yul phyogs der gtsug lag khang dang dge
NK133(po)002:778: nub phyogs b+ha mu gtsang skya bseng gi rigs mthong
NK133(po)002:779: ba'i bu legs mthong zhes pa dgra bcom pa su
NK133(po)002:780: k+aa y+aa na'i slob mar gyur pa de la bstan
NK133(po)002:781: pa gtad nas byang phyogs ku sha'i tshal du mya
NK133(po)002:784: nub phyogs sin+d+hu'i yul du gnod sbyin mo seng+g+ha l+ai
NK133(po)002:785: ts+ai sogs bstan pa la ma dad pa'i klu dang
NK133(po)002:786: gnod sbyin lnga brgya tsam btul nas sangs rgyas kyi
NK133(po)002:787: bstan pa rgya cher spel bar mdzad do //
NK133(po)002:788: skabs 'di tsam na rgya nag gi yul du'ang bstan pa'i mgo tshugs par grags te /
NK133(po)002:789: de yan chad la bstan pa'i gtad rab bdun zhes bshad do //
NK133(po)002:790: 'di'i tshe rgyal po d+harma a shwa ka rgyal srid byed pa las de'i bu ku na la'i mig /
NK133(po)002:794: ka nish+ka'i bar gyi rgyal rabs bzhi la dge slong
NK133(po)002:795: lha chen sogs kyis rtsod pa spel ba'i rgyus dge
NK133(po)002:797: nyan thos rtsa ba'i sde bzhi nas rim par bco brgyad kyi bar du gyes so //
NK133(po)002:798: de'i tshe dgra bcom pa rtsibs log dang /
NK133(po)002:799: ba su mi tra sogs kyis gyes pa bco brgyad
NK133(po)002:800: sangs rgyas kyi bkang bsgrubs te bka' bsdu gsum pa'i
NK133(po)002:801: dus so // theg chen pha rol du phyin pa'i
NK133(po)002:802: sde snod rnams ni lha klu gnod sbyin sogs kyi
NK133(po)002:803: yul du rgya cher 'phel zhing mi yul gzhan du
NK133(po)002:804: khol bur spyod pa las yul dbus su cher ma
NK133(po)002:805: dus so // dar kyang / dus 'di tsam na
NK133(po)002:806: yul e ti bi shar rgyal po bla srung zhes
NK133(po)002:807: pa'i khyim du 'phags pa 'jam dpal gyi sprul pa'i
NK133(po)002:808: dge slong zhig gis brgyad stong pa'i glegs bam zhig
NK133(po)002:809: bzhag ste song ba nas bzung /
NK133(po)002:810: theg chen dar ba'i dbu brtsam pa yin zhing /
NK133(po)002:811: rim bzhin byang chub sems dpa' byams pa dang /
NK133(po)002:812: 'jam dpal sogs las dngos su chos gsan pa'i pan+di ta mang du byon nas /
NK133(po)002:813: dkon mchog brtsegs pa dang lang kar gshegs pa sogs
NK133(po)002:814: theg chen gyi sde snod phal che ba mi yul
NK133(po)002:816: de nas ring por ma lon par sangs rgyas nyid
NK133(po)002:817: kyis bka'i dgongs 'grel mdzad pa por lung bstan pa'i
NK133(po)002:818: shing rta chen po rnam gnyis byon nas theg pa
NK133(po)002:819: chen po dar rgyas su mdzad tshul ni /
NK133(po)002:820: lang kar gshegs pa'i mdo las /
NK133(po)002:821: lho phyogs be da'i yul du ni //
NK133(po)002:822: dge slong dpal ldan cher grags pa //
NK133(po)002:823: de ming klu zhes 'bod pa ste //
NK133(po)002:824: yod dang med pa'i phyogs 'jig pa //
NK133(po)002:825: nga yi theg pa 'jig rten du //
NK133(po)002:826: bla med theg par rab bshad nas //
NK133(po)002:827: rab tu dga' ba'i sa bsgrubs te //
NK133(po)002:830: sangs rgyas mya ngan las 'das nas lo bzhi brgya
NK133(po)002:831: lon pa na dpal mgon 'phags pa klu sgrub zhabs
NK133(po)002:832: kyis / rgyas pa 'bum klu yul nas spyan 'dren pa dang /
NK133(po)002:833: bka' dang po'i dgongs 'grel du gtam tshogs /
NK133(po)002:834: bar ba'i dgongs 'grel du rigs tshogs /
NK133(po)002:835: tha ma'i dgongs 'grel du bstod tshogs sogs mdzad nas
NK133(po)002:836: zab mo dbu ma'i lam gyi srol phye bar mdzad
NK133(po)002:837: do // slob dpon thogs med ni /
NK133(po)002:839: thogs med ces bya'i dge slong ni //
NK133(po)002:840: bstan bcos de ni don la mkhas //
NK133(po)002:841: mdo sde nges don drang ba'i don //
NK133(po)002:842: rnam pa mang po'ang rab tu 'byed //
NK133(po)002:844: thogs med sku mched byon te /
NK133(po)002:845: thogs med zhabs kyis rje btsun ma pham pa las byams chos lnga dngos su gsan zhing /
NK133(po)002:848: gcung dbyig gnyen gyis rab tu byed pa brgyad sogs
NK133(po)002:849: brtsams pa rnams la byams pa dang 'brel ba'i chos
NK133(po)002:851: rnal 'byor spyod pa sems tsam pa'i gzhung 'byed par mdzad do //
NK133(po)002:852: gzhan yang slob dpon klu sgrub kyi rjes su 'brang nas zab mo dbu ma'i srol 'dzin /
NK133(po)002:855: zla ba grags pa sogs dang /
NK133(po)002:856: thogs med yab sras kyi rjes su 'brang nas /
NK133(po)002:858: phyogs kyi glang po chos kyi grags pa /
NK133(po)002:860: mkhas shing grub pa'i khyu mchog chen po rtsod pa
NK133(po)002:861: dang bral ba rnams kyis bshad sgrub las kyi 'khor
NK133(po)002:862: lo gsum gyis rgyal ba'i bstan pa la mdzad pa
NK133(po)002:863: ji ltar bgyis pa rnams rgya cher gzhan las shes
NK133(po)002:864: par bya'o // gsang chen bla na med pa'i rgyud
NK133(po)002:865: sde gtso bor gyur pa'i rig pa 'dzin pa sngags
NK133(po)002:867: ston pas 'og min du gsungs nas nyid las mi gzhan pa'i rgyal sras rigs gsum sems dpa' dang /
NK133(po)002:869: phyi rabs kyi gang zag chos kyi spyan ldan rnams
NK133(po)002:870: dang bcas pa la bstan pa mi nub pa'i btsas
NK133(po)002:871: su rgyud gtad par mdzad pa yin te /
NK133(po)002:872: glang chen rab 'bog gi rtog pa dum bu'i rgyud las /
NK133(po)002:873: sku gsung thugs kyi sprul pa rigs gsum mgon //
NK133(po)002:874: de la gtad pas khams gsum sgron me yin //
NK133(po)002:875: rigs lnga 'khor gyi mkha' 'gro sde bzhi rnams //
NK133(po)002:876: de la gtad pas gsang sngags srung ma yin //
NK133(po)002:877: sngon sbyangs gang zag chos kyi spyan ldan rnams //
NK133(po)002:878: de la gtad pas bstan pa dar ba yin //
NK133(po)002:880: de las rgyal sras rigs gsum sems dpas thog mar
NK133(po)002:881: lha klu gnod sbyin gyi gnas so sor gsang sngags
NK133(po)002:882: kyi bstan pa ji ltar spel tshul ni /
NK133(po)002:883: mkhyen rab kyi dbang phyug 'jam dpal gzhon nu mdzes pa'i sku dang ldan pa de nyid kyis /
NK133(po)002:884: lha rnams kyi lus dang bsam pa dang mthun par lha grags ldan mchog skyongs la bshad /
NK133(po)002:887: tshangs pa skye dgu'i bdag po /
NK133(po)002:890: lha'i dbang po brgya byin rnams la brgyud nas /
NK133(po)002:891: tshom bu 'bum dang bcas pas mchog gi dngos grub brnyes te /
NK133(po)002:892: lha yul du bstan pa dar bar gyur to //
NK133(po)002:893: byams brtse'i mnga' bdag spyan ras gzigs bdud rtsi sman gyi sku dang ldan pa des /
NK133(po)002:894: klu rnams kyi lus dang bsam pa dang mthun par klu rgyal mgrin pa nag po la bshad /
NK133(po)002:899: klu rgyal 'jog po rnams la bshad de tshom bu
NK133(po)002:900: 'bum dang bcas par rig pa 'dzin pa'i sar bkod
NK133(po)002:901: nas klu'i yul du bstan pa dar bar mdzad do
NK133(po)002:902: // mthu stobs kyi bdag po phyag na rdo rje 'jig tshul bsdigs pa'i sku dang ldan pa des /
NK133(po)002:903: gnod sbyin rnams kyi lus dang bsam pa dang mthun par gnod sbyin kun tu bzang po la bshad /
NK133(po)002:905: gnod sbyin lag na rdo rje dang /
NK133(po)002:906: skar mda' gdong sogs las brgyud nas tshom bu 'bum
NK133(po)002:907: dang bcas pa rdo rje 'chang gi sar gshegs te
NK133(po)002:908: / gnod sbyin gyi yul du bstan pa rgyas par mdzad do //
NK133(po)002:909: de nas bstan pa de nyid mi'i yul du yongs su grags par ji ltar byung tshul ni /
NK133(po)002:910: mdo dgongs pa lung ston las /
NK133(po)002:911: rgyu la mos par rgyu'i chos kyi //
NK133(po)002:912: 'khor lo rab tu bskor byas nas //
NK133(po)002:913: rdo rje theg pa'i nye lam zhig /
NK133(po)002:915: zhes ma 'ongs pa'i dus na 'bras bu rdo rje'i theg pa 'byung ba spyir lung bstan cing /
NK133(po)002:916: bye brag du dus ci tsam na gang zag gang
NK133(po)002:917: la gnas gang du tshul ji ltar snang ba yang
NK133(po)002:919: nga ni 'di nas mi snang nas //
NK133(po)002:920: lo ni brgyad dang bcu gnyis na //
NK133(po)002:921: lha gnas gsum du grags pa yi //
NK133(po)002:922: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /'dzam gling shar gyi phyogs mtshams kyi //
NK133(po)002:923: mi las rig can skal ldan de //
NK133(po)002:924: rgyal po dza zhes bya ba la //
NK133(po)002:925: sngon du ltas snang snang gyur te //
NK133(po)002:926: drag shul can zhes bya ba'i rtser //
NK133(po)002:927: grogs kyi sems dpa' dman pa'i lus //
NK133(po)002:928: lang ka'i bdag po la sogs la //
NK133(po)002:929: lag na rdo rjes snang bar 'gyur //
NK133(po)002:931: ston pa mchog gi sprul pa'i sku mya ngan las 'das nas lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad na /
NK133(po)002:935: srin po blo gros thabs ldan /
NK133(po)002:936: mi'i rig 'dzin li tsa b+ai dri med grags pa ste /
NK133(po)002:937: dam pa'i rigs can dra ma lnga po rang rang
NK133(po)002:938: gi gnas su nang du yang dag 'jog pa la
NK133(po)002:939: zhugs pa las langs pa dang 'jig rten mun pa
NK133(po)002:940: lta bur gyur pa mthong nas ston pa mya ngan
NK133(po)002:942: gang du 'du ba'i gnas ni ji skad du /
NK133(po)002:943: rtse na rtsal gyi rgyal po gnas //
NK133(po)002:944: ngos la brag dkar khyi tshugs pa //
NK133(po)002:946: rtsi sman rtsa brgyad rtsa bar 'khrungs //
NK133(po)002:947: 'du ba'i nad kyis yongs mi tshugs //
NK133(po)002:948: spyi bor ka lan+ta ka ni //
NK133(po)002:949: mi gnyis gcig pur gnas pa yi //
NK133(po)002:950: mdzod ldan de yi tshang bcas pa //
NK133(po)002:951: skal ldan rnams kyis bgrod par sla //
NK133(po)002:952: skal med rnams kyis yongs mi thar //
NK133(po)002:953: zhes pa'i mtshan nyid rnams dang ldan pa'i lang+ka'i yul
NK133(po)002:954: gyi ri bo drag shul can nam gnam lcags yod
NK133(po)002:955: pa'i rtse mor rang rang gi rdzu 'phrul gyi bya
NK133(po)002:956: bas gshegs te / kye ma'o kye hud 'jig rten klong //
NK133(po)002:957: ston pa'i sgron me'i 'od nub na //
NK133(po)002:958: 'jig rten mun pa gang gis sel //
NK133(po)002:959: zhes pa la sogs pa'i gdung tshig nyer gsum bton pas /
NK133(po)002:960: gsang ba'i bdag po dngos su byon nas /
NK133(po)002:961: dam pa'i rig can dra ma lnga sogs rig 'dzin 'dus pa phal mo che la /
NK133(po)002:962: sngar 'og min sogs su bstan pa'i gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde rnams slar yang bzlas te gsungs so //
NK133(po)002:963: de rnams srin po blo gros thabs ldan gyis rin
NK133(po)002:964: po che gser gyi glegs bu la bee d+aur+ya'i zhun
NK133(po)002:965: mas yi ger bris nas dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin
NK133(po)002:966: gyi rtsal gyis / mi zad pa'i gter nam mkha'i mdzod du rgya bdun gyis btabs so //
NK133(po)002:967: de'i tshe de'i byin rlabs kyis sa ho ra'i rgyal
NK133(po)002:968: po dza la rmi ltas ngo mtshar ba bdun byung
NK133(po)002:969: ba ni / sku gsung thugs rtags thim pa dang //
NK133(po)002:970: rin chen glegs bam babs pa dang //
NK133(po)002:971: chos kyi bgro ba byed pa dang //
NK133(po)002:972: kun gyis dam par bsgrags pa dang //
NK133(po)002:973: mchod pa chen po byas pa dang //
NK133(po)002:974: rin chen char du babs pa dang //
NK133(po)002:975: sangs rgyas sa la lung bstan pa'o //
NK133(po)002:977: rmi ltas dang mthun par rgyal po'i khang steng du badz+ra p+aa ni'i sku khru gang ba zhig dang /
NK133(po)002:978: sarba bud+d+ha sa ma yo ga sogs rgyud sde chen
NK133(po)002:979: po rnams kyi glegs bam mang po babs par gyur
NK133(po)002:980: to // de nas glegs bam rnams la rgyal pos brtags pas don ma shes nas /
NK133(po)002:981: 'jig rten na 'di'i brda' mjal ba su yod ces bsgrags pa na /
NK133(po)002:982: za hor gyi rgyal po u pa r+aa dza zhes
NK133(po)002:983: bya ba mkhyen rab che bar gsan nas de la
NK133(po)002:984: bstan pas kyang don dang brda' ma mjal /
NK133(po)002:985: de nas slob dpon ku ku r+aa dza la bstan pas /
NK133(po)002:986: de'i rdor sems zhal mthong gi le'u rtogs te bsgrub
NK133(po)002:987: pas rdo rje sems pa'i zhal bstan nas rgyud kyi
NK133(po)002:988: don rnams rgyal po nyid la gsang ba'i bdag pos
NK133(po)002:989: ston par 'gyur ro zhes lung bstan pa ltar /
NK133(po)002:991: de nas rgyal po nyid kyis rdo rje sems dpa'
NK133(po)002:992: zhal mthong gi le'u dang badz+ra p+aa ni'i sku la
NK133(po)002:993: brten nas sgrub pa mdzad cing gsol ba btabs pas
NK133(po)002:994: / rdo rje sems dpa'i zhal gzigs nas /
NK133(po)002:995: khyod kyi ston pa ni gsang ba'i bdag po yin gyis /
NK133(po)002:996: des ston par 'gyur ro zhes gsungs pa thos nas
NK133(po)002:997: dga' ba cher skyes te sgrub pa la brtson pas
NK133(po)002:998: / re zhig na gsang ba'i bdag po mngon sum du byon nas /
NK133(po)002:999: theg pa thams cad rdzogs pa'i dbang bskur zhing rgyud kyi don rnams bstan nas /
NK133(po)002:1000: tshig gi bstan pa li tsa bi dri med grags
NK133(po)002:1001: pa la zhus shig ces lung bstan pa ltar gsan
NK133(po)002:1002: zhing / gsang bdag gi bka' ltar rgyud sde chen po bco brgyad du so sor phyes nas /
NK133(po)002:1003: slob dpon ku ku r+aa dza la bshad /
NK133(po)002:1004: des in+d+ra bo d+hi la bshad /
NK133(po)002:1006: des u pa r+aa dza la /
NK133(po)002:1007: des sras mo go ma d+ae wi la bshad cing
NK133(po)002:1008: so so'i tshom bu dang bcas pa rdo rje 'chang
NK133(po)002:1011: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i lam rim las /
NK133(po)002:1012: gsang ba'i bdag po mngon gshegs nas //
NK133(po)002:1013: lha klu gnod sbyin srin po dang //
NK133(po)002:1014: mi las skal ldan 'dus pa la //
NK133(po)002:1015: dbang pos ji ltar lung bstan dus //
NK133(po)002:1016: rgyal bu rig can ltas shar ba //
NK133(po)002:1017: 'brel pas snang ba mngon rtogs pas //
NK133(po)002:1018: thugs kyi sgrub pa mngon rtogs te //
NK133(po)002:1019: de nyid sgo nas de nyid bsgrubs //
NK133(po)002:1020: bstan pa'i dngos grub de nas thob //
NK133(po)002:1021: don dam bcud kyis de nas rgyas //
NK133(po)002:1023: smon pa'i lha dang de ru mjal //
NK133(po)002:1024: de nas rdo rje gdan steng gi //
NK133(po)002:1025: 'dzam gling shar gyi phyogs mtshams su //
NK133(po)002:1026: pho brang rin chen dam pa der //
NK133(po)002:1027: bkra shis pa yi khang pa ru //
NK133(po)002:1028: ku ku r+aa dza in+d+ra bo d+hi dang //
NK133(po)002:1029: sing+ha u pa r+aa dza dang //
NK133(po)002:1030: sras mo go ma d+ae la sogs //
NK133(po)002:1031: sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i dbang thob nas //
NK133(po)002:1032: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mngon bsgrubs te //
NK133(po)002:1033: rdo rje 'chang sar mngon du gshegs //
NK133(po)002:1037: sprul pa'i sku 'das phyi ma'i dus kyi tshe //
NK133(po)002:1038: rgyal ba'i bka' gsang 'dzam gling gnas su shar //
NK133(po)002:1039: rgyal po'i khab tu spyan rabs mchod byas te //
NK133(po)002:1040: dga' zhing gus bstod legs bltas brda' ma mjal //
NK133(po)002:1041: thugs rje'i 'brel shugs gsang sngags 'dzin par grags //
NK133(po)002:1042: dam par bzung nas glegs bam gzigs par zhus //
NK133(po)002:1043: sgyu 'phrul thig le stong pa'i dkyil 'khor gzhung //
NK133(po)002:1044: grub thob lhag pa'i lha yis lung bstan mdzad //
NK133(po)002:1045: rdo rje theg pa'i gzhung lugs sna tshogs mtha' //
NK133(po)002:1046: dam pa rnams kyis gdams pa ji bzhin pa //
NK133(po)002:1047: mi 'gal legs par bsdus shing rab dkrol te //
NK133(po)002:1048: 'grel dang bsdus don sgrub thabs mang du bstan //
NK133(po)002:1050: de nas sras mo go ma d+ae wis ku ku r+aa dza phyi ma la bshad /
NK133(po)002:1053: sangs rgyas gsang ba gsum sogs la bshad pa nas rgya cher 'phel lo /
NK133(po)002:1054: 'di dang dus mnyam du a nu yo ga'i rgyud rnams sing+ga la'i nags tshal du babs pa dang /
NK133(po)002:1055: kri ya'i rgyud rnams w+aa ra na si /
NK133(po)002:1056: yo ga rnams me ri 'bar ba'i rtse mor babs par bshad /
NK133(po)002:1057: gsang chen a ti yo ga'i rgyud sde rnams ni /
NK133(po)002:1058: lha'i bu kun dga' snying po zhes bya ba de nyid /
NK133(po)002:1059: nub phyogs o rgyan gyi yul du /
NK133(po)002:1060: rgyal po u pa r+aa dza'i sras mo su d+harma
NK133(po)002:1061: zhes bya ba'i sras su 'khrungs pa sprul pa'i sku
NK133(po)002:1063: 'og min du rdo rje sems dpa' las rang bzhin
NK133(po)002:1064: rdzogs pa chen po'i chos rnams mngon sum du gsan
NK133(po)002:1065: nas slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen sogs la bstan
NK133(po)002:1066: pa nas bzung rim par dar ro //
NK133(po)002:1067: 'di dag ni gtso bor snga 'gyur gyi phyogs su grags che ba tsam zhig brjod pa yin gyis /
NK133(po)002:1068: gzhan du na o rgyan gyi yul dang sham b+ha la sogs nas grub pa brnyes pa'i skyes bu /
NK133(po)002:1071: mtsho skyes zhabs sogs kyis blangs nas dar ba sogs
NK133(po)002:1072: gsang sngags kyi byung tshul ni mtha' yas par yod
NK133(po)002:1073: pas mtha' gcig tu 'chad par mi nus so //
NK133(po)002:1074: gsum pa bod gangs can gyi ljongs 'dir mdo sngags kyi bstan pa dar tshul ni /
NK133(po)002:1075: bod kyi rgyal po'i thog ma gnya' khri btsan po nas bzung rgyal rabs nyer drug 'das pa /
NK133(po)002:1076: lha tho ri snyan shal gyi sku ring la bod
NK133(po)002:1077: du chos dar ba'i snga ltas su dpang skong phyag
NK133(po)002:1078: rgya pa dang mdo sde za ma tog sogs pho
NK133(po)002:1079: brang yul bu bla mkhar gyi steng du babs pa
NK133(po)002:1080: nas dam pa chos kyi dbu brnyes /
NK133(po)002:1081: chos rgyal srong btsan sgam po'i sku ring la /
NK133(po)002:1082: ra sa 'phrul snang sogs mtha' 'dul gyi gtsug lag khang mang du bzhengs /
NK133(po)002:1083: rten gyi gtso bo jo sh+aaka rnam gnyis spyan drangs /
NK133(po)002:1084: lo ts+aa ba thon mi sam b+ho ta rgya gar du bardzangasa nas /
NK133(po)002:1085: yig rigs dang sgra sbyor la phul du phyin par bslabs te /
NK133(po)002:1086: bod yig gi srol btod cing sum cu pa dang
NK133(po)002:1087: rtags kyi 'jug pa sogs brda' sbyor gyi bstan bcos
NK133(po)002:1088: kyang mdzad / mdo sde dkon mchog sprin dang /
NK133(po)002:1089: za ma tog sogs theg pa chen po'i sde snod
NK133(po)002:1090: mang du bsgyur nas dam pa'i chos kyi srol btod
NK133(po)002:1091: / khyad par du 'phags pa 'jam pa'i dbyangs kyi
NK133(po)002:1092: sprul pa chos skyongs pa'i rgyal po btsad po khri
NK133(po)002:1093: srong lde'u btsan gyi ring la /
NK133(po)002:1094: za hor gyi mkhan po zhi ba 'tsho dang /
NK133(po)002:1095: o rgyan gyi slob dpon sangs rgyas gnyis pa pad+ma sam b+ha wa spyan drangs /
NK133(po)002:1096: slob dpon chen pos bod kyi lha 'dre mthu bo
NK133(po)002:1097: che rnams dam 'og tu bcug nas sa gzhi byin
NK133(po)002:1098: gyis rlabs / zan yangs mi 'gyur lhun gyis grub
NK133(po)002:1099: pa'i gtsug lag khang bzhengs nas rab tu gnas par
NK133(po)002:1100: gyis rlabs / mdzad / mkhan chen zhi ba 'tshos /
NK133(po)002:1103: pa gor bee ro ts+aa na /
NK133(po)002:1104: ngan lam rgyal ba mchog dbyangs /
NK133(po)002:1107: la sum rgyal ba byang chub bdun thog mar rab tu phyungs nas bsnyen par rdzogs te /
NK133(po)002:1108: mtshan dpal dbyangs dang ye shes dbang po sogs su
NK133(po)002:1109: btags pa la 'dul 'dzin sad mi bdun zhes grags
NK133(po)002:1111: de nas gzhan yang rgya gar 'phags pa'i yul nas /
NK133(po)002:1112: slob dpon chen po sh+aan+tim gar+b+ha /
NK133(po)002:1120: bi ma mi tra sogs pan chen brgya dang rtsa brgyad spyan drangs /
NK133(po)002:1121: lo ts+aa ba ska lcog zhang gsum /
NK133(po)002:1123: gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra sogs kyis sgra bsgyur
NK133(po)002:1124: nas rgyu dang 'bras bu'i theg pa mtha' dag gi
NK133(po)002:1125: bka' dang bstan bcos thams cad bod du dar bar
NK133(po)002:1126: mdzad do // dus de tsam na dpal gyi bsam
NK133(po)002:1127: yas sogs chos 'khor gsum du klog pa thos bsam
NK133(po)002:1128: gyi 'khor lo gtso bor bzung nas sde snod gsum
NK133(po)002:1129: dang rgyud sde drug bcas lung gi bstan pa mtha'
NK133(po)002:1130: dag bshad nyan gyi sgo nas 'dzin skyong spel bar
NK133(po)002:1131: mdzad do // mdzad cing / 'chims phu sogs sgrub
NK133(po)002:1132: gnas gsum du spong ba bsam gtan gyi 'khor lo
NK133(po)002:1133: gtso bor bzung nas rtogs pa'i bstan pa sgrub pa'i
NK133(po)002:1135: gangs can gyi ljongs 'dir rgyal ba'i lung rtogs kyi
NK133(po)002:1136: bstan pa rin po che nyin mor byed pa'i dpal
NK133(po)002:1137: ltar 'bar zhing / mkhas shing grub pa brnyes pa'i
NK133(po)002:1138: bstan 'dzin gyi skyes bu rnams kyis kyang sa chen
NK133(po)002:1139: po'i khyon kun tu khyab par gyur to //
NK133(po)002:1140: de nas lha sras mu tig btsan po dang /
NK133(po)002:1141: mnga' bdag ral pa can gnyis kyi ring la yang /
NK133(po)002:1142: yab mes kyi srol bzung nas sngar gyi 'gyur 'phro rnams bsgyur ba dang /
NK133(po)002:1143: 'gyur zin pa rnams zhus dag bgyis nas bkas bcad
NK133(po)002:1144: kyis gtan la phabs pa sogs rgyal ba'i bstan pa
NK133(po)002:1145: la rma med pa'i mdzad pa bla lhag tu bgyis
NK133(po)002:1146: so // de ltar rgyal po tho ri gnyan shal nas bzung /
NK133(po)002:1147: mnga' bdag ral pa can gyi bar la skyid pa'i gdung rab bcu gsum zhes zer zhing /
NK133(po)002:1149: pan+di ta lha rig pa'i seng ge dang /
NK133(po)002:1150: lo ts+aa ba thon mi sam b+ho ta nas pan chen smri ti dang /
NK133(po)002:1151: lo ts+aa ba chos kyi bzang po'i bar du byon
NK133(po)002:1152: pa rnams kyis bsgyur cing bshad pa rnams la snga
NK133(po)002:1155: zhal nas gsungs pa'i bka' ma /
NK133(po)002:1156: rjes su gnang ba'i gter ma /
NK133(po)002:1157: byin gyis brlabs pa'i dag snang ma zhes brgyud pa'i srol ka chen po gsum du yod pa las /
NK133(po)002:1158: dang po'i phyogs la'ang rgyud sde dang sgrub sde bsam
NK133(po)002:1159: gyis mi khyab pa zhig mchis pa'i nang nas gtso
NK133(po)002:1160: bor gyur pa ni mdo sgyu sems gsum yin zhing
NK133(po)002:1161: / de dag gi brgyud pa'i babs lugs kyang /
NK133(po)002:1162: sgyu 'phrul sogs ma h+aa yo ga'i skor rnams ni /
NK133(po)002:1165: sangs rgyas gsang ba sogs nas /
NK133(po)002:1166: gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku ma dang /
NK133(po)002:1167: sog po dpal gyi ye shes sogs las brgyud nas gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes la bababasa so //
NK133(po)002:1168: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga sems phyogs kyi skor rnams kyang slob dpon sh+ri seng+ha las /
NK133(po)002:1169: lo ts+aa ba bee ro tsa nas gsan te /
NK133(po)002:1170: chos rgyal khri srong lde'u btsan dang /
NK133(po)002:1171: rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying po /
NK133(po)002:1172: spang mi pham mgon po gsum la bshad /
NK133(po)002:1173: bee ro dang g.yu sgra gnyis ka la gnyags kyis gsan nas /
NK133(po)002:1174: rim par gnubs la babs so //
NK133(po)002:1175: mdo dgongs pa 'dus pa sogs a nu yo ga'i skor rnams ni /
NK133(po)002:1176: bal po'i slob dpon ba su d+ha ra dang /
NK133(po)002:1177: bru sha'i slob dpon che btsan skyes sogs las gnubs chen nyid kyis gsan no //
NK133(po)002:1178: de ltar na bskyed rdzogs rdzogs chen gsum gyi bka'
NK133(po)002:1179: yi chu bo gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes la
NK133(po)002:1180: babs so // de la so ye shes dbang phyug sogs thugs kyi sras bzhi /
NK133(po)002:1181: sras kyi dam pa khu lung ba yon tan rgya mtsho dang lnga sogs yod pa las /
NK133(po)002:1182: yon tan rgya mtsho dang so ye shes dbang phyug
NK133(po)002:1183: gnyis las rim par brgyud de zur la babs so
NK133(po)002:1184: // zur po che sh+aakya 'byung gnas la slob ma /
NK133(po)002:1185: rtse mo bzhi rtse lkog dang lnga /
NK133(po)002:1186: sgom chen brgya dang rtsa brgyad la sogs par byung
NK133(po)002:1187: zhing de'i nang nas lta dgongs kyi rtse mo zur
NK133(po)002:1188: chung shes rab grags pa la /
NK133(po)002:1190: gdung brgyad sogs mang du byon /
NK133(po)002:1191: khyad par sku'i sras gsang bdag sgro phug pa sh+aakya seng ge la slob ma /
NK133(po)002:1194: mes bzhi ste bcu gnyis sogs shin tu mang bar byung ngo //
NK133(po)002:1195: de ltar zur pa mes dbon gsum gyi bka' drin
NK133(po)002:1196: las khams dbus kun tu snga 'gyur mdo sgyu sems
NK133(po)002:1197: gsum sogs kyi srol ka shin tu rgyas par gyur
NK133(po)002:1198: to // gzhan yang bar skabs rnams su gsar rnying
NK133(po)002:1199: mkhas grub thams cad kyi gtsug gi nor bu lta
NK133(po)002:1200: bur gyur pa zla med pa'i mkhas pa chen po
NK133(po)002:1201: rong zom chos kyi bzang po dang /
NK133(po)002:1205: lo chen d+harma sh+ri sogs rim par byon pa rnams
NK133(po)002:1206: kyis kyang rmad du byung ba'i snying stobs chen pos
NK133(po)002:1207: / 'chad rtsod rtsom pa'i khur bdag gir bzhes nas /
NK133(po)002:1208: rgyal ba'i bstan pa spyi dang /
NK133(po)002:1209: khyad par nang rgyud sde gsum sogs kyi brgyud pa'i srog mthud par mdzad pas /
NK133(po)002:1210: deng sang gi skabs 'dir chos 'di dag la cung
NK133(po)002:1211: zad tsam spyod du yod pa ni dam pa 'di
NK133(po)002:1212: rnams kyi bka' drin kho na las yin par shes
NK133(po)002:1213: par bya'o // de dag gis bstan pa'i babs tshul mdo tsam song nas /
NK133(po)002:1214: skabs 'dir theg dgu'i lam rim ltar gyi so byang
NK133(po)002:1215: sngags gsum so so'i bla ma brgyud pa'i rnam thar
NK133(po)002:1216: go rim ltar chu babs su 'god pa ra 'os
NK133(po)002:1217: kyang de ltar bkod tshe yi ge'i spom shin tu
NK133(po)002:1218: mang bar 'gyur gyis dog sa nas rgyas spros dor
NK133(po)002:1219: te sa bcad tsam zhig tu rags pa bsdu ba'i
NK133(po)002:1220: dbang du byas na gsum las /
NK133(po)002:1221: thog mar bstan pa'i gzhi ma 'dul ba so thar gyi sdom rgyun la /
NK133(po)002:1222: deng sang yod pa kha che lugs dang /
NK133(po)002:1224: 'dir phyi ma snga 'gyur lugs kyi brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)002:1225: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas /
NK133(po)002:1236: bla chen dgongs pa rab gsal /
NK133(po)002:1237: klu mes tshul khrims shes rab sogs nas rim par brgyud de /
NK133(po)002:1238: bdag cag gi mkhan po don gyi slad du mtshan nas smos te /
NK133(po)002:1239: thub bstan pad+ma rgyas pa'i nyin byed dpal bzang po'i zhal snga nas kyi bar du byon pa'o //
NK133(po)002:1240: gnyis pa theg chen sems bskyed kyi brgyud pa la lugs gsum las /
NK133(po)002:1241: zab mo lta ba'i brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)002:1245: zla ba grags pa sogs dang /
NK133(po)002:1246: rgya chen spyod pa'i brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)002:1250: mkhas mchog dbyig gnyen sogs dang /
NK133(po)002:1251: zab dang rgya che'i brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)002:1253: e la d+ha ri sogs te /
NK133(po)002:1254: de ltar brgyud tshul gsum kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal po klong chen pa la babs shing /
NK133(po)002:1256: rje bla ma rgyal ba'i sras po gzhan phan mtha' yas 'od zer gyi bar du'o //
NK133(po)002:1257: gsum pa gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i smin grol lam gyi brgyud pa la'ang /
NK133(po)002:1258: rgyud sde bzhi'am drug las bya ba'i rgyud du bzhag pa la /
NK133(po)002:1259: khri srong lde'u btsan nas bzung bod kyi rgyal po rnams kyi thugs dam du basngagasa pa /
NK133(po)002:1260: bder gshegs sman lha brgyad kyi cho ga'i brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)002:1261: mnyam med thub pa chen po nas /
NK133(po)002:1265: rgyal sras sad na legs sogs dang /
NK133(po)002:1267: 'phags pa gtsug tor dri ma med pa lha lnga'i cho ga gnyis kyang /
NK133(po)002:1268: chos rgyal yan gong ltar la de nas mu ne btsad po /
NK133(po)002:1270: lha sras gtsang ma sogs nas rim par rje bla ma'i bar du'o //
NK133(po)002:1271: spyod rgyud phyag na rdo rje dbang bskur dang /
NK133(po)002:1272: rnal 'byor gyi rgyud de nyid snang ba dag gi
NK133(po)002:1273: brgyud pa ni 'dus mdo'i skabs su gsal ba ltar
NK133(po)002:1274: ro // rnal 'byor bla na med pa'i rgyud sde la'ang gsum las /
NK133(po)002:1275: dang po ma h+aa yo ga'i skor la /
NK133(po)002:1276: sku'i rgyud dpal sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam par sbyor ba mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde mchog ni /
NK133(po)002:1277: dpal kun tu bzang po nas /
NK133(po)002:1280: li ts+aa bi dri med grags pa /
NK133(po)002:1284: mu di ta sogs nas rje bla ma'i bar du'o //
NK133(po)002:1285: gshin rje rol ba'i rgyud las /
NK133(po)002:1286: 'jam dpal ma ru tse dmar po dang kha thun nag po sogs kyis skor ni /
NK133(po)002:1287: khyab bdag rdo rje 'chang chen po nas /
NK133(po)002:1291: de nas bka' babs gsum gyi brgyud pa so sor
NK133(po)002:1292: 'dren tshul mi 'dra tsam yod pa gang ltar kyang
NK133(po)002:1293: gnubs chen yab sras las rim par brgyud de rje
NK133(po)002:1294: bla ma la'o // dpal he ru ka rol ba'i rgyud las /
NK133(po)002:1295: yang dag zla gam dgu ba'i skor ni /
NK133(po)002:1296: ston pa kun tu bzang po nas /
NK133(po)002:1297: rdo rje sems dpa' dga' rab rdo rje /
NK133(po)002:1303: nam mkha'i snying po sogs las rim par brgyud de rje bla ma la'o //
NK133(po)002:1304: phur pa rol ba'i rgyud las /
NK133(po)002:1308: sna nam lugs sogs mang du yod pa'i brgyud pa ci rigs 'dres pa'i gnad bsdus /
NK133(po)002:1309: phur pa rog lugs su grags pa /
NK133(po)002:1310: kun tu bzang po nas karma he ru ka /
NK133(po)002:1314: dpal gyi dbang phyug sogs las brgyud pa dang /
NK133(po)002:1315: rong zom lugs kyi phur pa kun bzang nas /
NK133(po)002:1322: sna nam rdo rje bdud 'joms sogs las brgyud pa
NK133(po)002:1323: ste gnyis ka'ang rim gyis rje bla ma dam pa
NK133(po)002:1324: la'o // spyi rgyud sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i skor rnams ni /
NK133(po)002:1328: dam pa'i rigs can dra ma lnga /
NK133(po)002:1329: rgyal po dzah ku ku r+aa dza /
NK133(po)002:1331: sing+ha r+aa dza sogs nas rje bla ma la'o //
NK133(po)002:1333: sgyu 'phrul gyi cha lag tu gtogs pa slob dpon
NK133(po)002:1334: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i lugs kyi tshe sgrub skor ni
NK133(po)002:1344: bi ma la sogs nas rje bla ma la'o //
NK133(po)002:1345: rnal 'byor spyi khrus na rag dong sprug gi skor ni /
NK133(po)002:1350: sh+aakya pu tri sogs nas rim par rje bla ma la'o //
NK133(po)002:1351: drag dmar bka' ma 'o bran lugs ni /
NK133(po)002:1360: ri rab brtan pa ste 'o bran bdun brgyud /
NK133(po)002:1362: nyi ma rgyal mtshan sogs nas rim par rje bla ma dam pa'i bar du'o //
NK133(po)002:1363: de dag gi bstan srung dregs pa'i skor la /
NK133(po)002:1364: mgon po legs ldan tshogs kyi bdag po'i skor ni /
NK133(po)002:1368: rgyal po dzah ku ku r+aa dza /
NK133(po)002:1373: gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes sogs nas rje bla ma'i bar du'o //
NK133(po)002:1374: mgon po stag zhon dang bing bka' gter zung 'jug gi brgyud pa ni /
NK133(po)002:1382: gnubs chen sogs nas rje bla ma'i bar du'o //
NK133(po)002:1383: lha mo re ti rang byung rgyal mo ni /
NK133(po)002:1388: skyi nag gyang 'gyel sogs nas brgyud pa bka' ma dang /
NK133(po)002:1390: gter ston pu rangs pa zhang btsun /
NK133(po)002:1391: khyung pa stag sham pa sogs nas brgyud pa gter
NK133(po)002:1392: ma ste lugs gnyis ka gang ltar yang gter chen
NK133(po)002:1393: nas rim bzhin rje bla ma'i bar du'o //
NK133(po)002:1394: rnam sras gsang sgrub drag po rta sngon can ni /
NK133(po)002:1398: gnubs chen sogs nas rje bla ma dam pa'i bar du'o //
NK133(po)002:1399: gnyis pa a nu yo ga las 'dus pa mdo'i skor ni /
NK133(po)002:1400: rgyal po dzahyana chad sgyu 'phrul gyi babs dang 'dra ba las /
NK133(po)002:1401: de nas u pa r+aa dza /
NK133(po)002:1406: ro langs bde ba sogs nas rim par rje bla ma la'o //
NK133(po)002:1407: bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi man ngag tu grags pa rgya
NK133(po)002:1408: bod mkhas pa mi bzhi'i dgongs bcud bka' brgyad bka'
NK133(po)002:1409: ma rdzongs 'phrang du grags pa'i skor ni /
NK133(po)002:1410: ston pa kun tu bzang po nas /
NK133(po)002:1416: gnubs chen yab sras sogs nas rim par brgyud de rje bla ma la'o //
NK133(po)002:1417: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga sems phyogs kyi skor las /
NK133(po)002:1418: sems sde ma bu bco brgyad sogs kyi dbang dang gdam khrid rnams ni /
NK133(po)002:1419: kun tu bzang po rdo rje sems dpa'/
NK133(po)002:1427: gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes sogs nas rim par
NK133(po)002:1428: brgyud de rje bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa chen
NK133(po)002:1429: po rig pa'i rdo rje bee ro tsa na rtsal
NK133(po)002:1431: bdag cag gi rigs kyi bdag po rje thams cad mkhyen pa 'di nyid la /
NK133(po)002:1432: snga 'gyur theg rim dgu'i brgyud pa thams cad gcig
NK133(po)002:1433: tu 'dus pas bstan pa yongs rdzogs kyi babs so
NK133(po)002:1434: bzhi bar gyur pa yin no //
NK133(po)002:1435: bka' ma theg rim dgu'i phrin chog rnams kyi dkar
NK133(po)002:1436: chag yid bzhin dbang gi rgyal po'i bang mdzod las
NK133(po)002:1437: / bstan pa rin po che spyi'i babs tshul lo rgyus su brjod pa'i skabs te dang po'o ////
NK133(po)002:1438: gnyis pa ji ltar spar du sgrub tshul bzhugs byang dkar chag dngos 'god pa la /
NK133(po)002:1439: gang gis spar du sgrub par mdzad pa po'i gang zag /
NK133(po)002:1441: de ltar bsgrubs pa'i zhal byang dang gsum las /
NK133(po)002:1443: spyir thun mong rig gnas dang bcas pa'i rang bzhin
NK133(po)002:1444: gyi grub mtha' rgya mtsho'i pha rol du son zhing
NK133(po)002:1445: theg pa mtha' dag gi don la dbang 'byor ba
NK133(po)002:1446: / khyad par du snga 'gyur bka' babs kyi chu bo rnam bzhi yongs su rdzogs shing /
NK133(po)002:1447: snyigs ma'i dus 'dir rgyal ba'i lung rtogs kyi bstan
NK133(po)002:1448: pa la sangs rgyas dngos kyi mdzad pa dang tha
NK133(po)002:1449: mi dad pa'i rje bdag nyid chen po 'di'i /
NK133(po)002:1450: phyi nang gsang ba'i rnam par thar pa mtha' dag
NK133(po)002:1451: brjod pa la ni 'phags chen rnams kyang ngal ba'i
NK133(po)002:1453: bdag cag byis pa'i skye bo blo gros sbrang bu'i
NK133(po)002:1454: gshog pa dang mtshungs pa dag gis ji zhig brjod
NK133(po)002:1455: par nus te / phyogs tsam yang mtshon par rngo thogs pa ma yin mod /
NK133(po)002:1456: de lta na'ang deng gi dus su phan bde'i 'byung
NK133(po)002:1457: gnas bstan pa rin po che spyi dang bye brag
NK133(po)002:1458: gi rtsa lag chen por gyur cing /
NK133(po)002:1459: shin tu dkar ba'i legs byas 'di nyid kyang sgrub
NK133(po)002:1460: pa'i bdag po'i rkyen gcig pur gyur pa'i phyir gtam
NK133(po)002:1461: gyi sbyor ba skabs su babs pas /
NK133(po)002:1462: ji ltar rgya mtsho chen po las skra'i rtse mos
NK133(po)002:1463: blangs pa ltar skyes bu chen po'i mdzad pa las
NK133(po)002:1464: brtsam ste cha shas tsam zhig 'god pa la /
NK133(po)002:1465: de yang 'di skad ces thos te /
NK133(po)002:1466: rnam 'dren mchog gi sprul pa'i sku /
NK133(po)002:1467: 'di nyid nges pa'i don du bskal pa dpag tu med pa'i snga rol nas /
NK133(po)002:1468: bcom ldan 'das dpal rnam par snang mdzad chen por mngon par sangs rgyas nas /
NK133(po)002:1469: slar yang gdul bya'i zhing khams 'jig rten 'bum phrag
NK133(po)002:1470: bcu'i rdul gyi grangs dang mnyam par sangs rgyas dang
NK133(po)002:1471: byang chub sems dpa'i rnam par rol pa tshad med
NK133(po)002:1474: 'khor los bsgyur ba sogs sprul pa'i rnam rol sgyu
NK133(po)002:1475: ma ltar ris su ma chad par snang ba las
NK133(po)002:1476: / bye brag tu mi mjed 'jig rten gyi khams
NK133(po)002:1477: 'dir thabs la mkhas pa'i ye shes kyi rol ba
NK133(po)002:1478: tshad med pas ston 'khor tha dad pa ltar bstan
NK133(po)002:1479: kyang don la dgongs pa dbyer mi phyed pa'i /
NK133(po)002:1480: rgyal sras rigs gsum sems dpa' dang /
NK133(po)002:1481: mnyam med thub pa'i dbang po'i nye gnas mang du
NK133(po)002:1482: thos pa'i mchog tu gyur pa 'phags pa kun dga'
NK133(po)002:1483: bo // gsang chen rgyud sde kun gyi bdag por dbang bskur ba chos rgyal lung bstan rdo rje /
NK133(po)002:1484: dpal ldan sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i bka' babs slob dpon ku ku r+aa dza /
NK133(po)002:1485: sems phyogs man ngag gi bdag po 'jam dpal bshes gnyen /
NK133(po)002:1486: mdo lung rgyud 'grel gyi shing rta bde ba gsal mdzad sogs dang /
NK133(po)002:1487: gzhan yang gangs can gyi mig gcig lo ts+aa ba chen po thon ni sam b+ho ta /
NK133(po)002:1488: pan chen bee ro tsa na /
NK133(po)002:1490: rong zom chos kyi bzang po /
NK133(po)002:1491: ras chung rdo rje grags pa /
NK133(po)002:1492: glang lung pa rgyal ba don 'grub /
NK133(po)002:1494: chos rgyal rdo rje gling ba /
NK133(po)002:1495: o rgyan kun skyong gling ba /
NK133(po)002:1496: grub thob me long rdo rje /
NK133(po)002:1498: rig 'dzin 'gyur med rdo rje sogs dus rim dang
NK133(po)002:1499: cig char sna tshogs su gcig las du mar 'char
NK133(po)002:1500: ba chu zla'i rol ba lta bu'i dag chen skye
NK133(po)002:1501: ba'i phreng ba du mar 'byams klas pa'i mthar /
NK133(po)002:1502: deng gi dus rgyal ba'i bstan pa rin po che nyams dma' bar gyur pa'i skabs 'dir /
NK133(po)002:1503: sngon rab du ma'i thugs bskyed dang smon lam stobs su gyur pas /
NK133(po)002:1504: slar yang snga 'gyur rdo rje theg pa'i ring lugs
NK133(po)002:1505: dri ma med pa'i grub mtha' gzhi bzhengs su slong
NK133(po)002:1506: ba'i shing rta chen por byon pa 'di nyid do
NK133(po)002:1507: // de ltar yang rig 'dzin 'gyur med rdo rje'i gter lung gab rgya can las /
NK133(po)002:1508: bee ro khyod ni skye matha'i byang sems teh khyod
NK133(po)002:1509: kyi 'di gong skye ba 'das pa nih smra bsam
NK133(po)002:1510: brjod 'das ye shes snying po'i donah sems can sangs
NK133(po)002:1511: rgyas mnyam nyid khyab brdal yangah khams gsum 'gro ba'i
NK133(po)002:1512: 'dren par rdo rje chosah sh+aaka thub nye gnas +aa
NK133(po)002:1513: na n+ta zhes dang rgyal po dza dang shin+tam gar+b+ha
NK133(po)002:1514: dngah bod du sam b+ho ta sogs dag pa yih
NK133(po)002:1515: skye ba de tsam snang gi ma dag pa'ih skye
NK133(po)002:1516: tshul brjod du long ba'i gnas ma yinah de ltar
NK133(po)002:1517: dag pa'i skye ba de dag gisah 'gro la snying
NK133(po)002:1518: rje chen po'i thugs bskyed pa'angah bee ro khyod du
NK133(po)002:1519: skye ba blangs pa yinah khyod kyang sh+r+ai seng+ha ye
NK133(po)002:1520: shes mdoh pad+ma bdag sogs gtsug gi bla mar bastenah
NK133(po)002:1521: gdams pa'i gnad rnams phu thag bcad byas nasah chos
NK133(po)002:1522: sku'i rang zhal mngon sum rtogs gyur pasah las 'phro
NK133(po)002:1523: ma dag skye ba len mi sridah 'on kyang sems
NK133(po)002:1524: bskyed smon lam bzang po yisah mtshams sbyor mtha' yas
NK133(po)002:1525: 'gro ba'i dpal nyid duh dbang phyug 'bar dang ra
NK133(po)002:1526: shag rdo rje glingah kun skyong gling dang mdo sngags
NK133(po)002:1527: gling pa sogasah pad+ma bdag gi zab gter bdag po
NK133(po)002:1528: dngah gzhan yang theg pa che chung sna tshogs lah
NK133(po)002:1529: de dang mthun pa'i ngo mtshar skye ba'i grangasah bcu
NK133(po)002:1530: phrag gcig dang gsum tsam 'das pa'i matharah zhes rim
NK133(po)002:1531: par lung bstan pa las khyad par chos rgyal gter
NK133(po)002:1534: khyad par snga 'gyur mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi skor rnams la /
NK133(po)002:1535: rgya chen po sdud pa dang /
NK133(po)002:1536: zab mo rnam par 'byed pa dang /
NK133(po)002:1537: 'khrugs pa go rims su sdebs pa dang /
NK133(po)002:1538: sgrub pa phyag bzhes su 'debs pa sogs 'dzin skyongs
NK133(po)002:1539: spel ba'i phrin las rgya chen po mdzad bzhin pa'i
NK133(po)002:1540: ngang nas / sku mya ngan las 'das kar shar
NK133(po)002:1541: phyogs su 'gro dgos par yod gsungs bzhengs nas gom
NK133(po)002:1542: pa bdun bor bar mdzad pa'ang /
NK133(po)002:1543: de dus kyi mdzad pa'i 'phro rnams da lta'i dus
NK133(po)002:1544: su khams kyi phyogs 'dir rje 'di nyid kyis skyongs
NK133(po)002:1545: pa la dgongs par gdon mi za zhing /
NK133(po)002:1546: der ma zad lkog gyur gyi chos rnams la sgrib
NK133(po)002:1547: med kyi ye shes mngon du gyur pa rig 'dzin
NK133(po)002:1549: gzhon nu dri med zla shar sogs kyis kyang gter
NK133(po)002:1550: bdag gling pa'i sprul pa 'khrul med du lung bstan
NK133(po)002:1552: rtsod bral gyi gter ston pad+ma 'gro 'dul rtsal gyi
NK133(po)002:1553: gdan sa rgyab stod brag dkar du phebs pa'i tshe
NK133(po)002:1554: / de'i tho rang khar rje de nyid kyi gzigs snang la /
NK133(po)002:1555: zhing skyes kyi d+aak+ki ma gsal 'debs kyi tshul du smras nas der 'phro 'jog pa zhig gsan pas /
NK133(po)002:1556: gter chen gyi sprul bar thugs thag chod de smin grol gyi gdams pa'ang mang du gsan /
NK133(po)002:1557: de dang mtshungs par rdzogs chen mchog gi sprul pa'i
NK133(po)002:1558: sku rin po che mi 'gyur nam mkha'i rdo rje'i
NK133(po)002:1559: gnas yul gyi lung byang las kyang /
NK133(po)002:1560: gnas 'di'i nye phyogs spyil chung bkod mdzes nang //
NK133(po)002:1561: bee ro'i rnam 'phrul drang srong brtul zhugs la //
NK133(po)002:1562: zhugs des 'brel tshad bde chen zhing du 'dren //
NK133(po)002:1564: bla ma dgongs pa 'dus pa'i lung bstan bka' rgya ma las kyang /
NK133(po)002:1565: dam pa 'di nyid gang du phebs pa'i chos brgyud dang bcas pa'ang gsal bar gsungs te /
NK133(po)002:1566: de la thog mar slob dpon pad+ma sam b+ha wa
NK133(po)002:1567: dang kun mkhyen dri med 'od zer sogs kyi ye
NK133(po)002:1568: shes kyi sku rjes su bzung bas don brgyud kyi
NK133(po)002:1569: bka' babs shing klong chen dgongs pa'i gsang mdzod rdol
NK133(po)002:1570: ba gar gyi dbang phyug rig 'dzin 'jigs med gling
NK133(po)002:1571: pa'am / rang byung rdo rje mkhyen brtse'i 'od zer
NK133(po)002:1572: zhes mtshan yongs su grags pa de nyid bla ma
NK133(po)002:1573: dgongs pa 'dus pa'i chos kyi bdag por lung bstan
NK133(po)002:1574: pa'am / pa ni / ji skad du lho phyogs 'od zer ming can sprul pa'i sku /
NK133(po)002:1575: zab don snying thig chos kyis 'gro ba 'adrenah 'brel
NK133(po)002:1576: tshad rig 'dzin zhing du 'phen pa 'abyungah zhes dang
NK133(po)002:1577: / rje de nyid kyi thugs sras dam pa mdo
NK133(po)002:1578: khams kyi phyogs su bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan 'dzin pa
NK133(po)002:1579: grub pa'i dbang phyug 'jigs med phrin las 'od zer
NK133(po)002:1581: shar phyogs 'od zer ming can gdung shugs canah phrin
