NK133(po)002:1582: las rmad byung blo stobs shes rab ldanah thugs kyi
NK133(po)002:1583: gsang mdzod rdol ba'i gdams pa 'adzinah bstan pa spel
NK133(po)002:1584: grogs byed pa'i skal ldan 'abyungah zhes klong chen brda'
NK133(po)002:1585: bsgyur nam mkha' mdzod kyi chos sde klong chen snying
NK133(po)002:1586: gi thig le'i chos kyi bdag po dang bstan pa
NK133(po)002:1587: spel ba'i byed por basngagasa pa'i skyes bu dam pa
NK133(po)002:1588: de nyid la chos brgyud 'dzin pa'i slob bu ji
NK133(po)002:1589: ltar 'byung ba'ang / rtsa ba'i 'khor slob gdung shugs
NK133(po)002:1590: ldan pa nih bud+d+ha mched drug rdo rje'i gdung bzhi
NK133(po)002:1591: steh shar gyi phyogs nas dung dkar 'khyil 'dra 'abyungah
NK133(po)002:1592: snyan grags sgrogs dang bstan pa spel bar byedah lho
NK133(po)002:1593: yi phyogs nas slob ma 'byung 'gyur teh 'bras kyi
NK133(po)002:1594: phung po spung pa lta bu yisah 'dod yon zas
NK133(po)002:1595: nor longs spyod spel bar byedah nub nas pad+ma dmar
NK133(po)002:1596: ser 'khrigs 'dra ba'ih sgrib med sgrub tshug 'dzin pa'i
NK133(po)002:1597: slob ma 'abyungah byang gi phyogs nas lcags phur lta
NK133(po)002:1598: bu yih mthu rtsal ldan pa'i slob ma 'ga' zhig
NK133(po)002:1599: nih bstan pa 'phel byed phrin las sgrub pa 'abyungah
NK133(po)002:1600: zhes sogs mang du gsungs pa las /
NK133(po)002:1601: khyad par du gyur pa rdo rje'i gdung chen bzhi'i nang tshan /
NK133(po)002:1602: nub phyogs nas 'byung bar lung bstan pa ni rje 'di nyid yin te /
NK133(po)002:1603: gang gi tshe gsang chen bla na med pa'i dkyil 'khor chen por dbang bskur ba'i gsang mtshan du /
NK133(po)002:1604: rig pa'i rdo rje bee ro tsa na rtsal zhes 'bod pas /
NK133(po)002:1607: 'khrungs yul sogs gang gi sgo nas kyang 'khrul pa'i gnas rdul tsam yang yod pa ma yin no //
NK133(po)002:1608: de ltar tshad mar gyur pa'i lung gis grub cing /
NK133(po)002:1609: grub mtha' ris med kyi dge ba'i bshes gnyen chen
NK133(po)002:1610: po chos kyi spyan can dpyad gsum rnam par dag
NK133(po)002:1611: pa'i blo gros dang ldan pa rnams kyis kyang /
NK133(po)002:1612: basngagasa brjod kyi me tog sil ma phyogs kun tu 'grem zhing /
NK133(po)002:1613: dad gsum gyi rnam 'gyur cir yang ngoms pas gus
NK133(po)002:1614: 'dud lhur len pa'i skyes bu dam pa 'di nyid
NK133(po)002:1615: ni / mdo khams sa yi thig le rma zla zal mo'i sgang gi stod kyi char /
NK133(po)002:1616: yab myes kyi phyogs nas bdun brgyud tshun la dag
NK133(po)002:1617: pa'i rigs rus dang cho 'brang sogs phun sum tshogs
NK133(po)002:1619: gzhon nu nyid nas skyes thob kyi mkhyen rab khyad par can mnga' bas /
NK133(po)002:1620: yi ge 'bri klog dang 'bru non gyi don sogs tshegs chung ngus mkhyen zhing /
NK133(po)002:1621: khyad par rje nyid dang gdung rus gcig pa'i mkhas
NK133(po)002:1622: pa chen po bla ma smon lam dar rgyas pa'i
NK133(po)002:1623: drung nas / bod kyi brda' dag thams cad kyi
NK133(po)002:1624: phyi mor gyur pa sum cu pa dang rtags kyi
NK133(po)002:1626: gzhan yang snyan ngag me long dang dkar rtsis sogs thun mong gi rig gnas dang /
NK133(po)002:1627: mdo sngags spyi'i gzhung lugs legs par ston pa yon tan mdzod rtsa 'grel sogs mang du gsan /
NK133(po)002:1628: skabs 'di tsam na rig 'dzin 'jigs med gling pa'i dngos slob /
NK133(po)002:1629: smon 'jug byang chub sems kyi rtsal 'byongs shing 'od
NK133(po)002:1630: gsal rdzogs pa chen po'i dgongs pa mngon du gyur
NK133(po)002:1631: pa / dpal nam mkha' lta bu'i rnal 'byor gyi
NK133(po)002:1632: dbang phyug chen po 'jigs med rgyal ba'i myu gus
NK133(po)002:1633: chos kyi 'khor lo thog mar bskor ba dang rten
NK133(po)002:1634: 'brel gyi sgo 'grigs nas thun mong dang thun mong
NK133(po)002:1635: ma yin pa'i lam gyi rim pa spyi dang /
NK133(po)002:1636: khyad par skyes bu chen po'i blo sbyong gi skor rnams zhal khrid du gsan pa'i rkyen gyis /
NK133(po)002:1637: bskal ba du mar byang chub kyi sems la goms pa'i rigs sad de /
NK133(po)002:1638: 'khor ba las nges par 'byung ba'i blo dang /
NK133(po)002:1639: sems can la brtse ba'i shugs drag po gnyis phan
NK133(po)002:1640: tshun 'gran pa lta bus rgyud dbang med du 'khrul
NK133(po)002:1641: te / 'jig rten srid pa'i phun tshogs rnams la
NK133(po)002:1642: thugs zhen gting nas log cing 'dir snang mthun 'jug
NK133(po)002:1643: gi bya ba thams cad rgyab tu dor te /
NK133(po)002:1644: tshe 'dir sgrub pa'i rgyal mtshan zhig btsugs nas rang
NK133(po)002:1645: gzhan gyi don gnyis lhan gcig tu 'grub pa grub
NK133(po)002:1646: thob rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug gong ma rnams kyi
NK133(po)002:1647: rjes su snyogs pa zhig ci nas kyang byed dgos
NK133(po)002:1648: dgongs pa'i thugs bzhed nar mar yod thog gling grub
NK133(po)002:1649: chen bsod nams sbyin pa'i drung nas bstan pa la
NK133(po)002:1650: 'jug pa'i sgo yongs rdzogs dge bsnyen gyi khrims gsan
NK133(po)002:1651: zhing / smin grol gyi gdams pa mang du nos /
NK133(po)002:1652: de nas bla ma dam pa gzhon nu 'jigs med
NK133(po)002:1653: skal pa bzang po phyogs der phebs pa dang zhal
NK133(po)002:1654: mjal / khong nas rje gter bdag gling pa'i rnam
NK133(po)002:1655: sprul bka' 'gyur pa chen po mkhas grub bkra shis
NK133(po)002:1656: rgya mtsho'i yang srid du ngos bzung nas khri 'don
NK133(po)002:1658: skabs 'dir mkhas grub 'jigs med ngo mtshar las rnying ma rgyud 'bum dang /
NK133(po)002:1659: dge mang rab 'byams pa dge legs yar 'phel las byang chub lam rim chen mo sogs gsan /
NK133(po)002:1660: der grub dbang chos kyi rgyal po rig 'dzin byang
NK133(po)002:1661: chub rdo rje'i mtshan gyi snyan pa gsan pas thugs
NK133(po)002:1662: phrogs te dge ba'i bshes gnyen bsten pa la gcig
NK133(po)002:1663: tu rings bas / gnyen tshan dang yul mi rnams
NK133(po)002:1664: kyis bshol 'debs bslab ston sogs gang la yang ma
NK133(po)002:1665: tu rings bas / gsan par / chos phyir dka'
NK133(po)002:1666: ba spyad pa'i snying stobs zhums pa med pas shar
NK133(po)002:1667: phyogs ngos su byon pa na /
NK133(po)002:1668: rim gyis brag chen yar lung pad+ma bkod kyi sgrub
NK133(po)002:1669: sde rtsa gsum mkha' 'gro 'du ba'i gling chen por
NK133(po)002:1670: phebs nas / der grub pa'i dbang phyug chen po'i zhabs la gtugs shing rigs kyi bdag por bkur /
NK133(po)002:1671: rje des kyang thugs shin tu brtse bas rjes su
NK133(po)002:1672: bzung nas smin grol gyi gdams pa mtha' dag lhag
NK133(po)002:1673: lus med par bum pa gang byos tshul du gnang
NK133(po)002:1674: zhing / bdag la gzhan phan byang chub sems kyi
NK133(po)002:1675: brgyud pa zhig yod pa 'di khyod kyis 'dzin par
NK133(po)002:1676: zhing / re'o // zhes gsungs nas don gyis rgyal
NK133(po)002:1677: ba'i gdung 'tshob tu mnga' gsol zhing mtshan rgyal ba'i
NK133(po)002:1678: sras po gzhan phan mtha' yas 'od zer du btags
NK133(po)002:1679: zhing / re'o // / gzhan yang zhal gdams dang bslab bya mang du gnang /
NK133(po)002:1681: bskyed rdzogs dang sgom bzlas gang byasah pha rol du
NK133(po)002:1682: phyin pa drug dngah 'bral med du nyams su longs
NK133(po)002:1683: dngah khyod rang la gzhan phan mtha' yasah zhes bya
NK133(po)002:1684: yi ming don mtshungs bazhinah phan bde yi rtsa lag
NK133(po)002:1685: nyid 'agyurah zhes 'byung 'gyur gyi lung bstan dang bcas
NK133(po)002:1687: de nas gzhon nu 'jigs med skal pa bzang po las /
NK133(po)002:1688: dpal gsang ba'i snying po'i bshad pa dang /
NK133(po)002:1689: sgyu 'phrul zhi khro'i dbang dang gdams khrid kyi skor sogs mang du gsan /
NK133(po)002:1690: gzhan yang thugs sras kyi bu chen rnams las /
NK133(po)002:1691: gtum mo rtsa rlung gi skor 'ga' zhig dang /
NK133(po)002:1693: gcod yul sogs zab rgyas kyi gdams ngag mtha' yas
NK133(po)002:1694: par gsan nas bya btang rnal 'byor chen po'i spyod
NK133(po)002:1695: pa bskyangs te khams kyi rtsa ri tra'am rigs lnga'i
NK133(po)002:1696: rdzongs su grags pa'i mgur chu nyi zla phug dang
NK133(po)002:1697: / ga gong seng ge yang dgon /
NK133(po)002:1698: ka ti shel gyi phug pa /
NK133(po)002:1699: ri bo dan tig dang yang tig tu grags pa
NK133(po)002:1700: rnams su bcud len dang gtum mo'i rnal 'byor grogs
NK133(po)002:1701: su brten nas zab gsang bla na med pa'i bskyed
NK133(po)002:1702: rdzogs rim pa gnyis kyi nyams bzhes spyi dang /
NK133(po)002:1703: 'od gsal rdzogs pa chen po'i gnad la rtse gcig
NK133(po)002:1704: tu gzhol bas thun mong dang thun mong ma yin
NK133(po)002:1705: pa'i lam gyi drod rtags brnyes shing /
NK133(po)002:1706: khyad par gnyug ma'i de nyid mngon du gyur pas
NK133(po)002:1707: skabs 'di dag tu nyams dbyangs rdo rje'i mgur ma
NK133(po)002:1708: thol byung du bzhes pa'ang mang du snang /
NK133(po)002:1709: gzhan yang sog po'i yul gru mtsho sngon gyi phyogs tshun chad dang /
NK133(po)002:1710: rgya nag glang chen 'gying ri yan chad kyi gnas
NK133(po)002:1711: ri dang sgrub gnas thams cad du phebs shing sgrub
NK133(po)002:1712: pa kho na mdzad cing bzhugs pa'i bar skabs rnams
NK133(po)002:1713: su las dang skal bar ldan pa'i bu slob 'ga'
NK133(po)002:1714: la smin grol gyi gdams pa phog cing /
NK133(po)002:1715: dad 'dus kyi tshogs pa spyi la'ang las 'bras kyi
NK133(po)002:1716: chos mang du gsungs pas gdul bya rnams la phan
NK133(po)002:1717: 'dogs par mdzad khyad par rgyal mo rong gi phyogs
NK133(po)002:1718: tsha kha dang mdo chen sogs su rje 'di nyid
NK133(po)002:1719: kyis phyag 'debs mdzad pa'i sgrub sde dang dgon sde
NK133(po)002:1720: 'ga' zhig yod pa la da lta'i dus su bshad
NK133(po)002:1721: sgrub kyi srol kyang legs par dar /
NK133(po)002:1722: de nas grub dbang chen po'i 'byung 'gyur gyi lung byang las /
NK133(po)002:1723: de phyir na ru dam dben par //
NK133(po)002:1725: bskyed rdzogs la brtson pa bskyed na //
NK133(po)002:1726: gzugs can dang gzugs med 'gro ba //
NK133(po)002:1727: phal mo che gdul byar 'gyur zhing //
NK133(po)002:1728: rang gzhan gyi don gnyis lhan gcig /'grub nges pa pad+ma'i bkar mtshungs //
NK133(po)002:1729: zhes sogs gsungs pa la brten nas /
NK133(po)002:1730: ru dam gyi dben gnas rnams su sgrub pa rtse gcig mdzad par bzhed de phebs pa las /
NK133(po)002:1731: gdan sa chen po o rgyan bsam gtan chos gling
NK133(po)002:1732: du rdzogs pa chen po chos nyid mngon sum gyi
NK133(po)002:1733: don la dbang 'byor pa grub pa'i dbang phyug mi
NK133(po)002:1734: 'gyur nam mkha'i rdo rje dang mjal /
NK133(po)002:1735: der 'dus pa mdo dbang chen mo dang /
NK133(po)002:1736: zab gsang mkha' 'gro snying thig gi dbang lung khrid dang bcas pa zhib rgyas su gsan nas /
NK133(po)002:1737: gshin rje phug dang tshe ring phug sogs su sgrub pa mdzad de bzhugs pa'i bar skabs rnams la /
NK133(po)002:1738: mchog sprul rin po che'i zhal snga nas rje 'di
NK133(po)002:1739: nyid la dgon 'dir bshad sgrub kyi srol ka re
NK133(po)002:1740: btod rgyu byung na legs tshul gyi gsung nan yang
NK133(po)002:1742: gzhi byis kyi bla sprul dang grwa tshang bcas khyon brgya skor tsam la /
NK133(po)002:1746: dpal ldan gsang ba snying po sogs gdul bya'i blo
NK133(po)002:1747: dang mtshams par lung rig gi lam nas nges pa
NK133(po)002:1748: 'drong ba'i bshad pa gting tshugs par mdzad /
NK133(po)002:1749: skabs 'dir dgon 'di ga'i ri khrod du bzhugs pa'i bla ma dam pa /
NK133(po)002:1750: mkhas btsun bzang po'i dpal gyis mngon par mtho zhing /
NK133(po)002:1751: mang du thos pa'i blo gros rgya mtsho dang mtshungs kyang /
NK133(po)002:1752: dben pa'i ri la gcig tu dgyes shing sbas pa'i
NK133(po)002:1753: tshul du bzhugs pa'i rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po
NK133(po)002:1754: pad+ma mang+ga la sh+r+ai b+ha dra'i zhal snga nas /
NK133(po)002:1755: bstan pa'i gzhi ma 'dul ba so thar gyi rab
NK133(po)002:1756: byung gzhi chog la brten nas bsnyen par rdzogs pa
NK133(po)002:1757: dge slong gi dngos par bsgrub /
NK133(po)002:1758: slar yang dbu ma lugs kyi theg pa chen po'i
NK133(po)002:1759: sems bskyed kyi cho ga la brten nas byang chub
NK133(po)002:1764: phur pa rong zom pa'i lugs /
NK133(po)002:1765: dka' 'grel 'bum nag tu grags pa rnams dang /
NK133(po)002:1768: sems klong man ngag gi sde gsum /
NK133(po)002:1771: 'dod 'jo bum bzang sogs snga 'gyur bka' gter gyi
NK133(po)002:1772: gzhung rgya mtsho lta bu las deng sang gi dus
NK133(po)002:1773: su yod pa'i rgyun phal che ba zhig gsan /
NK133(po)002:1774: de nas dbus phyogs su yang deng sngon lan gnyis tsam rim par phebs shing /
NK133(po)002:1775: der rgyud stod mkhan po dge 'dun dar rgyas las /
NK133(po)002:1777: dbu ma rig pa'i tshogs drug sogs 'phags yul mkhas
NK133(po)002:1778: pa'i gzhung lugs kyi rgyun yod do co ga thams
NK133(po)002:1779: cad dang / o rgyan smin grol gling gi rdor
NK133(po)002:1780: 'dzin mkhan po 'gyur med mi pham dpal bzang po
NK133(po)002:1781: las rgyal ba'i bka' 'gyur chen mo yongs rdzogs /
NK133(po)002:1782: lha lung pad ri sprul sku las /
NK133(po)002:1784: mi tra brgya rtsa sogs kyi skor /
NK133(po)002:1785: smin gling khri chen las gter chen bka' 'bum yongs rdzogs /
NK133(po)002:1786: na len+t+ra'i gzims 'og sprul pa'i sku las /
NK133(po)002:1789: yongs 'dzin dam byams pa 'phrin las yon tan las /
NK133(po)002:1791: lam 'bras kyi skor sogs gsar rnying ris med kyi
NK133(po)002:1792: skyes chen du ma las gsan bsam mtha' yas par
NK133(po)002:1793: mdzad / gzhan yang bsam yas mchims phu /
NK133(po)002:1796: dpal gyi r+ts+wa ri tra sogs su sgrub pa mdzad pa dang /
NK133(po)002:1797: gnas skor pa rnams la rtsam tshul gtong ba sogs sbyin gtong rgya cher mdzad /
NK133(po)002:1798: chos 'khor gsum dang jo sh+aaka rnam gnyis sogs la mchod 'bul /
NK133(po)002:1799: o rgyan smin grol gling gi 'dus sde'i rgyun nyams
NK133(po)002:1800: gsos sogs 'khor lo gsum gyi mdzad pa rmad du
NK133(po)002:1801: byung ba bsgrubs / slar khams phyogs su byon te /
NK133(po)002:1802: rgyal ba'i bka' 'gyur dang bstan 'gyur gyis mtshon /
NK133(po)002:1803: mdo sngags bka' gter gyi rgyun nyag phra ba rnams la 'chad spel rgya chen po mdzad /
NK133(po)002:1804: khyad par du rgyal bstan rin po che spyi'i gzhi ma yin pa dang /
NK133(po)002:1805: gdul bya'i gang zag rnams kyi mig rkyen du dgongs nas /
NK133(po)002:1806: gzhi gsum gyi cho ga sogs 'dul ba'i phyag bzhes
NK133(po)002:1807: rnam par dag pa'i srol btod nas bstan pa'i me
NK133(po)002:1809: deng gi gnas skabs 'dir bstan pa yongs rdzogs kyi bdag por bzhugs bzhin pa 'di nyid do //
NK133(po)002:1810: de ltar rje 'di nyid kyi rnam par thar pa
NK133(po)002:1811: rgya mtsho lta bu las cha shas tsam zhig bkod
NK133(po)002:1812: pa yin gyis / gzhan du rgyal sras byang chub
NK133(po)002:1813: sems dpa'i spyod pa rlabs po ches phan bde'i 'byung
NK133(po)002:1814: gnas rgyal ba'i lung rtogs kyi bstan pa rin po
NK133(po)002:1815: che la bshad sgrub las gsum gyis mdzad pa ji
NK133(po)002:1816: ltar bgyis pa mtha' dag ni blos 'chun par yang
NK133(po)002:1817: dka' bas phyogs gcig tu bri bar ma nus so
NK133(po)002:1818: pa yin gyis / // mdor na bdag cag gi /
NK133(po)002:1819: rnam 'dren dam pa 'di ni rgyal ba'i ye shes kyi rol ba bsam bzhin du /
NK133(po)002:1820: srid par skye ba'i myu gu bzung bas mdo sngags
NK133(po)002:1821: kyi gzhung nas bshad pa'i bla ma dge ba'i bshes
NK133(po)002:1822: gnyen gyi mtshan nyid rnams da nga yang dag par
NK133(po)002:1823: ldan pa ste / 'dul ba so thar gyi lugs ltar na /
NK133(po)002:1825: tshul khrims ldan zhing 'dul ba'i cho ga shes //
NK133(po)002:1826: nad par snying brtse 'khor ni dag pa dang //
NK133(po)002:1827: chos dang zang zing phan 'dogs kyis brtson pa //
NK133(po)002:1828: dus su 'dom pa de dag bla mar basngagasa //
NK133(po)002:1830: brtan mkhas btsun pa phan 'dogs kyi yon tan bzhi dang ldan pa dang /
NK133(po)002:1833: bshes gnyen dul ba zhi ba nyer zhi ba //
NK133(po)002:1834: yon tan lhag pa brtson bcas lung gis phyug /
NK133(po)002:1835: de nyid rab tu rtogs pa smra mkhas ldan //
NK133(po)002:1836: brtse ba'i bdag nyid skyo ngal spang la bsten //
NK133(po)002:1837: zhes yon tan bcu dang ldan par bshad pa dang /
NK133(po)002:1840: ston pa mdzod ldan chu bo rdzogs //
NK133(po)002:1841: gnyer ldan rgyud dang las la mkhas //
NK133(po)002:1843: zhes rang bzhin brgyad ldan du bshad pa ste /
NK133(po)002:1844: de rnams kyang gzu bo'i blo dang ldan pa dag
NK133(po)002:1845: gis re re nas phye zhing zhib mor brtags na'ang
NK133(po)002:1846: / 'di dang mi ldan no zhes rgol ba 'jug
NK133(po)002:1847: pa'i gnas cung zad tsam yang rnyed par sla ba
NK133(po)002:1848: / ma yin zhing / gzhan yang kun mkhyen chen pos yid bzhin mdzod du /
NK133(po)002:1849: shes rab rgya che skal bzang bla ma ni //
NK133(po)002:1850: rig gnas kun la shes bya'i dkyil 'khor rgyas //
NK133(po)002:1851: thos bsam rgya che grub matha'i tshig don mkhas //
NK133(po)002:1852: lta spyod phul byung gang gis smad du med //
NK133(po)002:1853: lung rig dang ldan rang bzo gzu lum med //
NK133(po)002:1854: gdul bya'i blo rigs brtags nas chos ston cing //
NK133(po)002:1855: byang chub lam 'dren ded dpon blo mig can //
NK133(po)002:1856: rin chen thar gling bgrod de gus pas bsten //
NK133(po)002:1858: rim brgyud byin rlabs ldan pa'i bla ma ni //
NK133(po)002:1859: gong ma mnyes byas grub thob brgyud pa 'dzin //
NK133(po)002:1860: thugs mdzod lon pas snyan brgyud gdams pa ldan //
NK133(po)002:1861: phyag bzhes mthong bas don gnyis sgrub la mkhas //
NK133(po)002:1862: sgrub la brtson pas dngos grub sprin tshogs brnyes //
NK133(po)002:1863: gzhan snang bsgyur nas thar pa'i lam sna 'dren //
NK133(po)002:1864: mdo rgyud bka' babs dam tshig gtsang gyur pa //
NK133(po)002:1865: de 'dra'i mkhas grub dpal mgon spyi bos bsten //
NK133(po)002:1867: mtshan nyid thams cad dang ldan pas na /
NK133(po)002:1868: rje 'di nyid kyi phyi nang gsang ba'i yon tan rnams ni /
NK133(po)002:1869: rgyal bas gsungs pa'i mdo rgyud dang /
NK133(po)002:1870: tshad ldan gyi bstan bcos dag la zhu dag bgyid nus pa 'ba' zhig yin no //
NK133(po)002:1872: de ltar snyigs ma'i dus 'dir 'gran zla dang bral ba'i skyes bu dam pa de nyid /
NK133(po)002:1873: sngar grub dbang bla ma'i gdan sar bzhugs yod pa'i skabs shig tu /
NK133(po)002:1874: mnal lam na gzhan zhig gis 'di slob dpon pad+ma'i
NK133(po)002:1875: gsung dngos yin zer nas pu sti zhig gtad byung
NK133(po)002:1876: bas / phyi nyin mched grogs kun la /
NK133(po)002:1877: deng sang slob dpon chen po'i gsung dngos bka' mar
NK133(po)002:1878: gyur pa'i yig cha khung ldan 'dra 'dir yod min
NK133(po)002:1880: khong rnams nas man ngag lta ba'i phreng ba rtsa 'grel bcas sngar yod kyang /
NK133(po)002:1881: de'i dpe stor nas yun ring song yang rtsad ma chod /
NK133(po)002:1882: gzhan de 'dra cang med zer ba la /
NK133(po)002:1884: kho bo la rmis ltas 'di 'dra zhig byung bas
NK133(po)002:1885: da lan dpe mdzod du btsal na rnyed pa srid
NK133(po)002:1886: dam gsungs nas / thams cad kyis btsal kyang phyag dpe'i khrod nas rnyed rgyu ma byung zhing /
NK133(po)002:1887: sngar chos khri'i 'og gi sa rdul rnams la gad
NK133(po)002:1888: brgyab pa'i khrod nas lta phreng gi dpe cha thon
NK133(po)002:1889: byung ba gzigs pas tshig don phun sum tshogs par
NK133(po)002:1890: 'dug pa la nges shes thun mong ma yin pa
NK133(po)002:1893: bye brag tu snga 'gyur bka' ma'i phyogs 'di ga
NK133(po)002:1894: dar ba zhig byed dgos dgongs pa'i thugs 'dun drag
NK133(po)002:1895: po rgyun chags su yod khar /
NK133(po)002:1896: dbus phebs snga ma spu kong brgyud nas phebs skabs /
NK133(po)002:1897: sngar dwags brgyud pa'i gdan sa phyis smin grol gling
NK133(po)002:1898: ba'i dgon lag tu gyur pa lha lung pad ri
NK133(po)002:1899: ru byon / der mchog gi sprul ba'i sku rig
NK133(po)002:1900: 'a dzin pad+ma dbang rgyal rdo rje dang zhal mjal
NK133(po)002:1901: ru byon / / legs bshad kyi 'bel gtam zhib
NK133(po)002:1902: tu byas pas thugs yid gcig 'dres su gyur cing
NK133(po)002:1903: phyi nang gsang ba'i yon tan dang /
NK133(po)002:1904: 'chad rtsod rtsom pa'i phrin las sogs gang nas kyang
NK133(po)002:1905: gter chen chos kyi rgyal po dngos dang tha mi
NK133(po)002:1907: rje de nyid kyi dbu zhwa dang khri ber bcas
NK133(po)002:1908: sku la phul te mi 'jigs seng ge'i khri la
NK133(po)002:1909: mnga' gsol / tshe sgrub 'chi med yang snying gi
NK133(po)002:1910: dkyil 'khor du brtan bzhugs kyi cho ga rgyas par
NK133(po)002:1912: snga 'gyur nang rgyud sde gsum gyi cho ga'i rim
NK133(po)002:1913: pa ltar chog khrigs yod pa rnams sor bzhag dang
NK133(po)002:1914: / med pa rnams rje nyid kyis ljags sgrigs mdzad
NK133(po)002:1915: nas mtha' dag phyogs gcig tu bsdus te dbang lung
NK133(po)002:1916: gi 'chad spel sogs chun gcig tu byed rgyu zhig
NK133(po)002:1917: / byung na / dngos su de dag gi rgyun btsal sla ba dang /
NK133(po)002:1918: brgyud nas bstan pa mi nyams pa'i gtsas su dgos pa dang /
NK133(po)002:1919: phan cha shin tu che bar 'dug ces nan tan
NK133(po)002:1920: chen pos zhu mchid tshigs bcad kyi lam nas spel
NK133(po)002:1922: phyogs dus rgyal ba kun gyi sras //
NK133(po)002:1924: lus can kun las sems 'phags pa'i //
NK133(po)002:1925: rnam 'dren bla ma mchog gi drung //
NK133(po)002:1926: sgo gsum tha dad ma yin gcig bsdus te //
NK133(po)002:1927: gus phyag bstod dbyangs gdung shugs bcas te gsol //
NK133(po)002:1928: thog mtha' bar gyi dus tshigs mi mngon pa'i //
NK133(po)002:1929: dang por byang chub mchog tu thugs bskyed nas /
NK133(po)002:1931: 1 / phyi ltar mdo lugs bskal ba grangs med dang //
NK133(po)002:1932: nang ltar sngags lugs tshe lus gcig gi mthar //
NK133(po)002:1933: gsang ba gsang chen rig stong chos sku'i zhal //
NK133(po)002:1934: mngon gyur rdo rje snying po'i klong der grol /
NK133(po)002:1936: 2 / rnam 'dren mchog dang kun mkhyen nyi ma'i gnyen //
NK133(po)002:1937: spang dang rtogs pa'i yon tan mnyam gyur kyang //
NK133(po)002:1938: mtshan dpe'i rgyan 'dis thub pa'i dbang po dang //
NK133(po)002:1939: snyigs dus bstan 'gro'i mgon khyod so sor rtogs /
NK133(po)002:1941: 3 / ma rtogs log par rtogs dang phyogs tsam rtogs //
NK133(po)002:1942: yang dag ji bzhin nyid du ma rtogs sogs //
NK133(po)002:1943: rang rang grub matha'i 'dod zhen ji snyed kun //
NK133(po)002:1944: gcod la 'jigs bral dpal mgon klu sgrub dngos /
NK133(po)002:1946: 4 / mdzes sku mig gi bdud rtsir gyur pa dang //
NK133(po)002:1947: zab rgyas gsung dbyangs rna ba'i bcud len du //
NK133(po)002:1948: thob pa'i skal bzang so skyes dngos yin kyang //
NK133(po)002:1949: sa bcu'i dbang phyug rnams kyi zla bor song /
NK133(po)002:1951: 5 / ci slad zab zhi spros dang bral ba yi //
NK133(po)002:1952: don bzang lus can kun la lhan skyes su //
NK133(po)002:1953: yod kyang mi rtogs bstan kyang shes dka' ba'i //
NK133(po)002:1954: de nyid khyod kyi drin las mngon sum rnyed /
NK133(po)002:1956: 6 / thub pa rnams kyis dam pa'i chos btsal tshe //
NK133(po)002:1957: legs par bshad pa'i tshigs bcad phyed gcig gi //
NK133(po)002:1958: phyir yang rgyu nor longs spyod rgyal srid dang /
NK133(po)002:1959: srog gi bar du btang zhes yongs grags na /
NK133(po)002:1961: 7 / bskal bar rnyed daka'i chos mchog 'di 'dra ba'i //
NK133(po)002:1962: ched du gling bzhi'i 'jig rten khor yug bcas //
NK133(po)002:1963: 'dzam bu'i chu bo'i gser gyis bkang byas kyang //
NK133(po)002:1964: de yi cha shas tsam yang gzhal nus min /
NK133(po)002:1966: 8 / bdag 'dra'i skye bo sred pa'i gzhan dbang can //
NK133(po)002:1967: rtag tu rnyed dang bkur stis zil non zhing //
NK133(po)002:1968: khab skud tsam zhig gtong la'ang snying zhums pas //
NK133(po)002:1969: bka' drin ji ltar 'khor snyam yid la bcags /
NK133(po)002:1971: 9 / de lta na'ang chos drin gso phyir dang //
NK133(po)002:1972: khyad par snga 'gyur rdzogs pa chen po zhes //
NK133(po)002:1973: sems klong man ngag sde las nyer 'phros pa'i //
NK133(po)002:1974: rgyud lung sbas pa shin tu zab mo'i chos /
NK133(po)002:1976: 10 / deng sang dus na mdo sngags thun mong gi //
NK133(po)002:1977: bstan 'dzin phal gyi spyod yul ma gyur pas //
NK133(po)002:1978: nyi nub zer dang 'chi kha'i mar me bzhin //
NK133(po)002:1979: zad la nye bar gyur pa'i gnas skabs 'dir /

NK133(po)002:2037: smon lam stobs bskyed e 'grub snyams /
