NK133(po)002:2040: sa bon zhing sar thebs zin pas //
NK133(po)002:2041: 'dod don snye ma g.yur za bar //
NK133(po)002:2042: bar chad med cing mthar phyin shog /
NK133(po)002:2043: ces sgrub rgyud karma tshang gi gdan sa'i shul 'dzin /
NK133(po)002:2044: o rgyan smin grol gling gi gra ba'i tha shal
NK133(po)002:2045: bla ming ser gzugs tsam 'dzin pa'i rmongs rtul ba
NK133(po)002:2046: / rig 'dzin pad+ma dbang rgyal rdo rje zhes 'bod pas /
NK133(po)002:2047: rab yid lcags yos kyi zla tshes bzang por lhag bsam rab tu dkar bas bris te phul /
NK133(po)002:2048: zhes nan tan chen pos bskul ba dang /
NK133(po)002:2049: slad nas o rgyan smin grol gling ba'i gdung 'dzin
NK133(po)002:2050: khri rabs drug pa 'gyur med sangs rgyas kun dag'i
NK133(po)002:2052: bkra shis pa'i re kha bkra ba'i mdzod btags /
NK133(po)002:2054: bzang phrug gi na bza' rnams kyi skyes dang bcas te /
NK133(po)002:2055: nye bar bskul bas mtshams sbyar /
NK133(po)002:2056: gzhan yang dbus phyogs su bzhugs yod pa'i skabs shig gi mnal lam du /
NK133(po)002:2057: rje nyid kyi ma yum de yin snyams pa'i bud med zhig gis ltos dang zer /
NK133(po)002:2059: gang snang thams cad yig 'bru shin tu che ba
NK133(po)002:2060: mang pos gang nas khra chem chem 'dug pa la
NK133(po)002:2061: / bud med des gser gyi rdo rje 'od 'bar
NK133(po)002:2062: ba zhig mdun thad kyi nam mkhar lan gsum 'phang
NK133(po)002:2063: ba'i mthar bar snang der rten med du bsdad song
NK133(po)002:2064: / ba / sdigs mdzub kyi brda' thabs gang du
NK133(po)002:2065: bstan pa'i phyogs der hril hril 'gro ba zhig gzigs
NK133(po)002:2066: / ba / pas / rdo rje theg pa'i bstan
NK133(po)002:2067: la ri mor gyis shig ces mkha' 'gros brdas bskul
NK133(po)002:2069: snga 'gyur bka' ma'i skor gyi dpe rgyun dkon rigs
NK133(po)002:2070: rnams dbus gtsang kun tu btsal bas ma rnyed par
NK133(po)002:2071: yod pa'i tshe / smin gling du bzhugs skabs cha
NK133(po)002:2072: shas tsam 'di ga'i dpe mdzod du yod zer ba
NK133(po)002:2073: zhig gzims lam du byung nas nyin gcig thog thag
NK133(po)002:2074: la phyag dpe thams cad klog kyang rnyed rgyu ma
NK133(po)002:2075: byung bar slar gzims shag tu phebs /
NK133(po)002:2076: de nub kyang da dung tshol dang nges par yod
NK133(po)002:2077: zer ba zhig gsan nas slar yang btsal bas sgyu
NK133(po)002:2078: 'phrul phra mo'i skor sogs kyi pu sti gnyis tsam
NK133(po)002:2079: phyag tu 'byor / de la sogs pa mkha' 'gro
NK133(po)002:2080: dang chos skyong rnams kyis kyang bskul ma dang phrin
NK133(po)002:2081: las sgrub pa'i rtags mtshan ngo mtshar ba mang po
NK133(po)002:2083: lha gnyen chen po rdo rje g.yung drung gi ri
NK133(po)002:2084: zhol 'og min o rgyan bsam gtan chos gling gi
NK133(po)002:2086: dpal seng ge ri'i gdan sa 'dir /
NK133(po)002:2087: skal bzang rnam 'dren bzhi pa mnyam med thub pa'i
NK133(po)002:2088: dbang po nyid mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas te
NK133(po)002:2089: chos kyi 'khor lo thog mar bskor nas da lta'i
NK133(po)002:2090: bar gyi 'das lo'i tshul la bzhed pa mang du
NK133(po)002:2091: snang yang / rang lugs lo chen d+harma sh+ri'i rtsis gzhung nyin byed snang ba ltar na /
NK133(po)002:2092: bgrang bya'i 'khor lo nyis stong dang bdun brgya drug cu rtsa drug 'das shing /
NK133(po)002:2093: rje nyid kyis dgung lo bzhi bcu rtsa gcig bzhes
NK133(po)002:2094: pa kun ldan zhes pa lcags pho byi ba'i lo'i
NK133(po)002:2095: hor zla gsum pa chu shel dbang po'i dkyil 'khor
NK133(po)002:2096: dpal ldan lha mo nag pas nya ba'i dmar phyogs
NK133(po)002:2099: skar ma snubs 'phrod sbyor rgyal mtshan sogs phun sum
NK133(po)002:2100: tshogs pa'i dus tshes dge ba la bya ba las
NK133(po)002:2101: kyi 'khor lo chen po 'dir dbu 'dzug par mdzad
NK133(po)002:2102: pa yin no // de la thog mar zhus dag
NK133(po)002:2103: dang snag shog gi las 'dzin spar shing sprod len
NK133(po)002:2104: sogs gnang khur gyi do dam pa /
NK133(po)002:2105: nyid kyi zhal slob sdom brtson dam pa mang du
NK133(po)002:2106: thos pa'i nor gyis phyug cing gzhung lugs rgya mtsho'i
NK133(po)002:2107: pha rol du son pa'i mkhas pa chen po dge
NK133(po)002:2108: slong rdo rje 'dzin pa pad+ma dge 'dun grags pa'am
NK133(po)002:2109: mtshan gzhan 'od gsal snying po zhes bgyi ba dang
NK133(po)002:2110: / spar gzhi 'dri mkhan yig chos bzhi bcu sogs
NK133(po)002:2111: la mkhas pa'i smyug 'dzin gyi dbang po dge slong
NK133(po)002:2113: gzhan yang snga phyi ci rigs par zhus dag bcas
NK133(po)002:2114: kyi grogs dan pa ni thun mong ma yin pa'i
NK133(po)002:2115: gzhung lugs rnams la mkhyen rab kyi spyan dkyus yangs
NK133(po)002:2116: pa'i bla ma dam pa 'jam dbyangs dang /
NK133(po)002:2118: rigs dbon dam pa thub bstan 'od zer /
NK133(po)002:2119: snying dbon byang chub rdo rje sangs rgyas rgya mtsho /
NK133(po)002:2120: gzhan phan 'od zer rnams kyis kyang bgyis te /
NK133(po)002:2121: rab byung gzhi chog sogs so thar gyi skor rnams rang gzhung gi bka' dang bstun cing /
NK133(po)002:2122: tshigs don cung zad mi gsal ba yod rigs /
NK133(po)002:2124: gzhi 'grel chen po sogs la gtugs shing gtan la phabs /
NK133(po)002:2125: sems bskyed kyi cho ga rgyal sras lam bzang sogs dang /
NK133(po)002:2126: 'og nas 'byung ba'i rgyud sde drug gi cho ga'i rim pa ji snyed pa rnams kyang /
NK133(po)002:2127: ma phyi smin gling gi spar yod pa rnams de dang /
NK133(po)002:2128: kham dbus kyi yig rnying khung thug rnams la gzhi byams /
NK133(po)002:2129: rang rang gi rgya gzhung dang 'grel ba sogs sgo bstun nas legs par zhus shing /
NK133(po)002:2130: dogs gnas che ba rnams rje nyid kyi spyan sngar phabs te /
NK133(po)002:2131: sngon rjes kyi 'jug pa rnam dbye tshig phrad bcas sum rtags sogs kyis gzhung dang mthun par bgyis /
NK133(po)002:2132: mi bcos su mi rung ba'i tshig don gyi cha la skyon zhugs pa rnams legs par bcos /
NK133(po)002:2134: sdeb sbyor gyi tshul cung zad mi 'dra yang don la skyon med pa rnams rang sor bzhag /
NK133(po)002:2135: sngags tshig phal skad rigs mi 'dra ba dang /
NK133(po)002:2136: bcos mi nus pa rnams dpe mthun mang ba dbang btsan du byas /
NK133(po)002:2137: gzhan sngags btu dang legs sbyar gyi gzhung rnams la brten nas dag par bsgrub /
NK133(po)002:2138: mchan bu dkyus shor sogs ma dag pa ngos gsal
NK133(po)002:2139: rnams dor te shin tu dag par gtan la phabs
NK133(po)002:2140: cing rnam par dpyod pa'i blo gros dang ldan pa
NK133(po)002:2141: dag gis yid rton par 'os pa'i gnas su bgyis
NK133(po)002:2142: pa yin no // de ltar ma phyi rnams zhus dag zin pa dang /
NK133(po)002:2143: spar gzhi bris nas yig mkhan so sos zhus dag lan re dang /
NK133(po)002:2144: zhus dag mkhan po rnams kyis lan gnyis rer zhus /
NK133(po)002:2145: spar du bsgrub zin nas kyang lan grangs du mar
NK133(po)002:2146: zhib tig bgyis te dag par bsgrubs pa yin la
NK133(po)002:2160: 12 bu shig 13bcas bcu gsum tsam gyis shing sbrul bar la snga phyi ci rigs su bskos shing /
NK133(po)002:2161: de dag gi tshe nar mar sbur ba'i bza' btung dang /
NK133(po)002:2162: thog tha bar gyi chos ston sogs sbyor ba spyi
NK133(po)002:2163: gnyer gyi las 'dzin rje nyid kyi nye gnas dge
NK133(po)002:2164: slong rdo rje 'dzin pa pad+ma dar rgyas kyis bgyis
NK133(po)002:2165: shing / spar shing dang shog rin yon 'bul bcas
NK133(po)002:2166: la zhib tshags mi bgrang par rags pa zhig bsdoms
NK133(po)002:2167: shing / pas / bzang ja spob rtse stong phrag gcig lhag tsam zhig song bas mtshon /
NK133(po)002:2168: nam yang zhum pa med pa'i snying stobs chen po'i
NK133(po)002:2169: phyag gis gtong ba'i sgo 'phar yangs por phyes pas
NK133(po)002:2170: / las tshan rnams kyang so so'i bsam pa yongs
NK133(po)002:2171: su rdzogs shing dga' spro'i dpal la spyod par gyur
NK133(po)002:2172: / to // gsum pa zhal byang dngos la /
NK133(po)002:2173: ji ltar 'god pa'i go rim phal cher yas babs kyi lugs su bkod pa mang yang /
NK133(po)002:2175: dpal gsang ba'i snying po las /
NK133(po)002:2176: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK133(po)002:2177: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK133(po)002:2178: zhes sa dang lam gyi rnam par bzhag pa thams
NK133(po)002:2179: cad mthar thug gsang ba'i snying po rang bzhin rdzogs
NK133(po)002:2180: pa chen por 'jug pa'i lam stegs su gsungs shing
NK133(po)002:2181: / der ji ltar dkri ba'i tshul yang phur pa zhe sdang khros pa'i rgyud las /
NK133(po)002:2182: so sor thar pa dang por sbyin //
NK133(po)002:2183: de la nyan thos chos rnams bstan //
NK133(po)002:2184: de nas byang chub sdom chen sbyin //
NK133(po)002:2185: de la dbu ma'i chos rnams bshad //
NK133(po)002:2186: mthar ni 'bras bu theg chen gyi //
NK133(po)002:2189: kyee rdo rje brtags pa phyi ma'i le'u las /
NK133(po)002:2190: dang por gso sbyong sbyin par bya //
NK133(po)002:2191: de rjes bslab pa'i gnas bcu nyid //
NK133(po)002:2192: de la bye brag smra ba bstan //
NK133(po)002:2193: mdo sde pa'ang de bzhin no //
NK133(po)002:2194: de nas rnal 'byor spyod pa nyid //
NK133(po)002:2195: de'i rjes su dbu ma bstan //
NK133(po)002:2196: sngags kyi rim pa kun shes nas //
NK133(po)002:2197: de rjes kye yi rdo rje bstan //
NK133(po)002:2198: slob mas gus pas blang nas ni //
NK133(po)002:2202: lam du ji ltar 'jug pa'i rim pa dang mtshungs par bkod pa yin te /
NK133(po)002:2203: dpal mgon klu sgrub zhabs kyis /
NK133(po)002:2204: thabs 'di rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis //
NK133(po)002:2205: skas kyi gdang bu lta bur bstan //
NK133(po)002:2207: de la 'dir rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang 'bras bu rdo rje theg pa'i phyogs gnyis las /
NK133(po)002:2208: dang po la'ang bstan pa'i gzhi ma 'dul ba so thar gyi rnams ni rim bzhin /
NK133(po)002:2209: glegs bam dang po ka pa la /
NK133(po)002:2210: so sor thar pa'i sdom rgyun gsol 'debs ngag dbang
NK133(po)002:2211: blo bzang rgya mtshos mdzad pa la lo chen dang
NK133(po)002:2212: rje bla mas kha skong bgyis pa /
NK133(po)002:2213: khyim pa rjes 'dzin gyi cho ga thar lam rab gsal 'gyur med rdo rjes mdzad pa /
NK133(po)002:2214: bsnyen gnas len pa'i cho ga mdo don gsal ba rje bla mas mdzad pa /
NK133(po)002:2215: rab byung gzhi'i cho ga rin chen them skas d+harma
NK133(po)002:2216: sh+r+ais sbyar ba dus brjod kyi re'u mig dang bcas
NK133(po)002:2217: pa / bslab pa yongs su sbyong ba'i gzhi gsum
NK133(po)002:2218: gyi cho ga thar gling du bgrod pa'i gru chen
NK133(po)002:2219: d+harma sh+r+ais sbyar ba dus nges pa'i gso sbyong gi
NK133(po)002:2220: 'das lus brjod tshul gyi re'u mig dang bcas pa
NK133(po)002:2221: pa / / dge slong pha'i so sor thar pa'i
NK133(po)002:2222: mdo gzhi thams cad yod par smra ba'i 'dul ba
NK133(po)002:2223: 'dzin pa slob dpon dzi na mi tra dang lo
NK133(po)002:2224: ts+aa ba cog ro klu'i rgyal mtshan gyis bsgyur ba
NK133(po)002:2225: pa / / rnams so // rnam mkhyen lam gyi
NK133(po)002:2226: dngos gzhi theg chen sems bskyed kyi phrin chog skor
NK133(po)002:2228: sems bskyed kyi brgyud pa'i gsol 'debs 'gyur med rdo
NK133(po)002:2229: rje sbyar ba la rje bla mas kha skong mdzad
NK133(po)002:2231: theg pa chen po dbu ma lugs kyi sems bskyed
NK133(po)002:2232: kyi cho ga rgyal sras lam bzang 'gyur med rdo
NK133(po)002:2234: rjes mdzad pa / de'i bslab bya ston pa byang
NK133(po)002:2235: chub sems dpa'i spyod pa la 'jug pa slob dpon
NK133(po)002:2236: zhi ba lhas mdzad pa pan+di ta sarba dz+ny+aa de
NK133(po)002:2238: rjes mdzad pa / ba dang / lo ts+aa ba
NK133(po)002:2239: dpal brtsegs kyis bsgyur ba rnams so //
NK133(po)002:2240: gnyis pa thabs kyis che ba 'bras bu rdo rje theg pa'i skor la'ang /
NK133(po)002:2241: spyir rgyud sde bzhi la nang gses kyis dbye bas
NK133(po)002:2242: bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhig bzhugs pas 'di tsam
NK133(po)002:2243: zhes phyogs gcig tu tshad bzung bar mi nus kyang
NK133(po)002:2244: dgos pa'i dbang gis rgyud sde so so'i gzhung tshad
NK133(po)002:2246: ye shes rdo rje kun las btus pa'i rgyud las /
NK133(po)002:2247: rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud kyi ming stong phrag bcu
NK133(po)002:2248: gnyis zhes bya ba ste rgyas par byas na grangs
NK133(po)002:2249: med do // gnyis ka'i rgyud stong phrag drug go //
NK133(po)002:2250: spyod pa'i rgyud stong phrag drug go //
NK133(po)002:2251: bya ba'i rgyud stong phrag bzhi'o //
NK133(po)002:2253: de yang rags pa tsam las zhib par na /
NK133(po)002:2254: bya ba'i rgyud kyi de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs gcig bu la'ang /
NK133(po)002:2256: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi rgyud sde'i tshad /
NK133(po)002:2257: 'bum phrag lnga dang bye ba phrag gsum dag /
NK133(po)002:2259: de bzhin du rnal 'byor bla med kho na'i rgyud kyang /
NK133(po)002:2261: rnal 'byor rgyud rnams kyi ni tshad //
NK133(po)002:2262: bye ba phrag ni drug tu nges //
NK133(po)002:2263: de bzhin rnal 'byor ma rgyud grangs //
NK133(po)002:2264: bye ba phrag ni bcu drug grags //
NK133(po)002:2265: zhes sogs dpag tu med par gsungs pa de rnams kyang mdor bsdu na /
NK133(po)002:2266: gsang sngags phyi nang gi rim pa gnyis su 'du ba las /
NK133(po)002:2267: phyi rgyud la yang bya spyod rnal 'byor gyi sde gsum du dbye zhing /
NK133(po)002:2268: bya rgyud la nang gses rigs kyi sgo nas dbye bas sgo drug tu 'gyur /
NK133(po)002:2271: rigs kyi bdag po sogs kyis dbye bas mang zhig mchis pa las /
NK133(po)002:2272: 'dir de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi gtso bo'i phyogs
NK133(po)002:2273: su gtogs pa'i rgyud sde'i dgongs pa 'khrul med du
NK133(po)002:2274: phyungs ba'i phrin chog skor la /
NK133(po)002:2275: bde gshegs sman rgyal bdun gyi mchod pa'i cho ga zhi ba 'tsho'i lugs /
NK133(po)002:2276: ngag dbang blo bzang rgya mtshos chog khrigs su btabs pa /
NK133(po)002:2277: yid bzhin dbang rgyal zhes bya ba /
NK133(po)002:2278: glegs bam gnyis pa kha pa la /
NK133(po)002:2279: 'od zer dri ma med pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho
NK133(po)002:2280: ga 'chi med 'byung ba bu ston rin chen grub
NK133(po)002:2282: 'od zer dri med kyi dkyil chog gi lhan thabs
NK133(po)002:2283: dbang chog dang bcas pa mun sel nyin byed snang
NK133(po)002:2284: ba dang / 'od zer dri med kyi dkyil chog
NK133(po)002:2285: gi kha skong dbang chog bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun zha
NK133(po)002:2286: lu ba bsod mchog gis mdzad pa /
NK133(po)002:2287: gtsug tor dri ma med pa lha lnga'i cho ga
NK133(po)002:2288: rin chen bsam 'phel zhes bya zha lu ba rin
NK133(po)002:2289: chen bsod nams mchog grub kyis mdzad pa dang /
NK133(po)002:2290: dri med rnam gnyis kyi gzungs la brten te mchod
NK133(po)002:2291: rten bzhengs pa'i nye bar mkho ba'i cho ga bklag
NK133(po)002:2292: pas grub pa lo chen d+harma sh+r+ais mdzad pa rnams
NK133(po)002:2293: so // skabs 'dir spyod pa'i rgyud las rnam snang mngon byang dang /
NK133(po)002:2294: rnal 'byor gyi rgyud las ngan song sbyong rgyud sogs
NK133(po)002:2295: kyi phrin chog 'god par 'os kyang sngon chad rang
NK133(po)002:2296: lugs kyi chog khrigs ma byung bas /
NK133(po)002:2297: slar bsgrigs zin pa dang 'dir 'dzud dgos shing /
NK133(po)002:2298: rang gzhung 'dus mdo'i yan lag gi cho ga dag
NK133(po)002:2299: ni 'og tu de nyid kyi skabs su gsal ba
NK133(po)002:2300: ltar ro // gnyis pa gsang chen bla na med pa nang gi rgyud la yang /
NK133(po)002:2301: thabs bskyed pa'i rim pa gtso bor ston pa rgyud ma h+aa yo ga /
NK133(po)002:2302: shes rab rdzogs pa'i rim pa gtso bor ston pa lung a nu yo ga /
NK133(po)002:2303: brjod bral gnyis su med pa'i ye shes gtso bor
NK133(po)002:2304: ston pa man ngag a ti yo ga ste gsum
NK133(po)002:2305: las / dang po ma h+aa yo ga'i skor la'ang /
NK133(po)002:2306: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i gzhi dang rtsa bar gyur pa'i rgyud sde lnga /
NK133(po)002:2307: sgrub pa lag len du ston pa rol ba'i rgyud sde lnga /
NK133(po)002:2308: spyod pa'i yan lag tu 'gro ba'i rgyud sde lnga /
NK133(po)002:2309: ma tshang kha skong gi rgyud sde gnyis /
NK133(po)002:2310: thams cad la khyab pa'i spyi rgyud chen po gcig dang bco brgyad yod pa las /
NK133(po)002:2311: dang po rtsa ba'i rgyud sde lnga'i nang tshan sku'i
NK133(po)002:2312: rgyud dpal sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam par sbyor ba'i
NK133(po)002:2314: mnyam sbyor gyi brgyud 'debs rje bla mas mdzad pa /
NK133(po)002:2315: dpal sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam par sbyor ba rigs bsdus pa'i sgrub thabs bde chen 'dod 'jo /
NK133(po)002:2316: de'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga kun tu bzang po'i zhal lung /
NK133(po)002:2317: dbang gi cho ga byin rlabs char 'bebs bcas gter
NK133(po)002:2318: chen 'gyur med rdo rjes khrigs su bsdebs pa rnams
NK133(po)002:2319: so // gnyis pa gsung gi rgyud zla gsang thig le /
NK133(po)002:2320: gsum pa thugs kyi rgyud gsang ba 'dus pa /
NK133(po)002:2321: bzhi pa yon tan gyi rgyud dpal mchog dang po /
NK133(po)002:2322: lnga pa phrin las kyi rgyud karma m+aa le rnams
NK133(po)002:2323: la sngar chog khrigs ma byung bas slar 'dir 'dzud
NK133(po)002:2324: dgos so // gnyis pa rol pa'i rgyud sde lnga las /
NK133(po)002:2325: sku gshin rje rol pa'i phrin chog gi skor la'ang gnyis las /
NK133(po)002:2326: dang po kha thun nag po'i skor la /
NK133(po)002:2327: gshin rje kha thun gyi ba rgyud 'debs rje bla mas mdzad pa /
NK133(po)002:2328: 'jam dpal gshin rje kha thun nag po'i sgrub thabs bklag pas don 'grub /
NK133(po)002:2329: de'i dkyil chog bcas rgyal sras rin chen rnam par
NK133(po)002:2330: rgyal ba'i chog khrigs kha thun gyi dbang chu bka'
NK133(po)002:2331: ma slob dpon pad+mas mdzad pa /
NK133(po)002:2332: yang kha thun rdo rje'i dbang chu 'jam dpal bshes
NK133(po)002:2333: gnyen gyis mdzad pa la kun mkhyen ri khrod pa
NK133(po)002:2334: ngag dbang grags pas chog khrigs bgyis pa rnams so
NK133(po)002:2335: // gnyis pa gnubs lugs gshin rje ru mtshon dmar po'i skor la /
NK133(po)002:2336: gshed dmar brgyud 'debs rje bla mas mdzad pa /
NK133(po)002:2337: gshin rje gshed dmar po'i las byang bdud dpung mthar
NK133(po)002:2338: byed gter chen 'gyur med rdo rje'i chog khrigs de'i
NK133(po)002:2339: dkyil chog dngos grub len pa bcas rgyal sras rin
NK133(po)002:2340: chen rnam par rgyal ba'i chog khrigs /
NK133(po)002:2341: 'jam dpal gshi na rje gshed dmar po'i phrin las
NK133(po)002:2342: rdo rje rtse brgya ba log rtog bdud dpung pham
NK133(po)002:2343: byed dbang chog dang bcas pa mkhan chen o d+ai
NK133(po)002:2344: y+aa na'i chog khrigs rnams so //
NK133(po)002:2345: gnyis pa gsung rta mchog rol pa'i phrin chog skor rnams slad nas 'dir 'dzud dgos so //
NK133(po)002:2346: glegs bam gsum pa ga pa la /
NK133(po)002:2347: gsum pa thugs he ru ka rol ba'i phrin chog skor la /
NK133(po)002:2348: yang dag gi brgyud 'debs rje bla mas mdzad pa /
NK133(po)002:2349: dpal yang dag he ru ka'i sgrub thabs bde chen thig le /
NK133(po)002:2350: de'i dkyil chog bdud rtsi'i nying khu /
NK133(po)002:2351: dpal chen yang dag lha dgu'i dbang chog bde chen
NK133(po)002:2352: 'jug ngogs bcas gter chen 'gyur med rdo rje'i chog
NK133(po)002:2353: khrigs rnams so // bzhi pa yon tan bdud rtsi
NK133(po)002:2354: rol ba'i phrin chog skor rnams slad nas 'dir 'dzud
NK133(po)002:2355: khrigs rnams so // dgos / lnga pa phrin las
NK133(po)002:2356: phur pa rol pa'i phrin chog skor la gnyis las
NK133(po)002:2357: khrigs rnams so // dgos / / dang po rog lugs su grags pa'i skor la /
NK133(po)002:2358: rog lugs phur pa'i brgyud 'debs d+harma sh+r+ais mdzad pa la rje bla mas kha skong bgyis pa /
NK133(po)002:2359: rdo rje phur pa rog lugs kyi sgrub thabs dngos grub char 'bebs /
NK133(po)002:2360: stod las kyi sgrub khog bde chen bdud rtsi'i bcud len /
NK133(po)002:2361: dbang chog bde chen mchog ster /
NK133(po)002:2362: smad las kyi sgrub khog gdug can mthar byed rdo
NK133(po)002:2363: rje 'bar ba'i 'khrul 'khor bcas lo chen d+harma sh+r+ai'i
NK133(po)002:2365: gnyis pa rong zom lugs kyi skor la /
NK133(po)002:2366: rong zom phur pa'i brgyud 'debs rje bla mas mdzad pa /
NK133(po)002:2367: rdo rje phur pa rong lugs kyi las byang dngos grub rgya mtsho'i snying po /
NK133(po)002:2368: de'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga bcas rin chen rnam rgyal gyi chog khrigs /
NK133(po)002:2369: dbang gi cho ga jo bo lang lab kyis bsgrigs pa rnams so //
NK133(po)002:2370: gsum pa spyod pa'i yan lag tu 'gro ba'i rgyud sde lnga dang /
NK133(po)002:2371: bzhi pa ma tshang kha skong gi rgyud sde gnyis
NK133(po)002:2372: bcas kyi phrin chog skor rnams slad nas 'dir 'dzud
NK133(po)002:2373: dgos so // glegs bam bzhi pa nga pa la /
NK133(po)002:2374: lnga pa spyi rgyud sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i phrin chog skor la /
NK133(po)002:2375: zhi khro thun mong gi brgyud 'debs 'gyur med rdo
NK133(po)002:2376: rjes mdzad pa la rje bla mas kha skong mdzad
NK133(po)002:2377: pa / rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba
NK133(po)002:2378: zhi ba 'bring po'i sgrub thabs ye shes char 'bebs
NK133(po)002:2379: pa / / de'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga rin chen phreng ba /
NK133(po)002:2380: dbang gi cho ga dkyil 'khor rgya mtshor 'jug pa'i
NK133(po)002:2381: gru chen bcas gter chen 'gyur med rdo rjes chog
NK133(po)002:2382: khrigs rnams so // sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba khro bo
NK133(po)002:2383: he ru ka'i dkyil 'khor bsdus pa'i sgrub thabs bde
NK133(po)002:2384: khrigs rnams so // chen char 'bebs / de'i dkyil
NK133(po)002:2385: 'khor gyi cho ga rdo rje'i phreng ba bcas gter
NK133(po)002:2387: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba khro bo'i dbang gi cho ga
NK133(po)002:2388: khrag 'thung rdo rje'i gad rgyangs zhes pa pad+ma dgyes
NK133(po)002:2389: pa 'gyur med rgya mtshos chog khrigs bgyis pa /
NK133(po)002:2390: zhi khro thun mong gi dbang gi rgyug byang rnams so //
NK133(po)002:2391: gzhan yang de'i cha lag tu gtogs pa /
NK133(po)002:2392: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba'i lugs kyi sgrub skor la /
NK133(po)002:2393: tshe sgrub kyi brgyud 'debs rje bla mas mdzad pa /
NK133(po)002:2394: bcom ldan 'das tshe dpag tu med pa'i sgrub thabs 'chi med mchog ster /
NK133(po)002:2395: de'i dbang gi cho ga bcas gter chen gyis khrigs ma rnams so //
NK133(po)002:2396: glegs bam lnga pa ca pa la /
NK133(po)002:2397: rnal 'byor spyi khrus mtshams med lnga sbyong gi phrin chog skor la /
NK133(po)002:2398: dong sprug gi brgyud 'debs gter chen gyis mdzad pa la rje bla mas kha skong bgyis pa /
NK133(po)002:2399: na rag dong sprug zhi khro khrom dkrug gi las byang 'khor ba kun grol /
NK133(po)002:2400: yang zhi ba pad+ma brgya ldan gyi las byang bde chen lam bzang bcas gter chen gyis khrigs ma /
NK133(po)002:2402: na raka dong sprug dbang gi mtshams sbyor bde chen
NK133(po)002:2403: lam bzang mi 'gyur dpal sgron gyis mdzad pa rnams
NK133(po)002:2404: so // de dag kun gyi rjes 'brel du 'gro ba'i phrin las sna tshog sa kyi skor la /
NK133(po)002:2405: ma h+aa yo ga'i dbang gi rgyug byang rje bla mas mdzad pa /
NK133(po)002:2406: gshin po rjes 'dzin gyi cho ga thar pa'i myur lam gter chen gyis mdzad pa /
NK133(po)002:2407: gtor ma cha gsum gyi cho ga gter chen gyis mdzad pa /
NK133(po)002:2408: rgyud lung la brten pa'i las bzhi'i sbyin sreg ngag
NK133(po)002:2409: 'don klag chog mar byas pa 'dod ster dbang gi
NK133(po)002:2410: rgyal po d+harma sh+r+ais sbyar ba /
NK133(po)002:2411: rten gsum rab tu gnas pa'i cho ga dge legs
NK133(po)002:2412: 'dod 'jo gter chen 'gyur med rdo rjes mdzad pa
NK133(po)002:2413: rnams so // rgyud kyi bka' srung gi skor la /
NK133(po)002:2414: legs ldan tshogs kyi bdag po'i gong gnon du /
NK133(po)002:2415: dgos pa'i dbang gis 'dir bzhag pa drag dmar 'o bran lugs kyi skor la /
NK133(po)002:2416: de'i brgyud 'debs rje bla mas mdzad pa /
NK133(po)002:2417: sgrub thabs dbang chog dang bcas pa 'dod 'jo las phyung pa gter chen gyis chog khrigs rnams so //
NK133(po)002:2418: dpal legs ldan nag po'i brgyud 'debs rje bla mas mdzad pa /
NK133(po)002:2419: legs ldan tshogs kyi bdag po'i sgrub thabs las bzhi'i
NK133(po)002:2420: rnam rol gter chen 'gyur med rdo rjes mdzad pa
NK133(po)002:2421: / yang legs ldan gyi sgrub thabs dbang chog dang
NK133(po)002:2422: bcas pa 'dod bum las byung ba gter chen gyis
NK133(po)002:2424: rgyud mgon trag shad kyi phrin chog 'dir 'dzud dgos /
NK133(po)002:2425: bka' gter zung 'jug gi mgon po bing dang stag
NK133(po)002:2426: zhon bcas so so'i sgrub thabs dbang chog dang bcas
NK133(po)002:2427: pa / re ti rang byung rgyal mo'i sgrub thabs dbang chog dang bcas pa /
NK133(po)002:2428: rnam sras drag po rta sngon can gyi sgrub thabs
NK133(po)002:2429: dbang chog dang bcas pa de rnams 'dod 'jo bum
NK133(po)002:2430: bzang las phyung ba gter chen rin po che'i chog
NK133(po)002:2431: khrigs skor ro // gnyis pa lung a nu yo ga'i phyogs la /
NK133(po)002:2432: rtsa rgyud kun 'dus rig pa dang /
NK133(po)002:2433: bshad rgyud spyi mdo dgongs 'dus sogs kyi gzhung don dang /
NK133(po)002:2434: bde ba gsal mdzad kyi las tho sogs man ngag gi rgyun rnams phyogs gcig tu bsdebs nas /
NK133(po)002:2436: yan lag theg brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor so sor phye
NK133(po)002:2437: nas dbang bskur ba'i thabs 'dus pa mdo dbang chen
NK133(po)002:2439: glegs bam drug pa cha pa la /
NK133(po)002:2440: 'dus pa mdo'i dbang gi spyi don rgyud lung man
NK133(po)002:2441: ngag gi gnad gsal byed sgron me d+harma sh+r+ais mdzad
NK133(po)002:2442: pa / 'dus mdo'i brgyud 'debs gter chen gyis mdzad pa la rje bla mas kha skong bgyis pa /
NK133(po)002:2443: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i sgrub thabs dngos grub char 'bebs gter chen gyis mdzad pa /
NK133(po)002:2444: 'dus pa mdo'i sgrub khog rin chen 'od kyi snang ba d+harma sh+r+ais mdzad pa rnams so //
NK133(po)002:2445: glegs bam bdun pa ja pa la /
NK133(po)002:2446: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga dri
NK133(po)002:2447: med 'od kyi phreng ba gter chen gyis mdzad pa
NK133(po)002:2448: / yan lag gi dkyil 'khor rnams kyi sgrub dkyil dngos grub 'dod 'jo /
NK133(po)002:2449: 'dus mdo'i cho ga'i zur 'debs dpag bsam snye ma bcas d+harma sh+r+ais mdzad pa rnams so //
NK133(po)002:2450: glegs bam brgyad pa nya pa la /
NK133(po)002:2451: 'dus pa mdo'i dbang gi cho ga rdo rje'i them skas d+harma sh+r+ais mdzad pa bzhugs so //
NK133(po)002:2452: gsum pa man ngag a ti yo ga rdzogs pa chen po sems phyogs kyi skor la /
NK133(po)002:2453: sems klong man ngag gi sde gsum so so'i nang
NK133(po)002:2454: gses kyis dbye bas klong dgu bam po nyi khri
NK133(po)002:2455: chig stong dang / rgyud 'bum phrag drug cu rtsa
NK133(po)002:2456: bzhi sogs dpag tu med pa zhig bzhugs pa las
NK133(po)002:2457: chig stong dang / / dang po sems phyogs su
NK133(po)002:2458: gtogs pa'i man ngag sgrub phrin gyi rim pa rgya
NK133(po)002:2459: bod mkhas pa mi bzhi'i dgongs nyams gcig tu dril
NK133(po)002:2460: pa bka' brgyad bka' ma rdzong 'phrang du grags pa'i
NK133(po)002:2461: chig stong dang / / skor ni / glegs bam dgu pa ta pa la /
NK133(po)002:2462: rdzong 'phrang gi rgyud 'debs rje bla mas mdzad pa /
NK133(po)002:2463: 'phrin las kyi chog khrigs he ru ka'i dgongs rgyan
NK133(po)002:2464: ces bya ba kahthoga pa 'gyur med tshe dbang mchog
NK133(po)002:2467: dbang bskur rdo rje'i phreng ba le'u bcu gsum pa
NK133(po)002:2468: u rgyan gyi mkhan po pad+ma 'byung gnas kyis sbyar
NK133(po)002:2469: ba rnams so // sems sde dngos la rdzogs pa
NK133(po)002:2470: chen po'i sems sde'i brgyud 'debs blo gros rgyal mtshan
NK133(po)002:2471: dpal bzang pos mdzad pa la rje bla mas kha
NK133(po)002:2472: ba rnams so // skong bgyis pa / byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po dang /
NK133(po)002:2473: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che /
NK133(po)002:2475: rig pa'i khu byug sogs sems sde ma bu bco
NK133(po)002:2476: brgyad kyi dgongs pa ngo sprod pa'i tha bas rig
NK133(po)002:2477: pa rtsal gyi dbang bco brgyad bskur ba'i chog khrigs
NK133(po)002:2478: bla ma'i zhal gdams zhes bya ba rgyug byang smon
NK133(po)002:2479: lam dang bcas pa g.yung ston rdo rje dpal bzang
NK133(po)002:2481: klong sde rdo rje zam pa'i byin rlabs kyi cho
NK133(po)002:2482: ga rgyas pa khrigs su byas pa kahthoga pa 'gyur
NK133(po)002:2483: med tshe dbang mchog grub kyis mdzad pa /
NK133(po)002:2484: man ngag sde rgyud bcu bdun sogs kyi phrin chog rnams kyang slad nas 'god dgos pa yin no //
NK133(po)002:2485: de ltar na spyir theg rim dgu dang /
NK133(po)002:2486: bye brag nang rgyud bka' ma mdo sgyu sems gsum
NK133(po)002:2487: gyi phyogs su gtogs pa'i phrin chog mtha' dag gi
NK133(po)002:2488: rgyun deng sang ljongs 'dir yod do cog phal che
NK133(po)002:2489: ba zhig 'dir bzhugs pa yin no //
NK133(po)002:2490: bka' ma theg rim dgu'i phrin chog rnams kyi dkar
NK133(po)002:2491: chag yid bzhin dbang gi rgyal po'i bang mdzod las
NK133(po)002:2492: ji ltar spar du sgrub tshul bzhugs byang dkar chag
NK133(po)002:2493: dngos 'god pa'i skabs te gnyis pa'o ////
NK133(po)002:2494: don gsum pa de ltar bsgrub pa'i dgos ched phan
NK133(po)002:2495: yon bsngo smon shis brjod dang bcas pa la bzhi
NK133(po)002:2496: las / dang po dgos ched ni /
NK133(po)002:2497: deng sang gi dus 'dir spyir rgyal ba'i bstan pa
NK133(po)002:2498: la bshad sgrub kyis bya ba mdzad pa'i gang zag
NK133(po)002:2499: phyogs thams cad na dkon zhing /
NK133(po)002:2500: khyad par du rgyal ba gong ma du ma'i mtshan
NK133(po)002:2501: snyan gyi cod pan gtsug tu dpyangs nas bstan 'dzin
NK133(po)002:2502: gyi skyes bur rlom pa'i chen po'i go sa 'dzin
NK133(po)002:2503: pa dag kyang / 'dir snang srid pa'i che thabs kho na lhur bzhes nas /
NK133(po)002:2504: gser dngul gyis bang mdzod 'gengs pa dang /
NK133(po)002:2505: rta nor gyis ri lung gang ba /
NK133(po)002:2506: che btsan gyi grags pa sgrub pa sogs mi dpon chen po'i bya bas thugs g.yengs te /
NK133(po)002:2507: rang lugs kyi bstan pa dngos la 'khor lo gsum
NK133(po)002:2508: gyis mdzad pas 'dzin skyongs spel ba'i phrin las sgrub
NK133(po)002:2509: dgos rgyu rnams gal chung g.yas chung du lus pa
NK133(po)002:2510: la brten nas / thub pa'i lung rtogs kyi bstan
NK133(po)002:2511: pa rin po spyi'i rnam bzhag yang gzugs brnyan tsam
NK133(po)002:2513: yang dgos snga 'gyur bka' ma'i smin grol gyi rgyun rnams ni phal cher 'ja' lus grub zin cing /
NK133(po)002:2514: cung zad re yod pa rnams kyang snums zad kyi mar me ltar gyur pa'i skabs 'dir /
NK133(po)002:2515: rje btsun chos kyi rgyal po 'di nyid kyi thugs dgongs la /
NK133(po)002:2516: 'di ltar mtha' dang dbus med pa'i srid pa'i rgya
NK133(po)002:2517: mtsho chen por las nyon rnam smin gyi sdug bsngal
NK133(po)002:2518: drag po'i dba' la 'phyan pa'i mtha' yas pa'i skye
NK133(po)002:2519: dgu rnams la gnas skabs kyi phan pa dang mthar
NK133(po)002:2520: thug gi bde ba 'byung ba'i gzhir gyur pa ni
NK133(po)002:2521: rgyal ba'i bstan pa rin po che kho na yin
NK133(po)002:2522: / de nyid yun ring du gnas pa'ang /
NK133(po)002:2523: bstan 'dzin gyi skyes bu rnams la rag las shing /
NK133(po)002:2524: bstan 'dzin gyi skyes bu zhes pa'ang thub pa'i bstan
NK133(po)002:2525: pa la 'dzin skyong spel ba'i phrin las mdzad pa'i
NK133(po)002:2526: sgo nas bzhag dgos par snang na yang /
NK133(po)002:2528: dbang lung dang dpe rgyun dkon rigs tsam yang btsal
NK133(po)002:2529: dgos pa'i thugs dgongs mnga' ba nam lang gi skar
NK133(po)002:2531: smin grol gyi gdam pa zab mo rnams kyang khron pas skom pa ded pa'i dpes /
NK133(po)002:2532: mas bu chung la nu zho bsnyod pa ltar byas kyang /
NK133(po)002:2533: da dung log rtog dang yul lugs ngan pa'i gshis
NK133(po)002:2534: la goms pas pha phor gtsang zhen gyi blos phyin
NK133(po)002:2535: ci log gi grub mtha' chags sdang gi gtam gyis
NK133(po)002:2536: 'dzin pa kho na las mi 'dug pas /
NK133(po)002:2537: ji ltar bgyis na rgyal ba'i bstan pa rin po
NK133(po)002:2538: che cung zad re gnas pa'i rgyur 'gyur snyam du
NK133(po)002:2539: dgongs pa las / 'di ltar bka' ma theg rim
NK133(po)002:2540: dgu'i phrin chog mtha' dag phyogs gcig tu bsdebs nas
NK133(po)002:2541: glegs bam mi zad pa'i yi ge'i phyi mo spar
NK133(po)002:2542: gyi 'du byed du bsgrubs te bzhag na /
NK133(po)002:2543: tshegs med par glegs bam gyi rgyun mang por 'phel ba dang /
NK133(po)002:2544: tshul 'di la mos pa rnams kyis smin grol gyi rgyun rnyed sla ba dang /
NK133(po)002:2545: de la brten nas klog pa thos bsam dang /
NK133(po)002:2547: bya ba las kyi 'khor lo sogs 'byung zhing /
NK133(po)002:2548: tshul des rgyal bstan spyi dang bye brag snga 'gyur
NK133(po)002:2549: bka' ma'i skor rnams kyang 'jig rten gyi khams su
NK133(po)002:2550: yun ring zhig tu gnas pa'i rgyu dang rkyen du
NK133(po)002:2552: dgos pa'i gtso bo ni phan bde'i 'byung gnas rgyal
NK133(po)002:2553: bstan rin po che mi nyams shing 'phel ba'i ched
NK133(po)002:2555: de'i mthus lus can spyi dang bye brag bod chen
NK133(po)002:2556: po'i ljongs 'dir 'khod pa'i skye dgu mtha' dag gnas
NK133(po)002:2557: skabs lha dang mi'i dpal la longs spyod nas /
NK133(po)002:2558: mthar thug rnam grol zhi ba mchog gi go 'phang mngon du byed pa dang /
NK133(po)002:2560: rig 'dzin gong ma rnams kyi dgongs pa yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
NK133(po)002:2561: khams dbus kyi skyes chen du mas bskul ba don yod pa dang /
NK133(po)002:2562: rgyal ba'i sras kyi mdzad pa rlab po che sgrub pa dang /
NK133(po)002:2563: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba rnams kyi dam pa'i chos 'dzin pa dang /
NK133(po)002:2564: rjes 'jug slob ma'i tshogs la smin grol gyi pha phog 'bog pa dang /
NK133(po)002:2565: 'byor ldan sbyin pa'i bdag po rnams kyi bsod nams
NK133(po)002:2566: kyi tshogs gong nas gong du spel ba sogs dgos
NK133(po)002:2567: pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa la thugs gzhol nas
NK133(po)002:2568: sngon rabs du ma'i thugs bskyed dang smon lam dus
NK133(po)002:2569: su babs pa'i mngon rtogs gsal bor rol pa yin
NK133(po)002:2570: te / bzang po spyod pa las /
NK133(po)002:2571: rgyal ba rnams kyi dam pa'i chos 'dzin cing //
NK133(po)002:2572: byang chub spyod pa kun tu snang bar byed //
NK133(po)002:2574: snga 'gyur pun+da r+ai ka'i rgyud las /
NK133(po)002:2575: srid pa las dang rkyen gyi dbang gyur te //
NK133(po)002:2576: gang dang gang du dam chos 'jig pa der //
NK133(po)002:2577: me tshogs spu gri'i so yang brgal nas ni //
NK133(po)002:2578: phyi mthar thug gi bar du dam chos bzung //
NK133(po)002:2581: spyir bde bar gshegs pa'i gsung rab rnams glegs bam
NK133(po)002:2582: la bris te rim gro bgyis pa la yang phan
NK133(po)002:2584: sdud pa tshigs su bcad pa las /
NK133(po)002:2585: la las bde gshegs yongs su mya ngan 'das pa yi //
NK133(po)002:2586: mchod rten rin chen bdun las byas shing mchod byed la //
NK133(po)002:2587: bde bar gshegs pa'i mchod rten de dag gang+g+aa yi //
NK133(po)002:2588: bye ma snyed kyi bye ba phrag stong zhig bkangs te //
NK133(po)002:2589: yongs su brtags bzung zhing rnams bye ba mtha' yas na //
NK133(po)002:2590: sems can ji snyed 'khod pa de dag thams cad kyis //
NK133(po)002:2591: las gzhan mi byed lha yi me tog spos rab dang //
NK133(po)002:2592: byug pas dus gsum bskal pa'am de bas lhag mchod pa //
NK133(po)002:2593: gang zhig gang las rnam 'dren stobs bcu 'byung 'gyur ba //
NK133(po)002:2594: bde bar gshegs kyi yum 'di glegs bam la bris te //
NK133(po)002:2595: 'chang zhing me tog byug pas bsti stang byed gyur na //
NK133(po)002:2596: mchod rten byas mchod bsod nams des ni char mi phod //
NK133(po)002:2598: de bas kyang glegs bam bgyis te gzhan la byin pa'i bsod nams khyad par du 'phags te /
NK133(po)002:2600: la las gang+g+aa klung gi bye snyed zhing rnams na //
NK133(po)002:2601: sems can ji snyed mchis kun dgra bcom nyid btul bas //
NK133(po)002:2602: gang gis shes rab pha rol phyin 'di yig bris te //
NK133(po)002:2603: sems can mchog la glegs byin bsod nams khyad par 'phags //
NK133(po)002:2605: de ltar theg chen thun mong gi mdo sde rnams las kyang phan yon mang du gsung na /
NK133(po)002:2606: de las kyang gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde zab mo
NK133(po)002:2607: rnams bris shing bcang ba'i phan yon ni tshad med
NK133(po)002:2608: de / rin po che spungs pa'i rgyud las /
NK133(po)002:2609: de yi phyir na gsang ba'i rgyud //
NK133(po)002:2611: rang rigs rnams kyi dbang thob ste //
NK133(po)002:2612: rgyud 'di bcang ba tsam gyis ni //
NK133(po)002:2614: rgyud 'di su yi bklag pa'i mi //
NK133(po)002:2615: lta ba'i don kun sems la 'char //
NK133(po)002:2616: 'di nyid su yis bris pa'i mi //
NK133(po)002:2617: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsung la rol //
NK133(po)002:2619: a ti bkod pa chen po las /
NK133(po)002:2620: gsang mchog bla na med pa 'di //
NK133(po)002:2621: mchod dang bstod pa bkur byas na //
NK133(po)002:2622: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub rnams //
NK133(po)002:2624: 'di nyid bcang ba tsam gyis kyang //
NK133(po)002:2627: khyad par bstan pa 'jig pa'i tshe dam pa'i chos
NK133(po)002:2628: bzung ba'i phan yon ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i
NK133(po)002:2629: tshul / blo gros rgya mtshos zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK133(po)002:2630: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems dang chos 'dzin dang //
NK133(po)002:2631: chos sgrub pa dang srog chags snying rje pa //
NK133(po)002:2632: chos bzhi 'di dag bsod nams mtha' yas te //
NK133(po)002:2633: de dag mtha' ni bde gshegs mi gsung ngo /
NK133(po)002:2635: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo las /
NK133(po)002:2636: gang dag phyin chad mdo sde 'di 'dzin pa //
NK133(po)002:2637: de dag rtag tu nga dang mthun pa'i sras //
NK133(po)002:2638: sangs rgyas bye bas de dag basngagasa brjod kyang //
NK133(po)002:2639: de dag basngagasa pa mthar ni phyin mi 'gyur //
NK133(po)002:2641: gang gis sangs rgyas stong rnams dang //
NK133(po)002:2642: brgya dang bye ba bgrang dag la //
NK133(po)002:2643: bskal pa gang+g+aa'i bye ma snyed //
NK133(po)002:2644: de snyed bskal par bkur ba pas //
NK133(po)002:2645: 'jig rten mgon gyis gsungs pa yi //
NK133(po)002:2646: dam chos 'jig tshe gang zhig gis //
NK133(po)002:2647: nyin dang mtshan du 'dzin byed pa //
NK133(po)002:2648: de ni bsod nams khyad par 'phags //
NK133(po)002:2650: 'jig tshe rgyal ba mchog gi chos bzung bas //
NK133(po)002:2651: mchog tu gzugs mdzes lta na sdug pa dang //
NK133(po)002:2652: skyes bu bud med lha rnams dga' ba dang //
NK133(po)002:2653: bde zhing mkhas la basngagasa shing shes rab ldan //
NK133(po)002:2654: ston pa stobs bcu mnga' ba lha yi lhas //
NK133(po)002:2655: gang gi mdun du mdo 'di rab bshad pa //
NK133(po)002:2656: mi de'i lag tu mdo sde 'di 'dra 'di //
NK133(po)002:2657: phyi ma'i dus kyi tshe na thob par 'gyur //
NK133(po)002:2659: gzhan yang 'phags pa dkon mchog brtsegs pa chen po'i chos kyi rnam grangs las kyang /
NK133(po)002:2660: de la sh+aa ri'i bu theg pa chen po la yang dag par zhugs pas /
NK133(po)002:2661: 'di lta bu'i mi bzad pa dang mi basngagasa pa dang /
NK133(po)002:2662: dam pa'i chos rab tu 'jig pa mthong nas brtson 'grus chen po'i shugs rab tu bskyed de /
NK133(po)002:2664: 'di lta bu'i mdo sde byang chub sems dpa'i sde
NK133(po)002:2665: snod kyi chos kyi rnam grangs 'di rab tu mnyan
NK133(po)002:2667: yi ger bris nas bcang bar bya /
NK133(po)002:2668: gzhan la yang go bar bya /
NK133(po)002:2669: rgya cher yang dag par rab tu bstan par bya'o //
NK133(po)002:2670: des kyang 'du shes bzhi bskyed par bya ste /
NK133(po)002:2672: bdag gi pha'i nor gyi phung po 'di rab tu 'jig par 'gyur te /
NK133(po)002:2673: gang gis phyir bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa
NK133(po)002:2674: dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK133(po)002:2675: sh+aakya thub pa des bskal pa bye ba khrag khrig
NK133(po)002:2676: brgya stong grangs med pa nas bzung ste /
NK133(po)002:2677: dka' ba spyad pa yin na /
NK133(po)002:2678: de'i phyir rab tu 'jig par mi 'gyur bar bzung bar bya /
NK133(po)002:2684: dper na sh+aa ri'i bu skyes bu zhig la bu gcig cig yod de /
NK133(po)002:2685: byams sdug yid du 'ong zhing mi mthun pa med
NK133(po)002:2686: par snang ba de g.yang sa chen por lhung bar
NK133(po)002:2687: gyur pa dang / des de lag gis bzung ste /
NK133(po)002:2688: sems can dmyal ba'i g.yang sa 'dir lhung bar ma
NK133(po)002:2689: gyur cig ces 'dzin rab tu 'dzin pa de bzhin
NK133(po)002:2690: du / sh+aa ri'i bu gang skyes bu dam pa
NK133(po)002:2691: de dag nga la dad cing chos dkon mchog bla
NK133(po)002:2692: na med pa 'di yang yongs su mi gtong zhing
NK133(po)002:2693: du / / mya ngan las 'das pa la yang
NK133(po)002:2694: re bar 'gyur ba de dag de'i dus na dam
NK133(po)002:2695: pa'i chos yongs su 'dzin par 'gyur bas ngas de
NK133(po)002:2696: dag la byang chub mchog 'di gtad par bya'o //
NK133(po)002:2698: sh+aa ri'i bu g.yul chen po'i nang na gang skye
NK133(po)002:2699: bo mang po bsrung ba'i phyir dmag gi mdun na
NK133(po)002:2700: 'dug par 'gyur ba'i sems can de dag ni nyung
NK133(po)002:2701: bar 'gyur ro // yang sh+aa ri'i bu gang dpa'
NK133(po)002:2702: ba 'os su gyur par byas pa g.yul las rnam
NK133(po)002:2703: par rgyal ba de dag de na g.yul mi bzad
NK133(po)002:2704: pa chen po'i dus na skye bo mang po'i phyir
NK133(po)002:2705: dmag gi mdun na 'dug pa de bzhin du /
NK133(po)002:2706: sh+aa ri'i bu de'i tshe dam pa'i chos 'jig par rab tu nye bar gnas pa na /
NK133(po)002:2707: gang lhag pa'i bsam pas yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa 'dod pa /
NK133(po)002:2708: dpa' ba brtson 'grus brtan par go cha sra ba
NK133(po)002:2709: bgos pa de dag brtson 'grus chen po'i stobs bskyed
NK133(po)002:2710: de bdud kyi dmag las rgyal zhing 'di lta bu'i
NK133(po)002:2711: chos dkon mchog 'di las snying po cung zad tsam
NK133(po)002:2714: sh+aa ri'i bu tshig bzhi pa'i tshigs su bcad pa
NK133(po)002:2715: gcig tsam yongs su spong ba la yangarjesa su yi
NK133(po)002:2716: rang bar mi byed cing rtsod par byed la 'di
NK133(po)002:2717: ni sangs rgyas kyis bshad pa'o zhes skye bo mang
NK133(po)002:2718: po la sgrogs shing shes par byed pa de ni
NK133(po)002:2720: da ltar gyi sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyis legs
NK133(po)002:2721: par bshad pa la rjes su yi rang ba ste
NK133(po)002:2722: / sh+aa ri'i bu de lta bu'i gang zag rnams
NK133(po)002:2723: la bsod nams kyi rnam par smin pa chung ngo
NK133(po)002:2725: nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i bsod nams kyi phung po dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
NK133(po)002:2727: sh+aa ri'i bu skyes bu dam pa de lta bu
NK133(po)002:2728: shin tu dkon te skyes bu mchog ces brjod do
NK133(po)002:2729: // skyes bu rab ces brjod de /
NK133(po)002:2730: skyes bu dpa' bo zhes brjod do //
NK133(po)002:2731: skyes bu chen po zhes brjod do //
NK133(po)002:2732: de ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i chos kyi phyogs so //
NK133(po)002:2733: de dag sder mi smra mi 'khrug go //
NK133(po)002:2734: de dag nan tan snying por byed pa ste /
NK133(po)002:2735: sh+aa ri'i bu 'chi ba'i matha'i bar du nan tan snying por bya'o //
NK133(po)002:2736: 'chi ba'i matha'i bar du dam pa'i chos yongs su bzung bar bya'o //
NK133(po)002:2737: 'chi ba'i matha'i bar du stong pa nyid la mos par bya'o //
NK133(po)002:2738: sh+aa ri'i bu chos de bzhi dang ldan na de'i tshe de'i dus na /
NK133(po)002:2739: dam pa'i chos rab tu rnam par 'jig pa'i dus /
NK133(po)002:2740: dam pa'i chos nub par 'gyur ba'i dus /
NK133(po)002:2741: tshul khrims 'chal ba'i phyogs mang ba'i dus /
NK133(po)002:2742: 'jig rten rgyangs phan pa'i gsang tshig kun tu tshol ba mang ba'i dus /
NK133(po)002:2746: nyon mongs pa snyigs ma'i dus /
NK133(po)002:2748: dus gsum la gnas par bya /
NK133(po)002:2749: 'thabs mo nye bar zhi ba la gnas par bya /
NK133(po)002:2750: sangs rgyas kyi byang chub dang 'bral bar mi 'gyur bar bya ste /
NK133(po)002:2751: sh+aa ri'i bu dus 'a di gsum la rab tu gnas par bya'o //
NK133(po)002:2753: blo gros rgya mtshos zhus pa'i mdo las kyang /
NK133(po)002:2754: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dam pa'i chos 'dzin pa //
NK133(po)002:2755: de ni de bzhin gshegs la byas bzo yin //
NK133(po)002:2756: rgyal ba rnams kyi mdzod 'dzin yid brten zhing //
NK133(po)002:2757: phyogs bcu rnams su sangs rgyas mchod pa yin //
NK133(po)002:2758: sangs rgyas spyan gyis gzigs pa'i zhing mang po //
NK133(po)002:2759: rin chen bkang ste de bzhin gshegs la phul //
NK133(po)002:2760: zad pa'i dus na ji ltar chos 'dzin ltar //
NK133(po)002:2761: bsod nams phung po de tsam 'phel ba yin //
NK133(po)002:2763: de dag rnams kyi yon tan phan yon rnams //
NK133(po)002:2764: bskal pa rgyun mi chad par brjod byas kyang //
NK133(po)002:2765: dam chos 'dzin pa'i phan yon 'di dag ni //
NK133(po)002:2766: brjod pas mtha' mar phyin par mi 'gyur ro //
NK133(po)002:2767: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK133(po)002:2768: gsum pa de lta bu'i phan yon gyi legs byas
NK133(po)002:2769: rgya chen po 'di nyid las byung ba'i bsod nams
NK133(po)002:2770: kyi dngos po gang du ji ltar bsngo ba'i tshul
NK133(po)002:2773: bsngo ba'i tshul dang gsum las /
NK133(po)002:2779: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i dge rtsa mtha' dag gzhan
NK133(po)002:2780: don du rdzogs byang gi rgyur blos stobs kyis yongs
NK133(po)002:2781: su bsgyur ba'o // nges tshig ni pa ri na
NK133(po)002:2782: ta zhes pa'i sgra las yongs su bsgyur ba'am spel
NK133(po)002:2783: su bsgyur ba'o // ba ste / dman pa mchog tu bsgyur ba dang /
NK133(po)002:2784: nyung ngu mang por spel ba'i don can no //
NK133(po)002:2786: 'khor gsum la bden zhen gyi blo dang bcas pas
NK133(po)002:2787: lha mi dang nyan rang gi sar bsngo ba ma
NK133(po)002:2788: dag pa dang / 'khor gsum la bden zhen bral
NK133(po)002:2789: ba'i blos mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las 'das par
NK133(po)002:2791: gnyis pa bsngo dgos pa'i rgyu mtshan la gnyis las /
NK133(po)002:2792: dang po ma bsngosa pa'i nyes dmigs ni /
NK133(po)002:2793: 'dus byas kyi dge ba ji lta bu zhig yin
NK133(po)002:2794: kyang thabs shes zung du 'brel ba'i bsngo ba khyad
NK133(po)002:2795: par can zhig gis rgyas ma thebs na /
NK133(po)002:2796: mi mthun phyogs kyis bcom sla zhing bar ma dor chud 'dza' bar 'gyur te /
NK133(po)002:2798: bskal pa stong du bsags pa yin //
NK133(po)002:2799: sbyin dang bde gshegs mchod la sogs //
NK133(po)002:2800: legs spyad gang yin de kun kyang //
NK133(po)002:2801: khong khro gcig gis 'joms par byed //
NK133(po)002:2804: rigs kyi bu byang chub sems dpa' chos bzhi dang
NK133(po)002:2805: ldan pa rnams kyi sbyin pa zad par 'gyur te
NK133(po)002:2808: yongs su ma bsngosa pa dang /
NK133(po)002:2810: dma' bar skye bar 'dod pa dang /
NK133(po)002:2811: sdig pa'i grogs po la bsten pa ste rigs kyi
NK133(po)002:2812: bu byang chub sems dpa' chos bzhi po de dag
NK133(po)002:2813: dang ldan pa rnams kyi sbyin pa ni yongs su
NK133(po)002:2816: der ma zad bsngo bas ma zin pa ni theg pa chen po'i khyur yang mi tshud de /
NK133(po)002:2818: nyan thos theg pa de las ni //
NK133(po)002:2819: byang chub sems dpa'i smon lam dang //
NK133(po)002:2820: spyod pa yongs ba sngo ma bshad des //
NK133(po)002:2821: byang chub sems dpar ga la 'gyur //
NK133(po)002:2823: gnyis pa bsngo ba'i phan yon ni /
NK133(po)002:2824: blo gros rgya mtshos zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK133(po)002:2825: blo gros rgya mtsho 'di lta ste /
NK133(po)002:2826: dper na mchil ma'i thal ba zhig bye ma'i steng du bor na myur du skam par 'gyur ro //
NK133(po)002:2827: de nyid rgya mtsho chen por bor na ni ji
NK133(po)002:2828: srid rgya mtsho chen po de nyid zad cing skam
NK133(po)002:2829: par ma gyur pa de srid kyi bar du mchil
NK133(po)002:2830: ma'i thal ba de yang mi skam mo //
NK133(po)002:2831: blo gros rgya mtsho de bzhin du /
NK133(po)002:2832: dge ba'i rtsa ba sgrub pa de yang /
NK133(po)002:2836: log par bsngosa na ni 'dzad la /
NK133(po)002:2837: gang rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi rgya
NK133(po)002:2838: mtsho chen por bsngosa na ni mi 'dzad cing gong
NK133(po)002:2841: dge ba gzhan kun chu shing bzhin du ni //
NK133(po)002:2842: 'bras bu bskyed nas zad par 'gyur ba nyid //
NK133(po)002:2843: byang chub sems kyi ljon shing rtag par yang //
NK133(po)002:2847: byang chub sems dpa' mkhas pa thabs mkhas gang zhig gis //
NK133(po)002:2848: de dag bsod nams bya ba'i dngos la yi rang nas //
NK133(po)002:2849: sems can don du byang chub mchog rab yongs bsngo na //
NK133(po)002:2850: yongs su bsngo bas 'gro ba thams cad zil gyis gnon //
NK133(po)002:2852: gsum pa bsngo ba'i tshul la /
NK133(po)002:2853: gang bsngo rgyu'i dge ba dang /
NK133(po)002:2854: gang du bsngo ba'i gnas dang /
NK133(po)002:2855: gang gi ched du bsngo ba dang /
NK133(po)002:2856: tshul ji ltar bsngo ba ste bzhi las /
NK133(po)002:2858: gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i mdo las /
NK133(po)002:2859: stong pa nyid la 'dir mos nas //
NK133(po)002:2860: byang chub sems kyang mi gtong dang //
NK133(po)002:2861: dam pa'i chos ni 'dzin bgyid pa //
NK133(po)002:2862: 'di ni bsod nams sdud pa lags //
NK133(po)002:2863: zhes pa ltar rnam par dkar ba'i legs byas kyi
NK133(po)002:2864: chu klung mang po phyogs gcig sdud pa'i bsod nams
NK133(po)002:2865: kyi rgya mtsho chen po chos sbyin mi zad pa'i
NK133(po)002:2866: phyi mo spar du bskrun pa las byung ba'i grags
NK133(po)002:2867: dkar gyi rlab phreng srid rtser 'phyur ba 'di nyid
NK133(po)002:2868: kyis mtshon te / dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas dang
NK133(po)002:2869: byang chub sems dpa' nyan thos rang rgyal so so'i
NK133(po)002:2870: skye bo tshogs dang bcas pa rnams kyi dge ba'i
NK133(po)002:2871: rtsa ba ji snyed mchis pa dang /
NK133(po)002:2872: rang gzhan mtha' dag gi lus longs spyod dge tshogs
NK133(po)002:2873: rgya mtsho rnams gcig tu bsdoms nas bsngo bar bya
NK133(po)002:2874: ba yin no // sdud pa las /
NK133(po)002:2875: dang po byang chub mchog tu sems skyed bskyed pa nas //
NK133(po)002:2876: rnam par 'dren pa rnams kyi dam chos zad kyi dus //
NK133(po)002:2877: de bar rgyal ba de dag bsod nams gang yin pa //
NK133(po)002:2878: pha rol phyin dang ldan dang sangs rgyas chos gang dang //
NK133(po)002:2879: gang yang sangs rgyas sras rnams dang ni nyan thos dang //
NK133(po)002:2880: slob dang mii slob dge ba zag bcas zag med pa //
NK133(po)002:2881: bsdus nas byang chub sems dpa' rjes su yi rang zhing //
NK133(po)002:2882: 'gro ba'i don rgyur byang chub phyir ni thams cad ba sngo //
NK133(po)002:2884: rdo rje rgyal mtshan gyi bsngo ba'i le'u las /
NK133(po)002:2885: 'gro kun dge rtsa ji snyed yod pa dang //
NK133(po)002:2886: byas dang byed 'gyur de bzhin byed pa rnams //
NK133(po)002:2887: bzang po ji bzhin de 'dra'i sa dag la //
NK133(po)002:2888: kun nas kun kyang bzang por reg gyur cig /
NK133(po)002:2891: lus dang de bzhin longs spyod dang //
NK133(po)002:2892: dus gsum dge ba skyes pa rnams //
NK133(po)002:2893: sems can kun gyi don sgrub phyir //
NK133(po)002:2894: phangs pa med par btang bar bya //
NK133(po)002:2897: spang rtogs phun sum tshogs pa'i bdag nyid mi gnas
NK133(po)002:2898: pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa chen po'i go 'phang
NK133(po)002:2899: kho na ste / yongs su bsngo ba'i mdo las /
NK133(po)002:2900: dge ba'i rtsa ba dag kyang sangs rgyas nyid kyi sar bsngo'o //
NK133(po)002:2903: dge ba'i rtsa ba de yang rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid ma gtogs pa /
NK133(po)002:2905: rang sangs rgyas kyi sar yongs su bsngo bar mi gzhug go //
NK133(po)002:2908: thog ma med pa'i dus nas dgra gnyen bar ma'i
NK133(po)002:2909: rang bzhin du mar phan tshun du 'brel ba'i mtha'
NK133(po)002:2910: yas pa'i lus can thams cad kyi ched du ste
NK133(po)002:2912: dngos sam yang na brgyud kyang rung //
NK133(po)002:2913: sems can don las gzhan mi spyad //
NK133(po)002:2914: sems can kho na'i don gyi phyir //
NK133(po)002:2915: thams cad byang chub rgyur bsngo'o //
NK133(po)002:2917: de ltar bsngosa pas sems can gyi khams bzhin phan yon kyang tshad med de /
NK133(po)002:2919: sems can khams ni chad med la //
NK133(po)002:2922: bsod nams kyi dngos po sems can gyi don du
NK133(po)002:2923: bsngo ba 'di ni gzhan la med pa'i sangs rgyas
NK133(po)002:2924: kyi bstan pa kho na'i khyad chos yin te /
NK133(po)002:2926: bsod nams bya ba'i tshogs dag ni //
NK133(po)002:2927: sems can rnams la yongs bsngo bar //
NK133(po)002:2928: bcom ldan khyod kyis gang gsungs pa //
NK133(po)002:2929: de gzhan bstan bcos las ma bshad //
NK133(po)002:2933: ji ltar dug dang 'dres pa'i kha zas bzang za ba //
NK133(po)002:2934: dkar po'i chos la dmigs pa'ang de 'drar rgyal bas gsungs //
NK133(po)002:2935: de ltar 'di ltar yongs su bsngo ba bslab bya ste //
NK133(po)002:2936: ji ltar rgyal ba de dag dge ba de mkhyen pa'i //
NK133(po)002:2937: rnam pa gang yin 'byung gang mtshan nyid gang yin la //
NK133(po)002:2938: rjes su yi rang de lta de ltar yongs su bsngo //
NK133(po)002:2939: de ltar bsod nams byang chub yongs su bsngo byed na //
NK133(po)002:2940: dug med sangs rgyas mi spong rgyal bas gsung ba smra //
NK133(po)002:2941: zhes pa bzhin dmigs pa'i dug dang bral ba'i 'khor
NK133(po)002:2942: gsum yongs dag gi bsngo ba rgyal ba dgyes pa'i
NK133(po)002:2943: lam bzang la slob pa gal che ste /
NK133(po)002:2944: de la 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa ni /
NK133(po)002:2946: gal te 'di ltar chos 'di 'gags shing zad pa dang //
NK133(po)002:2947: gang du yongs su bsngo ba de yang zad pa dang //
NK133(po)002:2948: chos kyis chos la nam yang mi bsngo shes gyur na //
NK133(po)002:2949: de ltar rab tu shes pas yongs su bsngosa pa yin //
NK133(po)002:2951: blo gros rgya mtshos zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK133(po)002:2952: blo gros rgya mtsho gzhan yang 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa gang zhe na /
NK133(po)002:2953: gang la bdag tu 'dzin pa med pa dang /
NK133(po)002:2954: sems can du 'dzin pa med pa dang /
NK133(po)002:2956: zhes sogs gsungs pa bzhin rnam par mi rtog pa'i
NK133(po)002:2957: shes rab zab mos bden gnyis res 'jogs su ma
NK133(po)002:2958: song bar chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis nam mkha'i
NK133(po)002:2959: dkyil ltar spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral ba
NK133(po)002:2960: mngon sum du mthong ba'i ngang nas lhun gyis grub
NK133(po)002:2961: pa'i snying rje chen pos sems can gyi khams la
NK133(po)002:2962: blta ba'i bsngo ba mtshan nyid pa ni /
NK133(po)002:2963: sa dang po nas brtsams te 'phags pa rnams kho na la yod kyis /
NK133(po)002:2964: mos spyod kyi lam pas de nyid sgra ji bzhin par lam du slong dka' ba yang /
NK133(po)002:2966: chos rnams thams cad rkyen yin te //
NK133(po)002:2967: 'dun pa'i rtse la rab tu gnas //
NK133(po)002:2969: gang zhig sangs rgyas yid byed pa //
NK133(po)002:2970: de yi mdun na ston pa bzhugs //
NK133(po)002:2971: zhes pa ltar 'dun pa bsgyur ba kho na gtso che bas /
NK133(po)002:2973: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams dang /
NK133(po)002:2974: sa chen po la bzhugs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po dang /
NK133(po)002:2976: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor tshad med pas chos kyi dbyings
NK133(po)002:2977: kyis mthas gtugs pa'i zhing khams rgya mtsho rgyas par
NK133(po)002:2978: bkang ste bzhugs par mos pa de dag gi drung
NK133(po)002:2979: du bdag nyid mngon par snang bar byas te /
NK133(po)002:2980: thabs snying rje chen po dang shes rab stong pa nyid zung du 'brel ba'i blos /
NK133(po)002:2981: ji ltar sngon gyi sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems
NK133(po)002:2982: dpa' rnams kyis bsngo bar mdzad pa de bzhin du
NK133(po)002:2983: bdag gis kyang yongs su bsngo bar bagyi'o snyams pa'i
NK133(po)002:2984: 'dun pa drag po rtse gcig tu bya ste /
NK133(po)002:2986: 'jam dpal dpa' bos ji ltar mkhyen pa dang //
NK133(po)002:2987: kun tu bzang po de yang de bzhin te //
NK133(po)002:2988: de dag kun gyi rjes su bdag slob phyir //
NK133(po)002:2989: dge ba 'di dag thams cad rab tu bsngo //
NK133(po)002:2990: dus gsum gshegs pa'i rgyal ba thams cad kyis //
NK133(po)002:2991: bsngo ba gang la mchog tu basngagasa pa des //
NK133(po)002:2992: bdag gi dge ba'i rtsa ba'i 'di kun kyang //
NK133(po)002:2993: bzang po spyod phyir rab tu bsngo bar bgyi //
NK133(po)002:2994: zhes pa'i tshul gyis bsngo ba ni 'phags pa'i lam
NK133(po)002:2995: dang rjes su mthun pa'i bsngo tshul rmad du byung
NK133(po)002:2996: ba'o // bzhi pa bsngo smon dang shis par brjod
NK133(po)002:2997: pa'i tshigs su bcad pa cung zad cig snyan ngag
NK133(po)002:2998: gi lam nas spel ba ni 'di lta ste /
NK133(po)002:2999: swa sti mang+ga la sh+r+ai dz+aa la b+ha wan+tuh bsam
NK133(po)002:3000: gyis mi khyab nam mkha'i khor yug til gyi gang
NK133(po)002:3002: stobs bcu'i dbang phyug mtshan dpe'i gzi 'bar thub mchog zla ba'i phreng ba las //
NK133(po)002:3003: kun nas mdzes bskor snying stobs rmad byung rgyal sras rgyu skar 'khrigs 'dra bas //
NK133(po)002:3004: sa bla'i khyon kun dogs por bgyis te mos ldan bsod nams zhing du dgongs /
NK133(po)002:3006: 1 / ring mo zhig nas 'gro khams yongs la bu gcig ltar brtse thugs rje'i shugs //
NK133(po)002:3007: goms pa'i dam baca'i gzhan dbang gyur phyir zhi ba mchog gi mthar son kyang //
NK133(po)002:3008: gdul bya'i 'gro la byams pas 'khyud pa srid pa'i mthar yang mi gtong zhing //
NK133(po)002:3009: bskul mi dgos par dge ba'i bshes gnyen gang gis mdzad pa de rnams kyi /
NK133(po)002:3011: 2 / zhabs kyi pad+mora gus pas btud de sgyu ma lta bu'i ting 'dzin dang //
NK133(po)002:3012: smon lam stobs kyis rnam par 'phrul las ngo mtshar mchod pa'i sprin phung ni //
NK133(po)002:3013: shin tu rgya che blo gros rmad byung kun tu bzang po'i spyod yul la //
NK133(po)002:3014: mngon par 'gran pa'i bkod pa rgya mtshos mtha' las rgyal ba'i zhing bkang ste /
NK133(po)002:3016: 3 / shes rab dang ni snying rje'i stobs kyis srid dang zhi ba'i mtha' bkag nas //
NK133(po)002:3017: bde bas phongs pa'i lus can mtha' dag byang chub snying po'i gser gling du //
NK133(po)002:3018: bsgrod pa'i gru chen rnam dag smon pa'i cho ga bzang po 'du byed na //
NK133(po)002:3019: mthun 'gyur rlung gi ba dan 'phyar la bden tshig grub rnams deng 'dir bzhengs /
NK133(po)002:3021: 4 / bde gshegs mchod dang sbyin sogs las byung bsod nams rnam grangs gzhan mang pos //
NK133(po)002:3022: cha shas tsam yang mtshon par nus min rgyal ba rnams kyi chos 'dzin pa'i //
NK133(po)002:3023: gzhi dang rtsa ba gsung rabs yi ge'i glegs bam char chen 'dzad med du //
NK133(po)002:3024: spel ba'i legs byas nam mkha'i bla rer phyogs kun khyab par bris pa 'dis /
NK133(po)002:3026: 5 / nye bar mtshon te rgyal dang rgyal sras nyan rang 'phags tshogs so skyes bcas //
NK133(po)002:3027: tha dad kun nas so sor bskrun pa'i rnam dkar chu klung 'bum phrag gcig /
NK133(po)002:3028: rjes su yi rang thabs mkhas spyod pa'i yur bar drangs te legs smon gyi //
NK133(po)002:3029: 'bab stegs mchog las rnam pa kun mkhyen rgya mtsho che der gcig tu gzhol /
NK133(po)002:3031: 6 / de yi mthu las phan bde'i 'byung gnas bslab gsum nor bu'i tog mdzes shing //
NK133(po)002:3032: zab rgyas chos tshul dar gyi sham bus kun nas 'khor ba'i bsil grib tu //
NK133(po)002:3033: las nyon sdug bsngal tsha bas gdung ba'i 'gro ba mtha' dag dbugs 'byin pa'i //
NK133(po)002:3034: thub dbang bstan pa'i gdugs dkar gcig gis sa gsum rtag tu skyongs gyur cig 7 /
NK133(po)002:3035: sna tshogs las kyi sgyu mas sprul pa'i 'gro ba'i gnas ris tha dad du //
NK133(po)002:3036: 'khrul snang tsha grang me lce'i dbal dang bkres skom chu bo'i dba' la g.yeng //
NK133(po)002:3037: glen lkug rmongs pa'i mun par 'khyams pa'i nyam thag 'gro ba 'di kun kyang //
NK133(po)002:3038: snyi las grol ba'i mkha' lding ji bzhin bde 'gro'i gnas su bskyod gyur cig 8 /
NK133(po)002:3039: de bzhin 'thab rtsod las kyis mnar ba'i sbyin skyes bu yi tshogs rnams ni //
NK133(po)002:3040: bzod dang chog shes byams pa'i sems thob khoms ldan min pa'i lus spong zhing //
NK133(po)002:3041: rtag tu bag med 'dod pas myos shing 'chi 'phos gzir ba'i lha dag kyang //
NK133(po)002:3042: dran dang bag ldan chos la spyod bzhin snang nas snang bar bsgrod gyur cig 9 /
NK133(po)002:3043: thar pa'i lam stegs mngon par mtho ba lha mi'i 'jig rten thams cad du //
NK133(po)002:3044: gtsug lag gnyis kyi khrims lugs ji bzhin nyes pa'i ra ri dang bral bar //
NK133(po)002:3045: legs par bskyangs pas sde bzhi'i dpal sogs rdzogs ldan dus kyi 'byor pa rnams //
NK133(po)002:3046: zla ba mthong ba'i chu gter lta bur ches cher gong du 'phel gyur cig 10 /
NK133(po)002:3047: dkar phyogs lha dang klu rnams dgyes pas btsa' sad ser ba'i ming med cing //
NK133(po)002:3048: dus dang dus su dbyar skyes phreng bas phyogs kyi go skabs phrog pa las //
NK133(po)002:3049: zim bur babs pa'i sprin gyi myu gus 'dzin ma'i gzhi kun brlan byas pas //
NK133(po)002:3050: rtsa ba sdong bu lo ma 'bras bcas 'dod dgu'i snye ma bdo gyur cig 11 /
NK133(po)002:3051: gcig tu gnag dang 'dren ma'i las kyi shing sdong rul ba las skyes me //
NK133(po)002:3052: 'phral rkyen rlung gis shugs kyis bskyod pas phan bde'i lcug phran bsregs pa'i lce //
NK133(po)002:3053: nad dang 'khrug rtsod dus kyi rgud pa yon por g.yo ba ma lus pa //
NK133(po)002:3054: bsod nams bdud rtsi'i char chen 'di yis ming gi
NK133(po)002:3055: lhag mar zhi gyur cig 12 /'dod sde mnar sems
NK133(po)002:3056: las kyis 'phang ba'i gshin rje'i sder gtogs gdon gyi
NK133(po)002:3057: tshogs // thal mdog lang tsho khrag gis gsher bzhin mi snyan bshugs glu'i sgra dang bcas //
NK133(po)002:3058: 'gro ba'i tshe srog yid la brnag pas mtshon mor rgyu ba de rnams kyang //
NK133(po)002:3059: byams pa'i sems kyis nye bar gnas shing sdig pa'i las las ldog gyur cig 13 /
NK133(po)002:3060: gang zhig legs nyes 'byed pa'i mig ni log lta'i mun pas khebs gyur cing //
NK133(po)002:3061: dam pa min pa'i grogs kyi rjes phyogs skye dgu'i bde skyid 'joms pa dang //
NK133(po)002:3062: dam par sdang zhing bstan la dgrar blta dkon mchog dbu 'phang smod byed pa'i //
NK133(po)002:3063: rgyal rigs gdol ba'i bsam sbyor mtha' dag 'dod pa'i don las nyams gyur cig 14 /
NK133(po)002:3064: sngon smon log pa'i bdud rigs kha cig snyigs ma'i dus 'dir rgyal bstan nyid //
NK133(po)002:3065: dkrug pa'i ched du dge sbyong zol gyis lta spyod phyin ci log ston cing //
NK133(po)002:3066: thub pa'i ring lugs mog por bgyid pa'i lto 'gro gdug pa'i sems ldan rnams //
NK133(po)002:3067: rgya mtsho'i rlab kyis mi ro ji bzhin 'jig rten gzhan du 'phen gyur cig 15 /
NK133(po)002:3068: sde bzhi'i dpal 'byor dge bcu'i khrims kyis drang po'i lam du srong mkhas pa'i //
NK133(po)002:3069: sngon byon chos rgyal rnams kyi lugs bzhin chos srid gnyis kyis mnga' ris kun //
NK133(po)002:3070: ma mas bu bzhin brtse bas skyongs pa'i gnam bskos sa yi dbang phyug gi //
NK133(po)002:3071: grags pa'i rgyal mtshan nam yang nub med phyogs las rnam par rgyal gyur cig 16 /
NK133(po)002:3072: kha ba'i ljongs 'dir thub bstan lung rtogs pad+mo kun nas rgyas pa'i tshal //
NK133(po)002:3073: snyigs ma'i spyod tshul ga bur rdul gyis rnying bar byas gang bshad sgrub kyis //
NK133(po)002:3074: nyin mor byed pa'i snang ba stong gis slar yang gsal mdzad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK133(po)002:3075: gzhan phan pha mtha' yas pa'i byed por zhabs pad bskal brgyar brtan gyur cig 17 /
NK133(po)002:3076: theg pa'i yang rtse shin tu rnal 'byor sde gsum klong dgu'i shing rta che //
NK133(po)002:3077: rdzogs chen pa zhes mtshan gyi grags pas 'khor yug ri bo'i khongs khyab pa //
NK133(po)002:3078: yab sras brgyud par bcas pa kun gyi bzhed don phrin las lhun grub cing //
NK133(po)002:3079: bstan 'dzin 'dus pa'i sde tshogs rnams kyang dbyar gyi mtsho ltar rgyas gyur cig 18 /
NK133(po)002:3080: khyad par tshul gnas thos dang bsam ldan sgom pa'i don la rab sbyor zhing //
NK133(po)002:3081: klog spong las kyi 'khor lo gsum gyis rgyal bstan bla nas blar 'degs pa'i //
NK133(po)002:3082: sh+aakya'i sras po ngur smrig 'chang ba'i li khris chu gter 'phyur ba lta'i //
NK133(po)002:3083: tshogs kyi mchog rab bsod nams zhing gis 'dzam gling tha gru khyab gyur cig 19 /
NK133(po)002:3084: snying stobs brtson pa'i go cha cher gos gtong pa'i sgo 'phar brgya phyes nas //
NK133(po)002:3085: phyi dus bstan pa'i btsas su bsgrub pa'i chos tshul nor bu'i za ma tog /
NK133(po)002:3086: chos sbyin mi zad 'dod dgur 'jo 'di chos 'dod skye bo'i tshogs rnams la //
NK133(po)002:3087: chos phongs las kyi duhkha bsal phyir chos kyi sku bzhin rtag gyur cig20 /
NK133(po)002:3088: legs byas mtshungs med rin chen mchog 'di brtson pa chen pos bsgrub pa'i tshe //
NK133(po)002:3089: legs pa'i bsam pas dngos sam brgyud nas zhabs tog sri zhu'i mthun sbyor dang //
NK133(po)002:3090: legs so'i gtam gyis rjes su yi rang bgyis pa tsam gyi skye bo yang //
NK133(po)002:3091: legs ldan lha dang mi yi dpal la tshe rabs kun tu spyod gyur cig 21 /
NK133(po)002:3092: dkar dkar lhag bsam gangs ri las 'ongs snyan snyan grags pa'i spring yig dang //
NK133(po)002:3093: mang mang bsod nams gang+g+aa'i klung 'di zab zab rnam kun mkhyen pa'i mtshor //
NK133(po)002:3094: lhung lhung babs la phyogs bcu'i rgyal kun lhag lhag dgyes pa'i rnam 'gyur gyis //
NK133(po)002:3095: yang yang shis par brjod dang chab gcig zim zim me tog char du bsnyil /
NK133(po)002:3097: 22 / bdag kyang deng nas tshe rabs kun tu bde ba can sogs zhing mang por //
NK133(po)002:3098: rgyal ba'i mdun sar pad+mo'i stan la mtshan dpes brgyan pa'i lus thob cing //
NK133(po)002:3099: 'jam pa'i dbyangs dang spyan ras gzigs mtshungs sems dpa'i tshogs dang lhan cig tu //
NK133(po)002:3100: smon lam thabs dang rdzu 'phrul stobs kyis chos kyi kun dgar spyod gyur cig 23 /
NK133(po)002:3101: rang don kho nar gcig tu gzhol min thabs mkhas spyod pa rgya mtsho yis //
NK133(po)002:3102: la lar dge sbyong bram ze lha dang drang srong de bzhin rgyal rigs dang //
NK133(po)002:3103: gzhan du khye'u bu mo'i tshul 'chang tshong dpon smad 'tshong gdol ba sogs //
NK133(po)002:3104: sna tshogs gzugs kyis gzhan phan sgrub la nam yang bsnyel bar ma gyur cig 24 /
NK133(po)002:3105: mdor na gangs kyi ri la skyes pa'i rtsi sman ji bzhin bdag nyid kyi //
NK133(po)002:3106: lus dang longs spyod dge tshogs bcas kun mtha' yas 'gro ba'i nyer 'tsho ru //
NK133(po)002:3107: dpag bsam shing dang yid bzhin nor ltar 'bad pa med par lhun grub nas //
NK133(po)002:3108: rnam par mi rtog rlom sems med cing rgyal ba'i mdzad pa bsgrub par shog 25 /
NK133(po)002:3109: chos nyid rgyu mthun bsam mi khyab dang chos can rgyu 'bras bslu ba med //
NK133(po)002:3110: lhag bsam stobs dang mchog gsum bden pa'i byin rlab rmad du byung ba'i mthus //
NK133(po)002:3111: deng 'dir legs par smon pa'i gnas kun gegs med yid bzhin 'grub 'gyur pa'i //
NK133(po)002:3112: dge mtshan bkra shis g.yang du 'khyil bas sa chen rtag tu khyab par shog 26 /
NK133(po)002:3113: bka' ma theg rim dgu'i phrin chog rnams kyi dkar
NK133(po)002:3114: chag yid bzhin dbang gi rgyal po'i bang mdzod las
NK133(po)002:3115: / de ltar spar du bsgrubs pa'i dgos ched dang
NK133(po)002:3116: phan yon bstan pa bsngo smon shis brjod dang bcas
NK133(po)002:3117: pa'i skabs te gsum pa'i bdag nyid can gyis legs
NK133(po)002:3118: / par rdzogs so //// zhes pa 'di ni skyabs
NK133(po)002:3119: rje thams cad mkhyen pa mtshan brjod par dka' yang
NK133(po)002:3120: don gyi slad du mtshan nas smos te /
NK133(po)002:3121: 7 rgyal ba'i sras po gzhan phan mtha' yas 'od
NK133(po)002:3122: zer mchog gi zhal snga nas kyis rmad du byung
NK133(po)002:3123: ba'i thugs bskyed rgya chen pos chos sbyin mi zad
NK133(po)002:3124: pa'i phyi mo spar du bskrun skabs /
NK133(po)002:3125: rje de nyid kyi zhabs rdul la spyi bos reg
NK133(po)002:3126: pa'i slob 'bangs yongs kyi tha shal du gyur pa
NK133(po)002:3127: / sh+aakya'i sras po'i gzugs brnyan tsam 'dzin pa'i rmongs
